# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:19
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_cfc018e4:

    # "I wake to the annoying din of my alarm clock, its bright red numerals lighting up my face."
    "目覚まし時計がうっとうしく鳴り響き、俺は目を覚ます。時計の数字の鮮やかな赤い光が俺の顔を照らしている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:23
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_209990fd:

    # "It's the same alarm clock I had at home, one of the few remaining artifacts from my days before coming to Yamaku. I'd hoped that using it would help ease my transition into this new life."
    "俺が家で使っていたのと同じものだ。山久学園に来る前の人生から引き継がれた数少ない遺物の一つ。これがあれば新しい人生への移行のショックが和らぐだろう、と思っていた。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:25
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_22de8e82:

    # "No such luck, though."
    "でも、ちっとも役に立ちゃしない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:27
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_2c369007:

    # "Groggily dragging myself out of bed, I wipe the sleep out of my eyes, then reach over to my desk. I open a couple of the bottles of medication strewn across it, and swallow a few pills dry."
    "ベッドからのそのそと起き出し眠い目をこすると、俺は机に近寄る。そこに散らばっている薬瓶を開け、水なしで薬をいくつか飲み込む。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:29
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_129293d6:

    # "By now, the process is starting to become automatic - something I should be glad for, given their purpose."
    "今ではこの習慣も体が覚え始めている。その目的を考えれば、これは喜ぶべきことなんだろう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:36
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_3279adb9:

    # "Feeling much more awake than before, I wander into the bathroom."
    "かなり目も覚めてきて、俺はバスルームに身を滑り込ませる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:43
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_9d2e4b78:

    # "While the shower warms up, my mind begins to wander as my new daily routine begins once again."
    "新しい日課がまた始まろうとしている。シャワーの温度が上がっていくあいだ、俺は思いを巡らせる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:45
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_f481e23b:

    # "The bright colors of the fireworks fill my mind, as do the two girls with whom I spent my time watching them. It feels strange to be moved so much by people I know so little about."
    "俺の心の中を占めているのは、鮮やかな色彩の花火と、それを一緒に眺め続けた２人の少女。ほとんど知らない人間のためにこんなにも心動かされるなんて、なんだか変な気分だ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:47
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_f5543ea2:

    # "Then again, I suppose these aren't normal circumstances. At least I have someone to talk to, now, aside from my schoolmate next door."
    "とはいえ、今の状況だって普通じゃないと思う。まあ、少なくとも話し相手はできた……隣の部屋のやつは置いとくとして。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:54
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_18392d56:

    # "With the time left before school begins today waning, I begin to get ready for class."
    "始業時間がだんだん近づいてきて、俺は登校のための準備を整える。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:61
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_ef224c4c:

    # "Walking through the door into the classroom, I notice that I'm still somewhat early. I see about five or six students milling around, most of them looking as if they'd rather be still in bed."
    "教室の入り口をくぐり、まだ少し早い時間であることに気づく。５、６人の生徒がクラス内をうろついているけど、そのほとんどはまだ寝ているかのようだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:63
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_067cc585:

    # "It's at times like this that I appreciate being a morning person. That said, two students in particular seem just as perky as always."
    "こんな時には自分が朝型人間であることをありがたく思う。まあ、あそこの２人もいつもどおり意気揚々に見えるけど。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:65
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_c67625c7:

    # hi "Hi Shizune, hi Misha."
    hi "やあ、静音、ミーシャ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:71
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_6073338f:

    # "I suddenly realize that my greeting would be lost on the former, so I quickly follow it up with a wave. She doesn't seem overly bothered."
    "静音には俺の挨拶は伝わらないであろうことに突然気づいて、急いで手を振ってフォローする。でも静音はあまり気にしていないようだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:73
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_dbaeb253:

    # "Or interested, for that matter."
    "というか、関心もなさそうだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:78
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_ef2b123c:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:83
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_fe67b690:

    # mi "Hello, Hicchan~! Are you feeling well?"
    mi "ひっちゃ～ん、おはよ！　調子どう？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:85
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_4b8901cb:

    # "I can only assume her greeting comes from Shizune. It's hard to tell if she's speaking as herself or Shizune, sometimes."
    "この挨拶はたぶん静音からのものだろう、と想像するしかない。時々ミーシャと静音、どっちの言葉なのかよく分からなくなることがある。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:87
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_7af88fd1:

    # hi "Better than most everyone else, I guess. You two seem bright and chipper."
    hi "他の連中よりは元気だと思うけど。２人ともなんだかえらく元気そうだな"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:96
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_3a3d20d6:

    # "Misha signs this back to Shizune as I say it, eliciting a somewhat terse answer, if her sharp and rapid arm movements are any indication."
    "俺がそう言うあいだ、ミーシャは手話で静音にそれを伝える。それに対する静音の返事が手厳しいものであろうことは、彼女の鋭く速い腕の動きで明らかだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:98
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_f9de7fcc:

    # "Considering that these two made such a big deal out of the festival preparations, I probably should've chosen my words more carefully."
    "学園祭の準備で大きな働きをしてきた２人を前にして、たぶん俺はもっと言葉を選ぶべきだったんだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:103
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_b33ba1f7:

    # shi "…!"
    shi "……！"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:108
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_f2ee3be2:

    # mi "Since you're a new student, we've been cutting you some slack. Please don't expect this kind of task-dodging to be allowed in the future."
    mi "新しい生徒だからあんまり仕事しないのも勘弁してあげてたけど、これからもそういうサボり行為が許されるとは思わないでくださいね"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:110
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_8b1b6c15:

    # "Misha looks as if she's about to add her own comment, but quickly goes back to interpreting as Shizune continues, unabated."
    "ミーシャも自分の言い分を付け加えたかったらしいけど、絶え間なく続く静音の手話を見てすぐに翻訳作業に戻る。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:116
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_23c53818:

    # mi "While your contribution to class 3-2's stall is appreciated—"
    mi "３－２の屋台作りに貢献したってのは感心だけどぉ――"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:118
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_9dd790f1:

    # "Huh. Word sure got around quickly. That, or these two have their fingers on the pulse of the school."
    "へえ。噂が伝わるのは早いもんだな。さもなきゃ、この２人は学校で起こるあらゆる出来事を把握しているんだろう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:123
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_52919325:

    # mi "—we would prefer your efforts to be focused on the task at hand. Namely, your own class."
    mi "――そういう労力は自分がやるべき所に集中して使ってほしいわね。つまり、自分のクラス、ってことね"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:125
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_ee93d9e1:

    # "As much as I hate to admit it, they do have a point. Before I can respond, though, Shizune adds something more, which draws a smile from Misha."
    "認めたくはないけど、正論だ。俺がそれに対して口を開こうとすると、静音が他になにかを付け加える。それを見てミーシャが微笑む。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:130
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_ef2b123c_1:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:135
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_8e8e1c9e:

    # mi "Did you enjoy the festival, then~?"
    mi "それでぇ～、学園祭楽しかった？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:137
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_f33b2189:

    # "Lecture over, I guess."
    "説教は終わり、みたいだな。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:139
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_efef2299:

    # hi "Yeah, it was good. Did you two enjoy it?"
    hi "ああ、楽しかったよ。そっちは？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:145
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_f225f44f:

    # "Shizune gives a short nod as Misha grins and bounces her head up and down. The contrast, side-by-side, is amusing."
    "ミーシャがにっと笑いながら大きく首を上下に振り、静音も軽くうなずく。この２人のしぐさは対照的で面白い。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:147
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_2f080066:

    # "Out of the corner of my eye, I notice more students starting to trickle into the classroom. A quick glance at my watch confirms that they're a few minutes late."
    "その時、ぱらぱらと教室に入ってくる生徒たちの姿が視界の隅に映る。時計に目をやると、数分の遅刻だ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:160
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_a0855f2a:

    # "I look over to Hanako's seat and realize that she's already there, and contentedly reading a book. It makes me wonder just how long she's been there without me noticing."
    "華子の席に目を向けると、彼女はすでにそこに座り、満足げに読書にいそしんでいる。今まで気づかなかったけど、いつからいたんだろう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:174
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_48b87a87:

    # "With heavy footsteps coming up the hallway signaling Mutou's arrival, our idle talking comes to an end and I take my seat next to Misha."
    "廊下のほうから重苦しい足音がする。武藤先生が来たのを知って、俺は雑談を切り上げミーシャの隣の席に座る。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:176
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_d5812d21:

    # "As the door slides open, he strides through with a ponderous gait. His posture is even worse than usual, and his eyes are barely staying open. I guess my quip to Lilly and Hanako about the staff was misplaced."
    "ドアが開き、先生が重い足取りで教室に入ってくる。いつもより姿勢が悪く、目はほとんど開いていない。この前リリーと華子にここのスタッフの皮肉を言ったけど、どうやらあれは間違っていたらしい。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:180
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_0ffd98b9:

    # "Everyone opens their books as he reaches his desk, and the first class of the new week begins."
    "先生が教卓まで来ると、クラスの皆がいっせいに教科書を開く。新しい週の一時間目の始まりだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:192
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_fbb93d12:

    # "I rub my eyes as the lunch bell rings out, glad for the temporary reprieve from work."
    "昼休みを告げるチャイムが鳴り、俺はつかの間の休息にほっとしながら目をこする。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:202
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_8d2cf21e:

    # "I'm entirely unsurprised when I look over to the door and see Lilly standing there, cane in hand, patiently waiting for Hanako."
    "思ったとおり、リリーが手に杖を持ち、教室の入り口のそばでじっと華子を待っている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:204
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_f72317b2:

    # "Considering her acceptance of my request to join them yesterday, I decide to spend my lunchtime with them rather than eat alone."
    "昨日も一緒に過ごすことをオーケーしてくれたことだし、昼食も１人で取るより彼女たちと一緒に取ることにする。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:215
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_9fe1e60e:

    # "Hanako moves surprisingly fast to meet her companion, and the two enter the hallway before I can catch up."
    "華子が驚くべき速さでリリーの元に駆け寄り、俺が呼び止める前に廊下に出て行ってしまう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:228
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_46add2a6:

    # "Lilly's head turns slightly, registering the sound of footsteps behind her. As Hanako notices and follows her lead, she almost jumps in surprise."
    "背後の足音に気づき、リリーがほんの少し振り返る。華子がつられて振り返り、俺を見て飛び上がるほど驚く。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:233
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_fd0aa95d:

    # ha "Hi… Hisao?"
    ha "ひ……久夫くん？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:241
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_181f7493:

    # ha "I mean… um… hello, Hisao…"
    ha "あ、その……えっと……こんにちは、久夫くん……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:243
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_0e1c2e96:

    # hi "Hi. Sorry if I startled you."
    hi "やあ。驚かせてごめんな"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:249
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_d1d2fa32:

    # "Lilly turns to greet me, helped in her orientation by Hanako."
    "正しい方向を向くように華子に助けられながら、リリーが振り返って挨拶する。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:254
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_5be9f64a:

    # li "Good afternoon, Hisao. Are you joining us?"
    li "ごきげんよう、久夫さん。一緒にいかがですか？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:256
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_20abc6a8:

    # hi "If it's no trouble. There's not much else to do, really."
    hi "うん、もしよければ。他にすることもなくてさ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:261
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_30b8a954:

    # "Lilly gives a small nod, as if to silently brush away any idea that it would be troubling in the least."
    "迷惑なことなんて少しもないとでも言いたげに、リリーが軽くうなずく。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:271
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_b4e51361:

    # "We descend one set of stairs and walk down the hallway to the usual room, our pace somewhat quicker than usual thanks to Lilly using Hanako for direction, rather than her cane and the railings."
    "階を一つ降り、いつもの部屋へと廊下を進む。華子の助けのおかげでリリーも杖や手すりを使うより速く歩ける。そうして俺たちは普段よりも早く部屋にたどり着く。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:276
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_6813c57b:

    # "As expected, it's deserted. The sounds of the other clubs can only barely be heard as sunlight streams into the room from outside."
    "予想通り、部屋は無人だった。外から日の光が差し込み、部活動に励む声が遠くのほうからかすかに聞こえてくる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:278
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_22aef5a0:

    # "Looking around the room, I notice a couple of empty easels propped up against a wall that I don't think were there before. The art club must use this room as extra storage."
    "周りを見渡し、空のイーゼルがいくつか壁に立てかけてあるのに気づく。前に来た時はなかったはずだ。美術部も備品置き場としてここを使っているんだろう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:283
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_1e3d9a46:

    # ha "Should I get the chess set out?"
    ha "チェス盤用意したほうがいいかな？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:285
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_883ce386:

    # "Hanako's voice seems less tense when she's directly addressing Lilly."
    "リリーに直接言葉を向ける時の華子の声は普段よりも柔らかく感じる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:294
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_220d1b6b:

    # li "Yes. I'll make tea while you sort the pieces."
    li "ええ。そのあいだに私は紅茶を淹れますね"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:296
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_bf5ff7bd:

    # hi "Ah, I can do that for you, if you'd like."
    hi "あ、よかったら俺がやるよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:306
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_43276568:

    # "She ponders the offer for a moment before smiling, confirming that I've made the right choice. Her face is remarkably easy to read."
    "彼女は少しのあいだ考えてから、にっこり微笑む。それを見て俺は申し出たのは正解だったと悟る。彼女の表情はとても読み取りやすい。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:311
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_fd3e1f8e:

    # li "Very well. Thank you."
    li "そうですか。ありがとうございます"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:324
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_387bc699:

    # "She slides her retracted cane into the handle of her bag and sets it against one of the table legs, before taking a seat opposite Hanako."
    "そう言うと彼女は縮めた杖を自分のかばんの取っ手に滑りこませ、それを机の脚に立てかける。そして華子の向かいの席に座る。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:326
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_6e6173c1:

    # "As I prepare tea for the three of us, I can hear the small wooden pieces being set on the board. I wonder how good Lilly is at chess, given her circumstances."
    "木製のチェスの駒が盤上に並べられる音を聞きながら、３人分の紅茶を用意する。ああいう境遇で、リリーはどれくらいチェスが上手いんだろう、と考える。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:328
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_5b512e1f:

    # "By the time I place the steaming teacups onto the table, Lilly and Hanako have already moved their first pieces as they nibble on sandwiches and rice balls from their respective bags."
    "俺が湯気の立ち上るティーカップを机に並べるころには、リリーと華子はそれぞれのかばんから出したサンドイッチとおにぎりをほお張りながら、両者とも最初の駒を進めていた。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:341
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_39f816ad:

    # "I note that the chessboard they're using has holes in the middle of each square and pegs on the bottom of the pieces, and has each dark square slightly raised."
    "彼女たちが使うチェス盤のそれぞれのマスの中央には穴が開いていて、駒の下部にはそこにはめ込むでっぱりがある。さらに、黒いマスは少し浮かび上がっている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:343
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_e3556111:

    # "Watching Lilly's fingers skating over the board, tracing out the positions of the pieces, makes me marvel a little at the simple ingenuity of the design. It must be specifically made for blind players."
    "リリーがチェス盤の上に手を滑らせ、駒の位置を確認する。チェス盤のシンプルかつ巧妙なデザインに少し感心する。これは目の見えない人のために特別に作られたものに違いない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:354
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_22c987dc:

    # hi "Here you go."
    hi "ほら、紅茶入ったよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:363
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_9bb6ec05:

    # "Hanako gives a small nod as I put down the cup next to her side of the board. Lilly's hand ventures sideways slightly, so I gently place the cup touching the tips of her fingers; a gesture she seems to appreciate."
    "チェス盤の華子側の脇にカップを置くと、華子が小さくうなずく。リリーの手が横に少しそれたので、その指先にそっとカップを触れさせる。リリーには感謝してもらえたようだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:368
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_5348a403:

    # "I finally take a seat and silently sip my tea as the two play. The contrast in their appearances while playing is interesting to watch."
    "ようやく席に座り、２人がプレイする脇で紅茶を静かに一口飲む。彼女たちが見せるプレイ中の姿は対照的で、見ていて面白い。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:373
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_c48283bf:

    # "Hanako looks closely at the board, her face one of focused concentration. Lilly, on the other hand, keeps her head level and maintains her calm neutrality."
    "華子は盤上に顔を近づけ、それをじっと見据えながら意識を集中している。一方リリーは姿勢を崩さず、穏やかな外見を保っている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:375
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_a5388aac:

    # "Lilly's gentle voice addresses both of us as she continues to play."
    "プレイが続行するなか、リリーが俺と華子に穏やかに話しかける。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:380
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_44ae68d3:

    # li "How was class, now that the festival's over?"
    li "学園祭も終わりましたけど、クラスはどうでしたか？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:386
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_a8f4627f:

    # "I look to Hanako to see whether she'll answer first, but see that she's doing the same."
    "華子が先に答えるかどうかを探るために俺が横を見ると、華子も俺と同じことをしている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:391
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_a6531f6a:

    # hi "Not… great. Half the class seemed to be dozing off, even including the teacher. Not to mention a test on top of all that."
    hi "良くは……なかったね。クラスの半分は居眠りしてたみたいだし。先生までそんな感じ。おまけにテストもあったしさ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:396
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_3ba01a37:

    # "Hanako quietly adds her own agreement with this."
    "華子が小さな声でそれに同意する。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:401
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_c4eb83b8:

    # li "I could imagine that being a bit difficult for you, being a transfer student."
    li "それは大変でしたね。久夫さんは転校生なのだし"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:406
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_c7be8f45:

    # hi "Well, I think I did fine. Other than the shock of a test coming so early, science is probably my best subject."
    hi "まあ、なんとかなったけどな。こんなに早くテストを受けるとは思わなかったけど、科学はたぶん俺の一番得意な教科だし"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:411
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_0dbdc18c:

    # hi "How'd you do, Hanako?"
    hi "華子はどうだった？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:416
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_95edaad7:

    # ha "Me? Ah… okay… I guess…"
    ha "私？　あの……まあまあ……かな……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:418
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_fd54115d:

    # "Hanako's too sincere to be able to pull off lying very well. That much is obvious."
    "華子は嘘がつけない性格だということがよく分かる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:423
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_3ab6b265:

    # "Lilly's smile slips very slightly. From her reaction, Hanako mustn't be skilled enough at academics to do very well without preparation."
    "リリーの笑みがほんの少しだけ消える。その反応を見るに、華子は予習なしでもいい成績が取れるほど学業優秀というわけではないらしい。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:428
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_e71d46df:

    # hi "How did your class handle it, Lilly?"
    hi "リリーのクラスはどうだったんだ？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:433
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_31f90efe:

    # li "It went surprisingly well, actually. Only one student was absent, which was better than what the teacher expected."
    li "驚くくらい上出来でしたよ。先生の期待を上回って、欠席者はたったの１人でしたから"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:439
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_e7d05f59:

    # "With the topic all but run dry, the two concentrate on their chess game once again."
    "これ以上話すこともなくなり、２人はまたゲームに集中する。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:444
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_0d73c6be:

    # "I can't say I've ever liked the idea of chess as a spectator sport, but given its unique nature, for once I'm rapt in watching the game unfold."
    "チェスが観戦スポーツだと思ったことはないけど、今回に限って言えば、こんなユニークな状況のゲーム展開には俺も思わず見入ってしまう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:450
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_7863142a:

    # "As time wears on, both of them demonstrate decent skill at playing the game. Having captured two more pawns than Hanako, Lilly has the upper hand, but only slightly."
    "時間が経過し、両者とも優れたチェス技術を披露する。ポーンを華子よりも二つ多く取ったリリーのほうが優勢だけど、その差はほんのわずかだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:456
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_d8e18ae1:

    # "…until Hanako makes a strange move with her queen. Seizing upon this lapse in judgment, Lilly takes the piece with her knight."
    "……華子が彼女のクイーンをおかしな場所に指すまでは。そのミスをとらえて、リリーがナイトで華子のクイーンを取る。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:461
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_448e1fc2:

    # "Without hesitation, Hanako moves a pawn to take Lilly's rook on the opposite side of the board, and promotes it to queen."
    "すると華子はためらうことなくポーンで盤の反対側にいたリリーのルークを取り、そのポーンをクイーンに昇格させる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:467
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_a4cb861f:

    # "Lilly's face falters as her fingers move over the pieces and she realizes that she just fell to Hanako's trap. It's a little distracting to have the board traced out after each move, even if it's out of necessity."
    "指で盤上の駒をなぞったリリーが、華子の罠にはまったことに気づいてたじろいだ表情を見せる。仕方ないこととはいえ、駒を動かすたびに指で確認しないといけないのはちょっと煩わしいな。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:469
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_5e3826da:

    # "Judging by Hanako's lack of reaction, she must be used to this. She and Lilly must have played at least a few games of chess against each other, after all."
    "こうしている間もなんの反応も示さない華子は、こういうプレイ方法に慣れているに違いない。彼女とリリーはこれ以前にも少なくとも数回はチェスの対戦をしたことがあるはずだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:471
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_7764d55b:

    # ha "Check."
    ha "チェック"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:476
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_8f7327a0:

    # hi "That's not bad at all. Nice, Hanako."
    hi "すごいじゃないか。いいぞ、華子"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:481
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_e72e67fe:

    # "The compliment causes her to flower into a surprised blush."
    "褒められた彼女は驚いたようにかあっと顔を赤らめる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:483
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_f8d5e9ff:

    # ha "Th-thank you. I didn't… think it would work."
    ha "あ、ありがとう。うまくいくと……思わなかった"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:488
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_c82e3000:

    # "I look over to Lilly, her fingers having just finished tracing out the position of her remaining pieces in an attempt to extricate her king from this bind."
    "リリーを見ると、ちょうど残った駒を確認し終わったようだ。自分のキングを救い出す方法を探っていたけど。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:490
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_508dc190:

    # li "I think this is checkmate…"
    li "チェックメイトのようですね……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:495
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_34d1d59d:

    # hi "Hmm?"
    hi "え？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:500
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_fa8a56d4:

    # "I take another look at the board to confirm."
    "俺はもう一度盤上を確かめる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:502
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_df77fbab:

    # "Sure enough, her king has nowhere to escape without being threatened by another piece. My earlier question as to which of them is better at this has just been answered."
    "その言葉通り、リリーのキングはどこにも逃げ道がない。２人のうちどちらが強いか、というさっきからの俺の疑問にもこれで答えが出た。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:507
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_bbc95e02:

    # hi "So it is."
    hi "そうみたいだな"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:512
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_88394bf5:

    # "Lilly gives a small sigh as Hanako smiles. From their reactions, this seems like a fairly usual result."
    "リリーが小さくため息をつき、華子が微笑む。２人の反応を見る限り、いつもどおりといった感じだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:517
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_a787d79f:

    # hi "How long have you two been playing?"
    hi "２人はどれくらいチェスをやってたんだ？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:523
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_aaea8c8c:

    # ha "Since… I was young."
    ha "小さい……ころから"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:529
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_29cd0152:

    # "Lilly nods at Hanako's brief answer."
    "華子の短い返答を聞いてリリーがうなずく。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:534
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_a5813e3d:

    # li "Hanako taught me how to play soon after I met her. I can beat her every now and then… but that's a rarity. I don't seem to have the right mindset for it."
    li "出会ってすぐ、華ちゃんが私にチェスを教えてくれたんです。時には私が勝つこともあるけれど……めったにないですね。まだ上手な駒の動かし方を知らないのかもしれません"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:536
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_b87fcf4e:

    # "If Lilly came to Yamaku at the start of high school, and met Hanako when she moved to the dorms, that'd mean she's only been playing for about one year."
    "リリーが山久学園に入学し、その後寮に移って華子に出会ったと考えると、つまり彼女のチェス歴は一年ぽっちということか。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:538
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_ce86aded:

    # "After seeing Hanako's level of play, I'm not too surprised Lilly has trouble beating her."
    "華子のハイレベルなプレイを見た後では、リリーがなかなか彼女を倒せないのもうなずける。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:544
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_7e10977e:

    # ha "But… she's better at languages than I am, so…"
    ha "でも……リリーは私よりも話すのが上手だから……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:550
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_d58113c4:

    # "Lilly gives an appreciative, if slightly amused, smile at Hanako's quick reversal of her compliment."
    "華子が素早く褒め言葉を返すのを聞いて、リリーが少し面白がるように感謝の笑みを浮かべる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:555
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_beedabe2:

    # li "Well, that's how it is."
    li "そう、そういうものかしらね"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:560
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_66fee553:

    # "Much to everyone's surprise, the bell suddenly rings, heralding an end to the lunch break."
    "突然昼休みの終わりを告げるチャイムが鳴り、俺たちは皆びっくりする。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:566
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_7fb6e2ab:

    # li "Hmm, that game lasted longer than I thought it did."
    li "あら、思っていたよりも勝負が長くなってしまったようですね"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:568
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_9765189b:

    # hi "Same. I guess we'd better get back to class."
    hi "同感だ。教室に戻ったほうがいいな"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:575
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_a470eb89:

    # "Hanako's already in the middle of packing up, so I take Lilly's bag and offer it to her. To my surprise, she takes it and nods, but then places it back down on the table."
    "華子はすでに片づけ始めている。俺はリリーのかばんを取り彼女に渡す。彼女はうなずきながらかばんを手に取った後、なぜかテーブルの上にそれを置いてしまう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:584
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_fec6788a:

    # li "Hisao, may I make a request?"
    li "久夫さん。一つお願いしてもいいですか？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:586
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_683db8a9:

    # hi "Sure, go ahead."
    hi "ん、ああ、いいよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:591
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_7642e029:

    # li "Would you mind if I were to quickly feel your face?"
    li "あなたの顔を触らせてもらってもいいですか？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:593
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_9bd5c3d0:

    # hi "Oh, uh… no, go ahead. I don't mind."
    hi "えっ、ええと……いや、構わないよ。俺は別に"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:595
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_961b7d07:

    # "The question takes me severely off guard, but once I regain my composure it seems sensible enough. So far Lilly's had no idea what I actually look like, and this would be her only way to find out."
    "俺にとっては完全に不意を突かれた頼みだったけど、冷静に考えてみれば別におかしな頼みでもない。リリーは未だに俺の外見を全く知らない。そして、触ることがそれを知る唯一の方法なんだろう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:602
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_66cd43f4:

    # "Lilly raises her right hand, which I take in mine and guide to my face before letting go."
    "リリーがそっと右手を上げる。俺はそれを手に取ると、自分の顔へと導く。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:604
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_8cf57413:

    # "The room is entirely silent as Lilly's hand moves over and around my features, from my chin, to my cheeks, to everywhere else."
    "あごから頬へ、そして他の全ての部分へ。リリーの手が俺の顔をなぞるあいだ、部屋は静寂に包まれる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:606
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_94c228ae:

    # "I expected this to feel a lot more disquieting than it does. I suppose that's because the action is entirely a matter of practicality, being functionally no different to simply looking at someone's face."
    "顔を触られるのはもっと煩わしいものだと思っていた。きっとこれも誰かの顔を見るのと同じ、ただ実用のための行為なんだろう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:608
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_c0f48b48:

    # "Her hand is soft, but what takes me by surprise is the length of her fingers, not to mention how sure even the slightest of her movements are. I have no doubt that her level of tactile feeling would be far beyond mine."
    "彼女の手は柔らかく、指は驚くほど長くすらりとしている。その動きは、例えそれがほんのわずかであってもいつも的確だ。彼女の触覚は俺のそれよりもはるかに敏感に違いない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:610
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_af383d5e:

    # "Her hand briefly runs once through my hair before retreating. I'm sure that every inch of my face has been committed to her memory. It's only now, too, that I realize Hanako has been silently watching the entire time."
    "最後に彼女は一度だけ俺の髪を軽く撫で、それから手を引く。これで俺の顔の全てが、細かい部分まで彼女の記憶に刻まれたはずだ。この時初めて、俺は華子が一部始終を静かに見守っていたことに気づく。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:619
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_a16de6b0:

    # li "Thank you for letting me do that, Hisao."
    li "ありがとう、久夫さん"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:624
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_ccbde474:

    # li "And if I might add, I think you are quite handsome."
    li "もう一言付け加えると、久夫さん、とてもハンサムだと思います"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:626
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_71e665b0:

    # "I blush a little at her remark, before raising a questioning eyebrow."
    "彼女の言葉を聞いて俺は少し赤くなり、疑念に眉を寄せる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:628
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_abf6dfa9:

    # hi "But if you can't see, how…"
    hi "でも、見えないのに、どうやって……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:633
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_b30cc688:

    # li "Just because I can't see, that doesn't mean I don't have my own preferences."
    li "あら、見えないからといって、私に好みがないというわけではないんですよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:638
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_d6d7cf4c:

    # ha "Um, we'd better go now…"
    ha "あの、そろそろ戻ったほうが……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:640
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_7ad89f6c:

    # hi "Yeah, that's a good point. I guess we'll see you later then, Lilly."
    hi "ああ、そうだな。じゃあリリー、また今度な"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:647
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_140bb7ff:

    # "Walking through the hallways back to our classrooms, I notice that Hanako seems quieter than before, but also more comfortable."
    "廊下を歩いているあいだ、俺は華子がさっきよりも静かに、そしてリラックスしているように見える。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:649
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_ebde3ce4:

    # "Lilly, her hand on Hanako's shoulder, seems to pick up on her assured pace as well, smiling as they walk."
    "華子の肩に手を乗せているリリーも華子の力強いペースからそれを感じ取ったようで、歩きながら微笑んでいる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:651
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_7ce1a44f:

    # "If I could spend the rest of my time at Yamaku like this, I don't think it'd be so bad. All that's needed for joy are small exchanges of happiness, after all."
    "もし山久での日々がこんな毎日なら、それも悪くないな。なんといっても、ほんの少しの幸せのやりとりこそが人生の喜びには必要なんだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:658
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_0f7b578e:

    # "As I reach my desk and set my bag beside it, I realize something. Or rather, my stomach does."
    "自分の席に着いてかばんを脇にかけた時、俺はあることに気づく。いや、俺の胃袋が、だ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:660
translate jp a2_lilly_earl_grey_5abfd5b8:

    # "I was so busy with those two, I forgot to buy lunch…"
    "あの２人のことばかりに気を取られて、自分の昼飯を買い忘れていた……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:676
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_8d9b1f87:

    # "Saturday. My second most favorite day of the week."
    "土曜日。俺が一週間で二番目に好きな曜日。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:678
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_854757a7:

    # "This is almost entirely due to the fact that it is the day with the second least amount of school, with class ending at the beginning of lunch."
    "二番目に授業時間が短い曜日、学校が半日で終わる曜日だから、というのがその理由だ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:683
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_0ee4f470:

    # "I open my door confidently, myself being more than confident of being able to get enjoyment out of the fine weather and shorter class length."
    "外の素晴らしい天気と授業時間の短さをめいっぱい楽しめるだろうという自信に満たされながら、俺は自分の部屋のドアを開ける。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:691
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_80108354:

    # "I confidently stride down the hallway and down the stairs to the lobby of the male dorms."
    "そのまま自信に満ちた足取りで廊下を進み、階段を降り、男子寮のロビーまでやって来る。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:695
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_ed4b8b1e:

    # "I confidently look behind me to see whose footsteps are approaching."
    "そして自信に満ちたまま後ろを振り返る。後ろから近づく足音の主を確認するために。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:699
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_7e541872:

    # "I… lose my confidence in this day being enjoyable."
    "そして……俺は楽しい一日を過ごす自信を失う。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:712
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_23c20dee:

    # ke "Hey man. Sup?"
    ke "よう、調子どうだ？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:714
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_fd7c5948:

    # hi "Not much I guess, just looking forward to the afternoon. You?"
    hi "別に、って感じ。午後が楽しみだよ。お前は？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:719
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_f2aab39b:

    # "He wraps an arm around my slumped shoulders far too comfortably. Something's up."
    "健二が俺の沈んだ肩に馴れ馴れしく手を回す。なんだか様子がおかしい。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:724
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_6742c84e:

    # ke "Let's step outside, shall we?"
    ke "よし、出るか。な？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:726
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_1e4020df:

    # hi "I was just about to, before you stopped me."
    hi "とっくに出てたんだよ、お前に引き止められてなければ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:734
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_5b2c0dd3:

    # "He doesn't take my reaction to his theatrics well. Ignoring him, I walk outside and start down the steps."
    "芝居じみた台詞に対する俺の反応も、健二は全く意に介さない。俺は健二を無視して、寮の外に出て階段を降り始める。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:736
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_4c8bdcb9:

    # "It doesn't take too long for him to catch up with me again. I wonder if he wants money, or to rant about another conspiracy. Maybe both."
    "すぐに健二が俺に追いつく。金の相談か、それともまた新しい陰謀論を垂れ流すのか。いや、両方かもしれない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:746
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_ab218535:

    # ke "I've got a bone to pick with you."
    ke "お前にちょっと言っときたいことがある"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:748
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_417298e1:

    # hi "Uh huh."
    hi "あっそ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:750
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_e5298636:

    # ke "It's about that blonde. You know who I'm talking about."
    ke "あの金髪女のことだよ。誰のことか、分かるな？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:752
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_9f1757b2:

    # "Conspiracy it is. For a moment I contemplate feigning ignorance, but realize this will go quicker if I just let him get it all out."
    "今回は陰謀論か。健二を無視するふりをしたほうがいいかと少し考えたけど、たぶんこいつの言い分を全て吐き出させたほうが早く終わるだろう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:754
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_4654e266:

    # hi "Lilly? The one from your class?"
    hi "リリーか？　お前のクラスの？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:759
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_9a1e05c4:

    # ke "You're on first name terms with her?!"
    ke "お前、下の名前で呼んでんのか！？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:761
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_b82211ca:

    # "He looks positively shocked at this development. Did he not expect me to be able to answer?"
    "健二はこの展開に明らかにショックを受けているようだ。俺が答えられるのを期待してたんじゃなかったのか？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:766
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_c7d47272:

    # "He gathers himself and coughs into his fist. Dramatically, like everything he does."
    "健二は気を取り直すと、こぶしを作って咳ばらいをする。芝居がかってるのもいつもどおりだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:768
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_e89f5c16:

    # ke "Well, never mind that. I'm here to warn you. You know. Man to man."
    ke "ふん、まあいい。忠告しといてやる。ほら、男同士の忠告ってやつだ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:770
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_1655a9fb:

    # hi "Warn me about what? Lilly?"
    hi "何の忠告だよ？　リリーのことか？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:772
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_cee24fb6:

    # ke "Yeah. You don't know her, man."
    ke "ああ。お前はあいつを知らないんだよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:774
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_935a1c53:

    # "It's mostly true. I've only known her and Hanako for less than two weeks, and even then we've just been exchanging banal chatter about school as we while away lunch."
    "それについてはだいたい正しい。俺がリリーと華子に会ってまだ二週間足らずだ。そのあいだも俺たちはただ昼休みに学校でのつまらない出来事について雑談していたに過ぎない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:776
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_906ca4e8:

    # hi "I'm pretty sure you don't either."
    hi "お前だってそうだと思うぞ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:778
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_fe6b1d2b:

    # ke "That's not the point. You're the one spending inordinate amounts of time with her."
    ke "そんなことは問題じゃない。あいつと不自然なくらい長い時間つるんでるのはそっちの方だろうが"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:780
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_7ebd27e4:

    # "It distresses me that someone like Kenji, who's probably as far out of the loop as one could possibly get, knows about such a trivial fact as who I choose to befriend."
    "健二みたいな他人と会話なんてこれっぽっちもしなさそうな奴が、俺が誰と仲良くなるかなんてどうでもいいことを知っている。それを聞いて、俺はげんなりする。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:782
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_497bdd00:

    # "Then again… I am a transfer student, and she's not only the representative of their class, but also a tall blonde."
    "でも、待てよ……俺は転入生で、リリーはただ学級委員ってだけじゃなく、背の高い金髪少女だ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:784
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_39e95b87:

    # "Maybe I should appreciate this ranting as a warning that the rumor mill exists in this school, and that I'm firmly within it."
    "こいつの戯言も、学校内で噂が広まっていて、しかも俺がその渦のど真ん中にいるという警告としてありがたく受け取るべきなのかもしれない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:786
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_ce160a7d:

    # hi "It's just lunch. Nothing special."
    hi "一緒に昼飯食ってるだけだよ。特別なことじゃない"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:791
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_2c2e8fa2:

    # ke "Look, man, under the bridge. See this bridge? You're under it. A man's gotta do what a man's gotta do to get intel."
    ke "まああれだ、やっちまったもんはしかたない。諜報活動のためなら、ヤバい橋もわたらなきゃいけない。それが男ってもんだ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:796
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_9ff38001:

    # ke "I just want to make sure you don't end up too far under the bridge."
    ke "ただし、あまり深入りしすぎないよう気をつけるんだぞ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:798
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_e3c652d9:

    # hi "You're losing me, Kenji."
    hi "健二さ、さっぱり分かんないんだけど"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:803
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_4d1c67c2:

    # ke "That's okay, lots of people get lost. That's why I'm here to help."
    ke "いいさ、他の連中もたいてい分かってない。だから俺が助けてやるんだよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:809
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_30e89f2d:

    # ke "Just be careful around her, okay? She looks all harmless on the outside, but I've heard shit. Bad shit."
    ke "あいつには注意しろ、いいな？　あいつ、一見無害に見えるけど、俺、聞いちまったんだよ。とんでもねえ話をよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:814
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_1f47e8c4:

    # ke "You know the Student Council, right?"
    ke "生徒会のことは知ってるな？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:816
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_64c2486e:

    # "He seems to involuntarily shudder as he says the words. Putting him and Shizune together in a room is an amusing mental exercise. I wonder if they've met."
    "その言葉を口にすると、健二は思わずぶるっと身を震わせる。こいつと静音を同じ部屋に閉じこめた様子を想像するのは、愉快な頭の体操だ。２人は会ったことあるんだろうか。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:818
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_b91aa998:

    # hi "Yeah, Shizune and Misha are in my class. I seem to have dodged the draft, though."
    hi "ああ、静音とミーシャは同じクラスだからな。俺はなんとか生徒会には入れられずに済んだけど"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:823
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_531b417f:

    # ke "Good man. Good man."
    ke "よしよし、それでいい"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:828
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_9f52f646:

    # ke "But this blonde? She was there. In the Student Council. Right. Damn. There."
    ke "だが、あの金髪女はどうだ？　あいつもいたんだよ。あの生徒会によ。ど・ま・ん・な・か・に、だ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:830
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_3cff92ac:

    # hi "I see. And?"
    hi "へえ。で？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:832
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_32a5d186:

    # ke "And she's not there now."
    ke "今はいない"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:836
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_35c4f685:

    # hi "…"
    hi "……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:838
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_a614d113:

    # ke "Seriously, think about it. Something must have gone down."
    ke "マジ、考えてみろって。絶対なんかあったはずだろ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:840
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_62efd8e9:

    # "I stop walking for a moment, giving the idea more thought than I probably should."
    "俺はしばらく立ち止まり、必要以上に想像を膨らませてしまう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:842
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_4e03f33d:

    # "It would explain that fight the two had, at least in part. Wait, no, not really. Even leaving the Student Council would need a catalyst."
    "この前の２人のいがみ合いもそれで説明がつく。少なくとも部分的には。待て、いや、そうとも言い切れない。生徒会を去ったこと自体にも何か原因があるはずだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:844
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_2e3ce77d:

    # "In the end, it doesn't explain much at all. Other than the fact that their feud goes back some ways."
    "結局のところ、これだけでは２人の確執が過去にさかのぼるということ以外何も分からない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:846
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_c76d7ede:

    # hi "I guess you have a point. I'm not seeing how that really affects me, though."
    hi "そうかもな。でも、それが俺にどう影響するんだよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:851
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_a4c49570:

    # ke "Okay, now field this one. Lilly's foreign, obviously."
    ke "よし、じゃあよく聞けよ。リリーはどう見ても日本人じゃない"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:853
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_fa08f1c5:

    # hi "Obviously."
    hi "そうだな"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:855
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_9d75420e:

    # ke "Now, what nationality is she?"
    ke "なら、あいつの国籍はどこだ？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:857
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_66015df6:

    # "I open my mouth to give the answer, but realize that I have none. In fact, I've given the matter very little thought."
    "その質問に答えるために口を開こうとして、俺は答えを知らないのに気づく。実際、それについてほとんど考えたことがなかった。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:859
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_ae5582fe:

    # "Given that she has no accent and acts perfectly Japanese, I suppose it never really seemed important. Now that he mentions it though, I am rather curious."
    "全く訛りのない言葉遣いと完璧な日本人の振る舞いを披露するリリーに接していると、そんなことは大して重要じゃないように思える。だけど、今こうして健二に言われてみると少し気になってしまう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:861
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_d0453458:

    # hi "To be honest, I don't know. Maybe English? They like tea."
    hi "正直、知らないな。イギリス人か？　イギリス人って紅茶好きだし"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:863
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_9cf2fb58:

    # "I probably shouldn't resort to stereotypes, but that's the only lead I have."
    "ステレオタイプな考え方に頼るべきじゃないんだろうとは思うけど、それくらいしか手がかりがない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:870
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_08c6b6db:

    # ke "You're not thinking. Luckily, you have me here to think for you."
    ke "お前、何にも考えてねえな。代わりに考えてやる俺がいてラッキーだぞ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:872
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_b32e4395:

    # hi "Gee, thanks."
    hi "はぁ、そりゃどうも"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:874
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_580efa52:

    # "He brushes off the quip effortlessly."
    "健二が俺の皮肉をあっさり無視する。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:879
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_a739fff4:

    # ke "Now answer me this: who has lots of social power, is filthy stinking rich - you know blondes are all rich, right? - has a long history of disputes and used to belong to a much larger organization?"
    ke "よし、じゃあ答えてみろ。莫大な権力を持ってて、薄ぎたねえ金持ちで――金髪ってのはみんな金持ちなのは知ってるな？――長い抗争の歴史を持ってて、でっかい組織に属してたのはどいつだ？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:881
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_19d3f135:

    # hi "The Roman Catholic Church?"
    hi "ローマカトリック教会か？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:886
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_34b49839:

    # ke "…Well okay, there's that."
    ke "……あー、まあ、それもそうだ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:891
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_f2e9121d:

    # ke "But there's also the Mafia. Come on. Rich, foreign, there's no way she doesn't have connections to them."
    ke "だが、マフィアもそうだ。おいおい、金持ち、外人ときたら、あの金髪女がつながってないわけないだろうが"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:893
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_cffe58bf:

    # "I have reason to doubt the logic of his deductions, but he shows no sign of stopping."
    "健二の推測に使われる論理は疑わしいことこの上ないけど、やつが話をやめる気配はない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:899
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_018329ca:

    # ke "So do you know where I think she's from?"
    ke "で、あいつがどっから来たと俺が考えてるか、分かるな？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:901
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_1d960b34:

    # hi "Italy?"
    hi "イタリア？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:906
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_90f119d6:

    # ke "Mainland Italy's small-time, dude. She has to be from Sicily. All those mafioso types come from there."
    ke "イタリア本土なんかザコだよ。シチリア島に決まってる。マフィア連中はみんなあそこ出身だからな"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:911
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_376f257a:

    # ke "Wait, no, Russia. Damn, this could be bad. The Mafia there is serious business, man; Ex-KGB everywhere, paramilitaries, hardcore smuggling, and—"
    ke "いや待て、違うな、ロシアだ。くそっ、最悪だ。あそこのマフィアはマジもんだぜ。元KGBだらけだろ、私兵に、筋金入った密輸に、それから何だ？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:913
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_b4761584:

    # hi "Wait, wait, stop, just slow down a sec. What point are you trying to get at here?"
    hi "待て待て、ストップ、ちょっと落ち着けって。お前、結局何が言いたいんだよ？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:918
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_8933072f:

    # ke "You don't know what she'll do, man. I won't get in your way - agents don't operate like that - but I just want you to be careful."
    ke "あいつが何するか分かんねえってことだよ。お前の邪魔はしねえよ――そんなのはエージェントのやり方じゃない――ただ、気を付けろってこった"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:923
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_7e2d3032:

    # ke "When the time comes, we'll need all the help we can get. I don't want to lose you, comrade."
    ke "いずれ時が来たら、俺たちはあらゆる手助けが必要になるんだ。お前を失いたくはないんだよ、同志"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:925
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_03335320:

    # "Well, at least he's concerned for me. Kinda."
    "まあ、少なくともこいつは俺の身を案じてくれているんだろう。それなりに。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:932
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_ae2db81a:

    # "I wave goodbye to him as we separate out to our respective classes, but I'm not sure that he sees the gesture."
    "別れてそれぞれの教室に入っていく時に、俺は健二に向かって手を振る。奴にそれが見えるのかどうか分からないけど。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:939
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_5b1c983d:

    # "Piling my books into my bag, I catch a glimpse of the library books I'd borrowed last week. I might as well return them, considering they took all of two days to finish."
    "本をかばんの中に詰め込みながら、先週図書室で借りた数冊の本にちらりと目をやる。全部読むのにまる二日かかったこの本、返しに行った方がいいな。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:941
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_32f14797:

    # "I briefly consider inviting Hanako along to the library, but she's already gone. It'll probably be better for my studying if I'm alone anyway."
    "華子も誘おうかと少し考えるけど、もう教室にいない。まあ、一人の方が勉強もはかどるだろう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:943
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_86aa5e35:

    # "With a quick stretch and a wave to a couple of classmates who give the same to me, I make my way out of the classroom."
    "クラスメイト数人と手を振り合ってお互いに別れを告げた後、俺は教室を出る。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:950
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_fc51f162:

    # "As I open my bag and shove the books through the returns slot in the front counter, I notice a strange person behind the desk. Old and graying, she must be Yuuko's replacement when she's working at the café."
    "かばんを開けカウンターの返却口に本を突っ込む時、俺は向こう側にいる奇妙な人物に気づく。高齢で白髪の女性だ。優子さんが喫茶店で働いているあいだの代理だろう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:952
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_ebd7dbd7:

    # "I begin looking for a free table, a task made somewhat difficult considering that, despite there not being many students in here, they're all sitting at their own tables."
    "空いた机を探し始めるけど、見つけるのは難しそうだ。それほど生徒がいるわけじゃないにしても、彼らはみんな各自の机を確保してしまっている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:954
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_ae912e20:

    # "Noticing a familiar head of hair, I walk over to one near the Braille section."
    "その時、見慣れた髪を持つ人物に気づき、俺は点字本コーナー近くの机に歩み寄る。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:959
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_7f42075f:

    # "It's hard to tell whether Lilly's concentrating hard or not, her placid expression holding perfectly still as her finger slides across the dot-filled pages of her book."
    "リリーは落ち着き払った様子のまま、点がいっぱいのページの上に指を滑らせている。彼女が読書に集中しているのかどうか、俺にはよく分からない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:961
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_65430f73:

    # hi "Hi. Mind if I sit here?"
    hi "やあ、ここ、座っていいかな？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:966
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_12a516df:

    # li "Hmm? Oh, no problem at all…"
    li "えっ？　ああ、もちろんですよ……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:968
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_16ad4f08:

    # "She trails off, evidently still focused on her business at hand."
    "手元の本に意識が集中したままのようで、リリーの言葉はだんだん尻すぼみになる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:975
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_a27535b0:

    # li "Ah, Hisao."
    li "あら、久夫さん"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:980
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_255aaa14:

    # "She gives a nod of greeting as I sit opposite her at the table, pluck a chemistry textbook out of my bag and quickly thumb to the chapter we're covering in class."
    "俺が反対側の席に座るあいだ、リリーが会釈する。俺は化学の教科書をかばんから引き出すとそれを素早くめくり、今授業で習っている部分を開く。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:982
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_f323f6d4:

    # "For a while, we sit there and read, each in our own way."
    "しばらくのあいだ、俺たちは座った場所でそれぞれのやり方で読書にいそしむ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:984
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_40903c14:

    # "Seeing her reminds me of what Kenji said this morning, though. That and the fact that I've never seen someone read in Braille before makes me keep throwing glances at her."
    "だけど、リリーを見て今朝の健二の言葉が脳裏をよぎる。そのことと、点字を読む人を見たことがないという事実のせいで、俺は彼女をちらちら見ずにはいられない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:986
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_4fe62599:

    # "I kind of feel guilty about it, given that she has no way to realize I'm doing so, so I decide to just ask her about it. Her lineage isn't exactly a state secret, after all, and there is another thing I've only just noticed from her movements."
    "リリーはそれに気づく術がない。そのことに罪悪感を感じた俺は、彼女に直接質問を投げかけることにする。実際、血筋のことは別に機密事項というわけでもない。それに、彼女の動きを見ていて気づいたこともある。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:988
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_30976bb3:

    # hi "Hey Lilly, mind if I ask a question?"
    hi "あのさ、リリー。ちょっと聞いてもいいかな？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:993
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_2f8227c6:

    # li "Not at all. Is anything wrong?"
    li "ええ、いいですよ。どうかしましたか？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:995
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_473e3592:

    # hi "I was just wondering… you're at least part foreign, right?"
    hi "リリーって……少なくともハーフとかクォーターなのかなあ、って。違う？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1000
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_c42b6b2d:

    # "She gives a small giggle before setting down her book."
    "彼女はくすりと笑うと、本を机に置く。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1005
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_d55f46a4:

    # li "I've always been amused at how squeamish people are about that. Akira's mentioned how much she and I look different from most others before."
    li "私からすれば、皆さんがそのことで神経質になるのがいつも面白いんですよ。姉さんも、私や姉さんの見た目は他の人たちととても違って見えると言っていました"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1010
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_065ffe05:

    # li "The details are a bit complicated, but I'm half Japanese, half Scottish."
    li "詳細は少し込み入っていますが、私は日本人とスコットランド人のハーフなんです"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1012
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_4d31e17e:

    # "…Scottish? That was not exactly my first guess. It takes some effort to not blurt it out loud."
    "……スコットランド？　明らかに俺の最初の予想と違う。それをうっかり言いかけて、慌てて口をつぐむ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1014
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_7c132b43:

    # "I try to conjure images of the place in my mind. I think as far as the UK goes, Scotland isn't bad to live in… but I'm not really sure."
    "それがどこにあるのか、記憶を呼び起こしてみる。イギリスって意味では、スコットランドも悪い所じゃない……のかなあ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1016
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_26bd030e:

    # "My first guess of England was surprisingly close, at least geographically. That does leave another question though."
    "まあ、イギリスという俺の最初の予想は、少なくとも地理的には驚くほど近かったわけだ。だけど、同時に別の疑問が湧いてくる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1018
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_c1289fe0:

    # hi "But you have no accent…?"
    hi "でも、全然訛ってないけど……？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1023
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_3b17bf36:

    # li "That's where the details begin. I was born and raised in Japan, despite my mother being foreign."
    li "そこが込み入っているところですね。母は外国人ですが、私は日本で生まれ育ったので"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1025
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_f27a2235:

    # hi "Ah, I get it."
    hi "ああ、なるほど"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1027
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_a4bba82a:

    # "Hold on, if she moved to the dorms simply due to Akira working longer hours…"
    "待てよ、もし晃さんの仕事が忙しくなったという理由でリリーが寮に移ってきたのなら……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1029
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_bec2b1ea:

    # hi "So they don't live near the school?"
    hi "じゃあ、家族の人は学校のそばで住んでるってわけじゃないの？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1034
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_a49e7c20:

    # "She gives a small sigh, as if she didn't expect me to go any deeper. Was her previous frankness just a front?"
    "リリーが小さくため息をつく。俺がこんなに突っ込んだ質問をするとは思っていなかったようだ。さっきの彼女の気さくさはただの飾りだったんだろうか？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1036
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_6a55a5c8:

    # li "Not… exactly. It's been a long time since we've actually met."
    li "いいえ……実際は、もう長いあいだ会っていません"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1038
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_06c3f775:

    # "I feel like I'm not getting the whole story, but I don't really want to go unduly prying into her situation. Her about-face shows she feels kind of awkward about it."
    "話の全体はまだ見えてこないけど、リリーの境遇についてこれ以上図々しく詮索したくはない。彼女の態度が急に変わったのは、この話題が気まずいと感じているということだろう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1040
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_61be3ec3:

    # hi "So… do you speak much English? To be honest I don't know that much about Scotland, but at least I know that's the main language there."
    hi "じゃあ……英語も話せるんだ？　正直言ってスコットランドのことはあまりよく知らないんだけど、そこの公用語だってことは知ってるよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1042
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_44cff7db:

    # "It takes her a moment to collect herself, appreciating the change in topic."
    "話題が変わったおかげでリリーも落ち着きを取り戻す時間を得たようだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1047
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_d08a062a:

    # li "That's right. My family mostly used Japanese around the house when I was young, but they made sure Akira and I knew our Scottish side just as well."
    li "ええ、そうです。私が小さいころは家族も家の周りでほとんど日本語を使っていましたが、同時に姉さんと私にスコットランド人としての教育を施すことも怠りませんでした"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1052
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_03730284:

    # li "I'm fluent in the language, but I'm also studying it in school. To keep my skills up and to have the qualifications on paper, mainly."
    li "英語を流暢に話すことはできますが、学校でも勉強しています。主に語学力を保つため、それからちゃんとした資格を得るために"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1054
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_d251289a:

    # hi "So you're bilingual? That's pretty impressive."
    hi "じゃあ、バイリンガルなの？　すごいな"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1059
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_d1a24460:

    # li "I wouldn't go that far. Having parents who can speak the language is a large advantage, and English books in Braille aren't too hard to buy or import. With Yuuko's help, at least."
    li "そこまではいきませんが、両親が英語を話せるというのは大きな利点でしょうね。点字の洋書も入手は難しくありませんし。少なくとも優子さんに助けてもらえればの話ですが"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1064
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_500d4233:

    # li "There's a relatively high demand for local English teachers here anyway, which also helps give me some motivation to learn it well."
    li "なにより、ここでの英語教師の需要が比較的高いことも学習のモチベーションを得る助けになりますしね"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1066
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_3c588ed9:

    # "Demand for English teachers? For a moment, I wonder why she brought this up."
    "英語教師の需要？　なぜそんなことを言い出したんだろう。俺はしばらく考え込む。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1068
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_75e2055d:

    # hi "You're planning to be an English teacher?"
    hi "つまり、英語教師になりたいってこと？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1073
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_63803f95:

    # "She gives an enthusiastic nod."
    "リリーが力強くうなずく。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1075
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_ca6b3e38:

    # "It must be nice, having such a definite future in mind. I've never really given much thought to mine, so I'm kind of envious."
    "はっきりした将来の目標を持つのは素晴らしいことに違いない。今まで自分の将来について真剣に考えたことは一度もないので、少しうらやましい気持ちになる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1077
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_a4df7806:

    # hi "Hmm…"
    hi "ふうん……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1082
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_132986ee:

    # li "What's wrong?"
    li "どうしたんです？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1084
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_4294f020:

    # hi "It's just… I could see you as a teacher pretty easily. It suits you."
    hi "いや……教師のリリーって簡単に想像できるよ。似合ってる"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1089
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_0611dff9:

    # "For a moment, she's speechless. She lowers her face a little and lets out a nervous giggle, something I've never seen her do before."
    "リリーがしばらく無言になる。ほんの少しうつむき、苦笑にも似た笑みをもらす。こんな彼女を見るのは初めてだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1091
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_e9ed0225:

    # "With Lilly's role as a class representative and her dependable nature, teaching does seem to be a line of work fitting her personality."
    "リリーの学級委員としての立場と信頼できる人柄を考えると、教職というのは確かに彼女の人格に合った職業のように思える。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1093
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_97422389:

    # hi "Sorry, that was probably a little much. It is true, though."
    hi "ごめん、ちょっと言い過ぎた。でも本当だよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1098
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_40d53304:

    # "Waving her hand in front of her face dismissively, she quickly recovers."
    "リリーが俺の言うことを打ち消すかのように自分の顔の前で手を振り、すぐに元の表情に戻る。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1100
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_cfd565df:

    # li "It's not that, it's just that… only one person's ever said that to me before."
    li "いえ、そうではなくて……同じことを言ってくれた人は過去に一人だけでしたので"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1104
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_b0443108:

    # "A short, somewhat awkward silence follows the discussion. Without knowing it, I ended up steering into a troublesome topic again."
    "短い、気まずい感じの沈黙が後に残る。気づかないうちに、また面倒な話題に首を突っ込んでしまったようだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1106
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_69b2c9c1:

    # "I should try to cheer her up a little. It was me who went and got her brooding, after all."
    "リリーを少し元気づけてあげないと。彼女が胸の内を明かすように仕向けたのはこっちなんだし。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1108
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_f336e180:

    # hi "Want to go grab lunch at the cafeteria after this?"
    hi "この後食堂で昼食でもどう？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1110
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_6f9f70d2:

    # "It might perk her up a bit, or at least take her mind off her apparently complicated family situation."
    "これで少しリリーが元気を取り戻すかもしれない。少なくとも複雑そうな家庭環境のことから彼女の気を紛らわせることができるんじゃないか。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1115
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_4e8be329:

    # "Going by her smile, it seems to have the intended effect."
    "彼女の笑顔を見る限り、狙いどおりの効果を得ているようだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1120
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_9b3c543d:

    # li "I appreciate the thought, but the food there…"
    li "誘ってもらえるのは嬉しいのですが、あそこの食べ物は……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1122
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_0da1cb4b:

    # "Quite a quick redirection of the conversation. She does have a point though - the food there isn't the greatest."
    "あっという間に話の流れが変わってしまう。だけど、リリーの言うとおりだ――あそこの飯はあまりうまくない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1124
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_16e5fc78:

    # hi "Maybe the Shanghai? We could ask Hanako if she wants to come as well."
    hi "上海なんかどう？　華子も来るかどうか聞いてみるか"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1129
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_948ec9ba:

    # li "Ah…"
    li "あ……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1131
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_46b9decc:

    # hi "What is it?"
    hi "どうした？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1136
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_495ff28d:

    # li "I almost forgot, until you reminded me. Hanako's birthday is coming up soon, and I was going to go shopping in the city for a present tomorrow."
    li "久夫さんに言われなかったら忘れてしまうところでした。もうすぐ華ちゃんのお誕生日なので、明日プレゼントを買いに街に行こうと思っていたんです"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1138
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_6773633a:

    # hi "If that's an invitation, I'd be happy to accompany you."
    hi "もしお誘いなら、喜んで。一緒に行くよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1140
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_03131f0d:

    # "The ability to get more used to the layout of the city would probably be a good thing. I have barely set foot in there, so I'd be hopelessly lost by myself."
    "ここの市街のつくりに慣れておくのはたぶんいいことだ。ほとんど行ったことがないので、一人なら絶望的に迷ってしまうだろう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1145
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_a816f2f5:

    # "She gives a nod, signaling that she happily approves of this plan for Sunday."
    "この日曜日の計画に満足したかのように、リリーがうなずく。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1147
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_c4cafb8b:

    # "We eventually get back to our books, though before I begin reading again I steal one last glance at her."
    "そして俺たちはまた読書に戻る。その直前に、俺はもう一度だけちらっとリリーを見たけど。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1149
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_4ea8d959:

    # "Maybe I've been thinking on my situation too much. After all, everybody here would have their own unique circumstances."
    "たぶん俺は自分の境遇について考え過ぎていたんだろう。ここにいる誰もが、それぞれ違った特別な境遇にいるんだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1151
translate jp a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_525f58b2:

    # "The chance to get outside and clear my head will probably do me good."
    "外出して頭をすっきりさせるのは、俺にとっていい気分転換になるだろう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1169
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_c1efd181:

    # "Bored of standing in place and watching the television in a shop window, I pull myself away from the tacky display with little effort."
    "店頭の窓際に置かれたテレビを突っ立ったまま観るのにも飽きて、たいした苦労もせずその場から離れる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1171
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_4bb26bac:

    # "After living at Yamaku, the city seems like an entirely different world."
    "山久に来てからというもの、街の光景は全く別世界のように感じる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1173
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_8e4f2929:

    # "No running in the halls. Calm and orderly conduct is to be used at all times in the classrooms. Students are to exit rooms after checking both directions for oncomers. Elevators are reserved for movement-impaired students. Single file on stairs."
    "廊下を走らない。教室では常に穏やかに節度をもって過ごすこと。部屋を出るときは人とぶつからないように左右を確認する。エレベーターは動作障害を持つ生徒専用。階段は一列に並んで昇り降りすること。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1175
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_fedcaa36:

    # "Compared to such strict, almost regimental, standards, the city's shopping arcade might as well be a strange country."
    "こんな軍規ともいえるような厳格な基準に比べたら、商店街は外国も同然だろう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1177
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_f53092f8:

    # "While the school may have its fair share of hustle and bustle during the festival, the outside world is much different."
    "学校だって学園祭の時は少しは羽目を外したりもするけど、やっぱり外の世界はあそことは全然違う。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1179
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_2b8845d1:

    # "It's strange. Having lived in a metropolitan city before my accident, this should feel more natural than Yamaku and the surrounding town ever could."
    "変な気分だ。倒れる前は大都会に住んでいたので、俺にとってここは山久やその周辺よりも自然な場所に感じるはずなのに。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1181
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_4fa5ae83:

    # "Yet it feels foreign, somehow. The elevated walkways and tall buildings, each adorned with billboards taller than any three people, don't do anything to distract me from the passing crowd's reactions."
    "それでも、自分が浮いている気がしてしまう。高架の遊歩道や人３人分よりも高い看板で飾り立てられた高層ビルも、すれ違う群集の反応から俺の注意をそらすことはできない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1194
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_979fa55c:

    # "Lilly keeps one hand on my shoulder, the other holding her cane which taps the ground with a metronome-like steadiness. Looking over to her, that neutral smile of hers still holds."
    "リリーは俺の肩に片手を乗せたまま、もう片方の手で杖を持ち、それをメトロノームのように規則正しく動かしながら地面を突いている。振り返ると、彼女は相変わらず当たり障りのない微笑を浮かべ続けている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1196
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_b88c98b4:

    # "Having only seen her in school uniform, I'd not have recognized her as she sat on a bench waiting for me to come, if not for her cane propped up against it and her distinctive hair."
    "制服姿のリリーしか見たことがなかったので、もしベンチに立てかけられた杖と彼女の特徴的な髪がなかったら、俺は危うくそこに座り俺を待つ彼女に気づかないところだった。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1198
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_00b448d9:

    # "I can't tell whether they're glancing at her due to her height, her foreign looks, her obvious blindness, or all three. Not that any of those would make the situation any less uncomfortable than it is."
    "人々がリリーをちらちら見るのは、彼女の背の高さのためか、外国人風の外見のためか、それとも目が見えない様子のためか。その全てかもしれない。どういう理由であっても居心地悪く感じることに変わりはない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1203
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_c4bed76b:

    # li "Do you have any ideas of where to look first, Hisao?"
    li "久夫さん、どこから見て回りましょうか？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1205
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_a97c4d21:

    # "Her soft voice breaks me out of my line of thought."
    "リリーの柔らかい声がそんな俺の思考を吹き飛ばす。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1207
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_2ea19df6:

    # "I can't imagine that she's failing to notice the attention she garners, but she seems unfazed by it. I get the feeling she's the type to enjoy walking outside, so she might be used to it by now."
    "人々の注意を引いているということをリリーが知らないとは思えないけど、本人はそれを気に留める様子もない。彼女は外出好きなタイプみたいだから、今ではこういう状況にも慣れてしまっているのかもしれない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1209
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_d3a97790:

    # hi "Not really. This is my first time in this city, so I've got no idea of where to go."
    hi "うーん。ここに来たのは初めてだから、どこに行けばいいのかよく分からないな"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1214
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_21706370:

    # "She furrows her brow in thought, planning a route for us to take. And, come to think of it, a way to communicate it."
    "リリーは眉間にしわを寄せ、俺たちがたどるべき道筋を思案する。というか、それを説明する方法を考えている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1216
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_365b889d:

    # "Something I'd noticed in the time I've been with her is how, when deep in thought, she lacks close to any form of body language to show it."
    "リリーと一緒にいて気づいたけど、彼女は深く考え込むとほとんど身振り手振りを使わなくなる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1218
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_d28aa5b0:

    # "Her expression may change, but not a hint of movement shows. She seems to have little in the way of sweeping physical gestures in general though, so I've assumed it's part of her reserved nature."
    "表情は変わるかもしれないけど、ぴくりとも動かない。ただ、リリーが普段からジェスチャーをほとんど使わないらしいことを考えると、これは一部には彼女の控えめな性格から来ているのかもしれない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1223
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_2c6c3bfa:

    # li "Is there a large electronics store near here?"
    li "この近くに大きな電器屋さんはありますか？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1225
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_aa267599:

    # "I take a quick look around, mostly finding clothing stores. After a few seconds I notice a store with a bright blue sign some distance away that fits her description."
    "軽く周りを見回すと、目に入るのは洋服屋ばかりだ。それでもすぐに、俺はリリーの描写に当てはまりそうな青く光る看板をかかげる店が少し離れたところにあるのを見つける。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1227
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_71676974:

    # hi "Yep, it's just a bit ahead of us. Should we go in that direction?"
    hi "ああ、ちょうどすぐそこにあるよ。そっちに行ってみようか？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1232
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_d9feda33:

    # "Thankfully, it's just the information she needed. With a nod we start off and head towards Lilly's unknown destination, landmarks being our guide."
    "幸いそれがリリーにとって必要な情報だったようだ。彼女がうなずき、俺たちはその店を目印に、まだ見ぬリリーの目指す場所へと歩き出す。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1241
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_d1aa582d:

    # "Storeowner" "Here you go. One vanilla, one chocolate."
    "店主" "どうぞ。バニラ一つ、チョコレート一つですね"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1246
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_1329f005:

    # "I hand the money over the counter and take the cones to the railing that Lilly's sitting on."
    "カウンター越しに代金を渡すと、俺はアイスを持って遊歩道の手すりに腰掛けるリリーの元へ戻る。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1248
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_0962595b:

    # "I can't believe I let her trick me like this. She not only led me to an ice cream stall, but also got me to buy her some. At least she gave me the money for hers."
    "リリーにこんなお茶目なことをされるとは思わなかった。アイス屋台に俺を連れて来ただけじゃなく、俺にアイスを買うようにせがんだりして。まあ、少なくとも彼女の分のアイス代は渡してくれたけど。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1254
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_b79c4c20:

    # "Sure enough, she's patiently waiting where I'd left her. I guess she was planning on making the day an event, rather than a simple shopping trip."
    "案の定、リリーは俺が残してきた場所で辛抱強く俺を待っている。たぶん彼女は今日の外出をただの買い出し以上の出来事にすべく計画を練っていたのかもしれない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1261
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_b2d132e5:

    # "I call out to her and slowly place the vanilla cone in her outstretched hands, being careful to make sure she has a good hold of it before letting go."
    "俺はリリーに声を掛けると、彼女の伸ばす手の中にゆっくりとバニラアイスを持っていき、彼女がそれをしっかりと握るのを確認してから、手を離す。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1263
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_87ed4b3d:

    # "At least her tastes are fairly normal. I was worried she'd ask for some weird flavor when she first asked."
    "少なくともリリーの味覚は正常だってことだ。アイスをせがまれた時、変な味のアイスを頼まれるんじゃないかと心配したけど。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1265
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_810283a7:

    # hi "Here's the change."
    hi "はい、お釣り"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1270
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_c61d7352:

    # li "It's okay, keep it."
    li "いいですよ。お釣りは取っておいてください"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1272
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_caf683e7:

    # "I move to protest, but realize the futility of doing so over such a small amount. I slip the coin into my pocket, supplementing my meager allowance ever so slightly."
    "断ろうとするけど、こんな少額のために彼女に逆らうのも無益だと思い直す。俺はその小銭をポケットに滑り込ませて、自分の乏しい小遣いのささやかな足しにする。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1277
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_526919b4:

    # "Lilly shows no signs of wanting to get up, so I take a seat beside her and start eating my own ice cream."
    "リリーが立ち上がる様子もないので、俺は彼女の隣に座り、アイスを食べ始める。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1279
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_033c98a9:

    # hi "The summer weather's nice. Hopefully it will hold out for a while."
    hi "夏の天気っていいよな。しばらく続くといいけど"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1284
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_69ed5824:

    # li "You too? I'm beginning to think I'm the only person who prefers winter."
    li "久夫さんもそう思います？　なんだか冬が好きなのは私だけのような気がしてきました"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1286
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_dd0d7d0d:

    # "I contemplate her statement for a long moment."
    "俺は彼女の言葉を聞いてしばらく考え込む。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1288
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_38642f8f:

    # hi "Yeah, I think you might be."
    hi "まあ、そうかもしれないな"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1293
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_df61433e:

    # "It draws the intended reaction. She's cute when she's pouting."
    "その言葉でリリーが狙い通りの反応をする。膨れっ面の彼女ってかわいいな。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1295
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_a3f778a6:

    # hi "Still, I can't really imagine what's so good about winter. You can't go out without bundling up, and you still freeze anyway."
    hi "だって、冬ってあまりいいことないだろ。着込まなきゃいけないし、それでもまだ寒いし"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1300
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_63a8ccae:

    # li "I used to live further north, where there'd be plenty of snow to play in, so it's a little nostalgic. I don't like the heat very much, either."
    li "北国に住んでよく雪遊びをしていたので、私は冬に少しノスタルジーを感じます。暑さも苦手ですしね"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1302
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_3403858c:

    # hi "At least you can wear a skirt, so don't complain about that."
    hi "少なくともスカートははけるじゃないか。それには文句言うなよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1307
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_ba45acbb:

    # "She gives an amused giggle as we both get back to finishing off our already melting cones."
    "彼女がくすくすとおかしそうに笑う。俺たちはすでに溶け始めている残りのアイスをまた食べ始める。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1315
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_ff9fdc73:

    # "I idly sit and watch the crowds going by as we eat, catching bits and pieces of conversation."
    "ぼんやり座って食べながら、行き交う群衆を眺める。人々の会話が断片的に聞こえてくる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1321
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_30d4abd2:

    # "Looking to Lilly, I see her dutifully licking her ice cream from the top downwards, blissfully unaware of the fact that it's beginning to melt."
    "リリーを見ると、律儀にアイスを上の方からなめていて、自分のアイスが溶け始めていることには全く気づいていない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1323
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_d6a9b8ce:

    # hi "It's melting."
    hi "アイス、溶けてるよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1328
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_f34e9e20:

    # li "Where?"
    li "えっ、どこですか？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1330
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_2c9d1540:

    # hi "Um… down a bit?"
    hi "ええと……ちょっと下のほうかな？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1335
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_bf8f3356:

    # "She lowers her mouth from the top of the cone, but has no idea of exactly where the ice cream's dripping. What follows is a game of guiding her left and right until she finally finds it."
    "リリーが自分の口を上から下のほうへと持っていくけど、どこでアイスがたれているのか見つけられない。そこから先は俺が彼女を左右にガイドするゲームみたいになって、やがてついにその場所を探し当てる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1337
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_363e7b0a:

    # "To any onlooker, it must seem absolutely bizarre - a girl with her eyes closed turning her cone over and over as the guy next to her gives instructions. A strange variant of childhood blindfold games, maybe."
    "はたから見れば異様な光景に違いない。目をつぶってアイスを何度も回している少女と、隣で少女に指示を出している男。ガキの頃にやった目隠しゲームの変化形みたいなものかもな。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1342
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_ec466669:

    # "In good time we finally finish our treats, and while away the time conversing casually."
    "長いあいだかかって俺とリリーはようやくアイスを食べ終わり、しばらく軽いおしゃべりの時間を過ごす。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1349
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_00604461:

    # "Caught mid-sentence, Lilly perks her head in her trademark manner. It's an unmistakable sign that something's caught her attention."
    "話している最中、リリーがいつもの調子ではっと頭を上げる。明らかに何かに注意を向けている様子だ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1354
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_948ec9ba:

    # li "Ah…"
    li "あ……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1356
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_46b9decc:

    # hi "What is it?"
    hi "どうした？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1361
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_70f4b98f:

    # li "Is Akira somewhere over there? I think I heard her."
    li "あの辺りに姉さんがいないでしょうか？　声が聞こえたような気がして"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1369
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_9f03fd14:

    # "I raise an eyebrow as I look in the direction she's facing, somewhat doubtful of her ability to pick out Akira's lone voice in the din."
    "驚いて、リリーが顔を向けるほうへと目を凝らす。でもこんな騒音の中で本当に晃さんの声を聞き分けられるのか、少し疑問に思う。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1376
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_71dd79a9:

    # "Sure enough though, a blonde girl in a suit can be seen through the tiny gaps between people walking every which way."
    "だけどリリーの言うとおり、縦横無尽に行き交う人々のほんの少しの隙間からスーツを着た金髪女性の姿が見える。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1378
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_9c0e287b:

    # "I raise a hand and wave, trying to catch her attention."
    "俺は彼女がこちらに気づくように手を大きく振る。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1380
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_2a330b55:

    # hi "Satou! Hey, Satou!"
    hi "砂藤さん！　おーい、砂藤さーん！"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1385
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_8868f7ef:

    # "She stops in her tracks and looks towards me, evidently noticing my calls. As she does, I notice someone walking beside her."
    "晃さんは俺の呼ぶ声に気づいた様子で、立ち止まって俺の方を見る。その時、俺は晃さんが誰かと一緒にいるのに気づく。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1387
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_868733cc:

    # "I can't get a good look at whoever it is though, before the two begin walking towards where we are."
    "だけど、ここからじゃよく見えない。そうこうするうちに、２人が俺とリリーのいる場所に向かって歩き出す。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1410
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_97418ca5:

    # "As they reach us, Lilly and I stand and dust ourselves off."
    "２人がそばに来たので、リリーと俺は立ち上がってほこりを払う。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1415
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_ea4a144e:

    # li "Akira?"
    li "姉さん？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1423
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_f4af1f4c:

    # aki "Hey, you two."
    aki "よう、２人とも"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1436
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_23d32919:

    # "She nods towards me, a gesture which I quickly return. My gaze shifts towards the young girl next to her, and our eyes meet. As they do, Akira plops a hand onto her head, a move which doesn't seem to faze her."
    "晃さんが俺に向かって会釈をし、俺もすぐに会釈を返す。隣にいる女の子に視線を移すと、ちょうど彼女と目が合ってしまう。その時、晃さんが女の子の頭にぽんと手を乗せる。女の子がそれに驚く様子はない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1441
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_2dbd862a:

    # hh "I don't believe we've met. I'm Hideaki. Pleased to meet you, Hisao."
    hh "会ったことはなかったよね。僕は秀明。初めまして、久夫さん"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1443
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_bb81baab:

    # "A guy's name, huh? Guess I just dodged a bullet there. He bows, somewhat restrained by Akira's hand being on his head."
    "男の名前、だよな？　危ない所だったな。秀明くんは晃さんの手に強制されるかのように俺にお辞儀している。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1449
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_57c9bbcf:

    # li "Oh, Hideaki's here too? Are you well?"
    li "あら、秀明くんもいるの？　お元気？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1454
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_b9e8a699:

    # hh "Akira's been taking very good care of me, thank you."
    hh "晃さんがしっかり面倒見てくれてるよ。おかげさまでね"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1460
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_5612a85c:

    # "Akira grins as if to affirm the point and rubs his head hard, dragging it around in a circular motion. His dreary face during this is somewhat amusing."
    "晃さんがそれに同意するかのようにニヤニヤしながら秀明くんの頭を強く撫で、彼の頭がそれに合わせてぐりぐりと回る。秀明くんのふてくされた表情がなんだか面白い。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1465
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_17944aa9:

    # aki "Uncle's out on business again, so I'm just taking him around town for today."
    aki "おじさんがまた出張でいないからさ、今日は秀明と街をぶらついてるんだ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1470
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_9115b3a5:

    # aki "I'd have preferred to be spending the day on a date with my boyfriend, but…"
    aki "あたしは彼氏とデートして過ごしたかったんだけどね……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1475
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_7eb444c6:

    # "Hideaki gives a cough to try and redirect Akira's thoughts."
    "秀明くんが咳払いをして晃さんの考えをそらそうとしている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1477
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_f903fd68:

    # "As he does so, though, I find mine wandering. They're related? And further, as first cousins? I suppose that explains why she's taking care of him in any case."
    "だけど、秀明くんがそうしているあいだ、俺は考えを巡らせる。２人は親戚同士か？　いや、正確に言えば従姉弟ということか？　まあ、それが晃さんが秀明くんの面倒を見ている理由だろう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1479
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_f592f1e0:

    # hi "Come to think of it, Hideaki, how did you know my name?"
    hi "そういやさ、秀明くん。なんで俺の名前知ってるの？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1484
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_4b6ca4f9:

    # hh "Akira told me. Being a Yamaku student, I suppose you're disabled in some way?"
    hh "晃さんが教えてくれたんだよ。山久の生徒ってことは、久夫さんも何か障害持ってるの？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1486
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_e8149f66:

    # hi "Not everyone in Yamaku's disabled…"
    hi "あそこに通ってるのが全員障害者ってわけじゃないよ……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1488
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_ae3d5159:

    # "Which I only learned a handful of days ago. I give silent thanks to Shizune and Misha for their stream of information about how the school works."
    "これは俺も最近まで知らなかったことだ。絶えず俺に学校関連の情報を流し続ける静音とミーシャに心の中で感謝する。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1490
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_ff90943f:

    # "Because of them, I found out that since the school will accept practically anybody suffering from non-mental disabilities, it doesn't discriminate against healthy people either."
    "２人のおかげで、俺はこの学校が知的障害者以外なら事実上誰でも受け入れていることを知った。障害者と同じように、健康な人間も差別しないのだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1492
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_708b12c8:

    # "It seems unlikely that many in good health would enroll there though. While the standard of education is pretty high, it's extremely isolated and very much focused on helping disabled students."
    "もっとも、健康な人間がたくさんこの学校に来るとはとても思えないけど。教育水準はかなり高いにしても、こんなへんぴな所にあるし、障害を持つ生徒の補助を重視している学校だし。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1497
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_30739bd7:

    # hh "You're dodging the question."
    hh "質問をはぐらかさないでよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1499
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_0ba98048:

    # "Damn, he's sharp."
    "くそっ、鋭いな。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1501
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_1b306030:

    # "Before I can say another word though, he decides to take a stab at it himself."
    "だけど、俺が返事をする前に、秀明くんは自分で答えを探ることにしたようだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1506
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_335e01ef:

    # hh "If I were to call it myself… your heart?"
    hh "僕が考えるに……心臓かな？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1515
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_9dbffc8e:

    # "Akira looks mildly curiously at me, her interest piqued as well. That sure was a lucky guess."
    "晃さんが興味をそそられた様子で好奇の視線を俺に向ける。こんなの絶対まぐれ当たりに決まってる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1517
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_cf455b71:

    # hi "How did you…?"
    hi "なんでそれが……？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1525
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_84895856:

    # hh "You show no missing limbs or deformities, so external disabilities are out."
    hh "五体満足に見えるから、外側の障害じゃないでしょ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1530
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_50039022:

    # hh "Considering the lack of any strange mannerisms, it's also unlikely that you'd have any mental disability."
    hh "挙動も別に変じゃないから、知的障害ってわけでもなさそうだし"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1535
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_de0a44c8:

    # li "But Yamaku doesn't take mentally disabled students."
    li "でも、山久には知的障害を持つ生徒はいないのよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1540
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_a82cf1e5:

    # hh "I know."
    hh "知ってるよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1545
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_0f231ad7:

    # hh "Leaving that aside, the only possibility left is that of internal disabilities."
    hh "そんなことは置いといて、残った可能性といえば体内の障害しかない"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1550
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_423e5adb:

    # hh "I didn't know which one you might bear, so I guessed. Correctly, as it turns out. And your reaction confirmed my guess."
    hh "まあ、どこかまでは分からなかったから推測だったんだけど、正解みたいだね。久夫さんの反応ではっきりしたよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1555
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_83c4dcc7:

    # "More than a little bemused, I look to Akira. She grins and shrugs, obviously taking some enjoyment out of her partner's deductions."
    "あっけにとられながら、俺は晃さんを見る。晃さんは明らかに秀明くんの推理を楽しんだ様子で、笑いながら肩をすくめている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1557
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_89ead067:

    # "He's sharp, yes, but more than a little unsympathetic. Logical, but lacking in tact. His attitude reminds me of Shizune, in a way, as do his looks."
    "そう、秀明くんは賢い。でも、かなり思いやりに欠ける。論理的だけど、気が利かない。その態度はある意味、静音を思い起こさせる。外見もだけど。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1562
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_cd7431a3:

    # hh "May I ask why you're staring at me? Surely I'm not that unusual a specimen."
    hh "どうしてそんなにじろじろ僕のこと見てるんですか？　別に珍しいものでもないと思うんですけど"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1564
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_0a13c00d:

    # "Does he not know how unusual he looks? I could overlook the spats and clothing as just being coincidental, but the ribbon in his hair really is too much."
    "自分の外見がどれだけ普通じゃないか、気づいてないのか？　スパッツと服はたまたま着てきただけと見過ごすことはできても、さすがに頭のリボンはないだろ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1566
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_6ab30047:

    # "This is entirely beside the point, though."
    "だけど、今はそんなことを問題にしてるんじゃない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1568
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_72265436:

    # hi "Sorry. You just remind me of someone."
    hi "ごめん。君を見てたらある人のこと思い出しちゃってさ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1576
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_8f5f45aa:

    # "Akira gives him a sharp jab with her elbow."
    "晃さんが肘で秀明くんを鋭く小突く。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1581
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_a2dfc8f0:

    # aki "Told ya you're not that much different from her."
    aki "だからあの子とそんなに違わないって言っただろ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1586
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_371061d5:

    # "He coughs into his hand to try and maintain an upright and serious demeanor."
    "秀明くんが咳払いをして、まっすぐ真面目そうな見た目を保とうとする。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1588
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_47898324:

    # hh "I see you've met my sister, then. Perhaps my full name might help you."
    hh "じゃあ、姉さんに会ったんだね。たぶん僕のフルネームを言えば分かると思うけど"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1593
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_d4db36c5:

    # hh "I am Hideaki Hakamichi. You are probably thinking of my sister, Shizune Hakamichi."
    hh "僕は羽加道秀明。久夫さんが考えてるのって、たぶん僕の姉さん、羽加道静音のことでしょ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1595
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_33038178:

    # "Oh, so he's Shizune's brother."
    "えっ、じゃあ秀明くんは静音の弟か。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1597
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_2bc840dd:

    # "Wait a minute, if Hideaki is the son of Akira's uncle, and Shizune is his sister, then that means Lilly and Shizune's fathers are brothers-in-law. Therefore…"
    "あれ、ちょっと待てよ、もし秀明くんが晃さんのおじさんの息子で静音が彼の姉なら、リリーの父親と静音の父親は兄弟ってことで、それってつまり……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1599
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_155b2ea6:

    # hi "Lilly and Shizune are first cousins?"
    hi "じゃあ、リリーと静音は従姉妹同士ってこと？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1605
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_9072231d:

    # "Lilly groans in an uncharacteristically unrestrained manner. The reaction earns an amused smirk from her sister."
    "リリーがいつになく抑制のきかない様子でうめき声を漏らす。その反応を見て彼女の姉が面白そうにニヤつく。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1607
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_1ab62561:

    # "The enmity between the two just took on another meaning. I had thought it simply a matter of difficulty of communication between the two, but a family feud makes things much more complicated."
    "リリーと静音の対立が別の意味合いを持ってしまった。２人の意思疎通の難しさのせいだとばかり思っていたけど、家ぐるみの確執となると事はもっと複雑だ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1612
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_9b2d3286:

    # aki "You can choose your friends, but you can't choose your family."
    aki "友達は選べるけど、家族は選べないからねえ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1617
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_b030a829:

    # "She gives a halfhearted shrug. She mustn't give as much weight to the two's conflict as I do."
    "晃さんが気のない様子で肩をすくめる。２人の対立に関して、きっと俺みたいに深刻には考えていないんだろう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1622
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_e22ef6d2:

    # aki "Well, that's how it is. What're you two up to anyway on this fine day?"
    aki "まあ、そういうわけさ。２人はこんな天気のいい日に何してんだい？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1627
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_28a39847:

    # li "We're shopping for Hanako's birthday present. The day will be coming up soon, so this is the last chance we'll have before school starts again for the week."
    li "私たちは華ちゃんのお誕生日プレゼントを買いに来たんです。もう日が近いから、この休日がお誕生日前にプレゼントを買える最後のチャンスなので"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1634
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_ebf788df:

    # "Akira makes a strange face, as if Lilly had just said that the sky wasn't blue and the clouds not white."
    "まるでリリーから空は青くなく雲は白くないという言葉でも聞いたかのように、晃さんが変な表情を見せる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1636
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_4244b400:

    # aki "Isn't her birthday on the tenth next month?"
    aki "華子の誕生日って、来月の１０日じゃなかったかい？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1641
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_3d074483:

    # li "Yes… Why? Is something wrong?"
    li "ええ……どうして？　それが何か？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1646
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_6f2f584e:

    # "Akira's face seems to collapse. It's an utterly unbefitting expression for someone so rowdy and headstrong."
    "晃さんの笑みが少し消えた気がする。こんなに騒々しくて気ままな人物には全然似つかわしくない表情をしている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1648
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_6c2d90fc:

    # aki "The folks didn't call you yet?"
    aki "じゃあ、まだ電話来てないんだな？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1654
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_5170bb10:

    # "As Lilly shakes her head cluelessly, I look at Hideaki to see if he knows anything about this. A simple shrug is his only answer."
    "リリーが何も分からないといった様子で首を振る。俺は秀明くんの方を見て何が起こっているのか知ろうとしたけど、彼もただ肩をすくめるだけだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1659
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_379905b2:

    # "For a moment, Akira ponders what to do before smiling once again. The fact that she can hide her emotions so quickly and effectively is unsettling."
    "晃さんはしばらくどうするか考えて、また笑顔に戻る。自分の感情をあっという間に隠してしまう晃さんに俺は戸惑う。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1664
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_48bbd4d2:

    # aki "Hey Shortie, sorry, but could you hang with Hisao for a while?"
    aki "よう、チビ助、済まないけど久夫としばらくその辺をぶらついててくれないかな？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1689
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_db7dc41b:

    # "He nods and waves her off, Akira placing an arm on Lilly's shoulder as she guides her away and out of earshot."
    "秀明くんはうなずいて、晃さんに手を振る。晃さんはリリーの肩に腕を回すと、俺の目の届かない所に彼女を連れて行ってしまう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1691
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_11657e51:

    # "And so, I'm alone with 'Shortie.'"
    "そんなわけで、俺は『チビ助』と２人、取り残される。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1693
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_f481691a:

    # hi "So… nice weather, isn't it?"
    hi "えっと……いい天気だよな"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1698
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_9daf9b5a:

    # hh "It seems so."
    hh "そうみたいだね"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1700
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1702
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_954125ef:

    # hi "I guess they dumped us."
    hi "やっかい払いされちゃったみたいだな"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1707
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_ded14347:

    # hh "Indeed."
    hh "そうだね"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1709
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_62e2292f:

    # "What a farcical attempt at smalltalk. I've got no idea of how to talk to this guy, and his robotic responses aren't helping. Blood and a stone come to mind."
    "なんて茶番劇だ。この子とどう話せばいいのか全く分からない。秀明くんのそっけない返事も全く助けにならない。この会話は成り立たないんじゃないかという気がしてくる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1714
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_8ac32134:

    # "Without another word, he begins to rock on his feet in an obvious gesture of boredom with this discussion. He really is like a little kid, despite his serious demeanor."
    "秀明くんは明らかに退屈した様子で何も言わずに足をぶらぶらさせ始める。真面目ぶっているけど中身は本当にまだ小さな子供みたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1716
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_bb4883ea:

    # "Suspecting the conversation over, I decide to accomplish what I came here to do in the first place."
    "秀明くんとの会話も終わっているような気がするので、俺はここに来たそもそもの目的を達成することにする。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1718
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_3b1057b5:

    # hi "I'm going to go search for a present. Coming?"
    hi "俺はプレゼントを探しに行くけど、一緒に来る？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1723
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_d6792514:

    # hh "Not much else to do."
    hh "他にすることもないしね"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1733
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_8f5e6aef:

    # "In a little while, we come to a small shop beside a convenience store."
    "しばらくして、俺と秀明くんはコンビニの脇にある小さな店にたどり着く。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1735
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_3f512ad9:

    # "For once the store windows aren't filled with electronics and computer games, but dolls, stuffed bears and all manners of wood-crafted oddities."
    "やっと見つかったその店のショーウインドウには、電化製品やパソコンゲームではなく、人形やぬいぐるみ、木製の工芸雑貨などが並べられている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1737
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_fd9b9669:

    # hi "Othello's… Antiques?"
    hi "オセローズ……アンティーク？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1739
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_84e7a8b2:

    # "An antique store? Well, if there's anything in this town that'd suit Hanako, I guess it'd be here."
    "アンティークショップ？　うーん、もしこの街に華子に合いそうなものがあるとしたら、たぶんここだろう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1741
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_db1fc8a4:

    # "I reach for the old-looking door handle, but pull back at the last minute as I realize my companion's gone adrift."
    "古ぼけたドアの握りを掴もうとして、秀明くんがふらりとその場を離れようとしているのに気づき、また手を引っこめる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1743
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_bc2e718f:

    # hi "Not coming in?"
    hi "入らないの？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1748
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_5ea57e38:

    # hh "I'll just be in the newsstand for a while. Don't mind me."
    hh "しばらく売店にでもいるよ。僕のことは気にしなくていいから"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1750
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_da9da446:

    # "His voice makes it painfully clear he has zero interest in what's in the store, and that he doesn't feel obligated to follow me."
    "秀明くんの声の調子から、彼が店の売り物に全く興味を持っていないのが痛いほど分かる。俺に付いていく義務も感じていないようだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1755
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_b34262a8:

    # "As he wanders off without another word, I push the thick wooden door and enter the store, a bell above me ringing out."
    "秀明くんがそのまま一言もしゃべらず立ち去った後、厚い木製のドアを開けて店の中に入ると、俺の頭上でベルが鳴る。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1767
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_79b75b17:

    # "The musty smell of old books and wooden shelves is distinctly anachronistic."
    "古い本と木製の棚から立ち込めるカビ臭さが、疑いようのない時の流れを感じさせる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1769
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_6a347470:

    # "I look to the counter beside the door. The graying man behind it sits there silently, reading a tattered book. He certainly fits the look of the place."
    "ドア脇のカウンターを見る。そこでは白髪の男の人が静かに座っていて、ボロボロになった本を読んでいる。この場に似つかわしい雰囲気だ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1771
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_85c776b6:

    # "Slowly wandering through the aisles, the person I'm reminded of as I inspect each handcrafted or imported oddity in turn isn't Hanako."
    "ゆっくりと通路をぶらつき工芸品や輸入雑貨を見て回っていると、華子以外のある人物のことが頭に浮かぶ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1773
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_8a2dc293:

    # "Crouching down, I examine the ancient oak desk inside the shop window."
    "身をかがめて、ガラスケースの中にある年代物の樫の机を眺める。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1775
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_1e22bbf7:

    # "At least thirty dolls, all varying wildly in size and make. The only similarity between them is the long Victorian dresses they wear."
    "大きさも造りも違う人形が、少なくとも３０体は並んでいる。共通点といえば、ビクトリア風の長いドレスを着ていることぐらいだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1777
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_8f3d3b31:

    # "I turn the price tag of one that looks to be about waist-height."
    "そのひとつの腰のあたりに付いている値札をめくってみる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1779
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_e225602e:

    # "…It's not in my price bracket. At all."
    "……とても手が届かない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1781
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_a308c340:

    # "I do the same to each of them, getting more and more depressed as they get smaller and smaller in size."
    "それぞれの値札を順番にめくっていく。人形がどんどん小さくなっていくのに反して、俺の失望はどんどん大きくなる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1783
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_2844e042:

    # "That is, until I reach the very smallest one. It's affordable, just, yet of quality make and with long, auburn hair and a little blue dress."
    "それも、一番小さい人形に行き着くまでのことだった。ぎりぎりで手が届く値段だけど、出来はいい。長い赤褐色の髪を持ち、小さな青いドレスに身を包んでいる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1785
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_27089efa:

    # "I decide that it's the kind of present Hanako would appreciate. Pretty-looking, and far from gaudy."
    "このプレゼントなら華子も喜んでくれるだろう。可愛らしくて、けばけばしくない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1787
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_4560730c:

    # "After I carefully pick it up, I decide to keep looking around the store. I'm not sure whether it's because I like the atmosphere or out of simple curiosity."
    "それを注意深く手に取った後も、俺はしばらく店内を見て回ることにする。店の雰囲気を気に入っているのか、ただの好奇心なのか、自分でもよく分からないけど。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1793
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_d5d7fefc:

    # "Peeking around the corner before I go to the next aisle, I see that the shelves in this one are stocked with wooden toys; from toy cars to intricate automatons."
    "隣の通路に移る前にちらっと隅を見ると、木製のおもちゃが並べられた棚が置いてある。そこにはミニカーもあれば、精巧なからくり人形もある。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1803
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_ea1dc45e:

    # "Tucked behind a line of nutcrackers, I notice a little plain wooden box. It feels surprisingly light as I pick it up with my free hand."
    "ずらりと並ぶくるみ割り人形の陰に隠れていた、小さくて飾り気のない木箱の存在に気づく。空いている手でそれを持ち上げると、びっくりするほど軽い。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1810
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_aadc0a52:

    # "The lid only needs the smallest movement to pop open, the little metal drum inside beginning to rotate immediately."
    "箱のふたは簡単に開き、すかさず中にある金属のドラムが回りだす。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1812
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_006c5945:

    # "For seconds on end, I simply stand there listening to the palm-sized melody."
    "しばらくのあいだ、ただその場に立ち尽くしたまま、俺は手の平サイズの旋律に耳を傾ける。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1814
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_b9d60217:

    # "As it plays, I take the tiny price tag in my fingers and bring it up to my face, the minuscule cursive writing taking some effort to read."
    "それがまだ鳴っている時に、小さな値札を指でつまんで顔の近くに持っていく。ものすごく小さな手書きの字で、読み取るのもひと苦労だ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1816
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_303959a8:

    # "It's affordable… sort of."
    "買えない……こともないな。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1831
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_6fde37da:

    # "Grimacing slightly, I close the lid and make my way to the counter with doll and music box in hand."
    "ほんの少し顔をしかめながら、俺は箱のふたを閉じて人形とオルゴールをカウンターまで持っていく。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1836
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_2ec76fa4:

    # "When I lay the two on the counter, the man behind it sits up and takes stock of them. He doesn't hide very well his surprise at someone of my age buying them."
    "俺が品物をカウンターに並べている時、男の人が姿勢を正してその二つに目を向ける。俺みたいな若い人間がこんなものを買うことに驚きを隠せないようだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1841
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_d345232c:

    # "It's painful, but I hand over the money for the two and leave the store with a small opaque bag in hand."
    "痛い出費だけど、俺は代金を支払い、小さくて中身の透けない袋を持って店を出る。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1849
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_51933500:

    # "Hideaki being there takes me by surprise."
    "秀明くんがその場にいて、俺は驚く。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1851
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_23ae9c24:

    # hi "Oh… hi. I thought you'd be at the newsstand."
    hi "おっと……やあ。売店にいるもんだとばかり思ってたけど"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1856
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_229b96ec:

    # hh "Akira gave me a call. She's waiting for us at the fountain with Lilly."
    hh "晃さんから電話がかかってきたんだ。噴水の所でリリーさんと待ってるってさ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1858
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_2eeb71d8:

    # "At least that solves the issue of trying to find them again."
    "少なくともこれであの２人を探す必要はなくなったわけだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1865
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_8ae97e74:

    # "We head off back to the fountain. Hideaki's immaculate posture and presentation despite his appearance makes for a strange contrast even as we walk."
    "俺たちは噴水目指して歩き出す。秀明くんの清楚ないでたちと外見に似つかわしくない振る舞いは、歩いている間でさえ変に対照的だ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1871
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_a6c744aa:

    # "Lilly and Akira stand there waiting for us, their faces hard to read."
    "リリーと晃さんが立ったまま俺たちを待っている。２人がなにを考えているのか、その表情からではよく分からない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1876
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_e1001b81:

    # aki "Hey. You ready to go, Shortie?"
    aki "よう。じゃあ行くか、チビ助？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1887
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_7b4f51dd:

    # "Hideaki's mood seems to improve as he rejoins her."
    "秀明くんも晃さんの元に戻って機嫌が直ったようだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1892
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_bbad04d9:

    # aki "Seeya Lilly, Hisao. Tell Hanako I said happy birthday."
    aki "またな、リリー、久夫。華子に誕生日おめでとうって伝えてくれ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1894
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_bedf77ab:

    # hi "We will. Bye."
    hi "伝えときます。それじゃ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1899
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_6e80cf90:

    # li "Goodbye, Akira."
    li "さようなら、姉さん"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1910
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_9c56ca77:

    # "And with that, the two disappear into the fracas of the afternoon city crowd."
    "その挨拶を最後に、２人は昼下がりの街の喧騒の中へと消えていく。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1912
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_e637660c:

    # "Turning to Lilly, I notice she's carrying a small bag. It's now that I realize why her disposition felt different from before; while Lilly's typically the type to wear her emotions on her sleeve, her expression and tone are clouded and difficult to read."
    "リリーに向き直ると、小さな袋を持っているのに気づく。その時、リリーの様子が以前と違うような気がした理由がわかった。普段は感情を隠したりしないのに、今のリリーの表情と口調は曖昧で、読み取りづらい。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1914
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_ed6384c5:

    # "It's more than a little off-putting, but given the effort she's making to hide her emotions, I doubt she wants to be cornered on why she's feeling this way."
    "かなり気になるけど、リリーが自分の感情を隠そうとしているところを見ると、今の気持ちを俺に根掘り葉掘り聞かれたくはないだろう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1916
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_9165163c:

    # hi "Already bought Hanako a present?"
    hi "華子へのプレゼントはもう買った？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1921
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_ca17ea7a:

    # li "Yes. Have you?"
    li "ええ。久夫さんは？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1923
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_142d50b9:

    # hi "Yeah."
    hi "そうだな"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1928
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_562f741f:

    # li "Shall we head back to the bus stop then?"
    li "それでは、バス停に戻りましょうか？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1930
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_fe16565f:

    # hi "Okay. There should be a bus back to Yamaku pretty soon."
    hi "分かった。もうすぐ山久行きのバスが来るはずだしな"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1932
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_590225ec:

    # "And with that, we begin to walk."
    "こうして、俺とリリーは歩き出す。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1940
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_dea4a049:

    # "It feels strange compared to before. Lilly's hand on my forearm feels unusually tense, and the whole atmosphere is extraordinarily awkward."
    "さっきと比べて様子が変だ。俺の腕を掴むリリーの手は不自然にこわばっていて、なんだかものすごく気まずい雰囲気になる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1942
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_e0dd01e8:

    # "The silence continues for a long while. I really don't like seeing her like this."
    "沈黙が長い間続く。こんなリリーを見るのは全くいい気がしない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1947
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_03707b21:

    # li "Hanako's birthday party is going to have to be held earlier. Is the fourth going to be all right for you?"
    li "華ちゃんのお誕生日会、早めに開かないといけなくなってしまったのですが。久夫さんは４日でも大丈夫でしょうか？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1949
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_8d946768:

    # "I have no other possible obligations anyway, so I reflexively nod. Only afterwards do I remember that doing so is pointless, and quickly answer so by speech."
    "別に他にすべきこともないだろうし、俺は反射的にうなずく。その後でこの行為が無意味であることを思い出し、すぐに口に出して返事をする。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1951
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_ecbc1783:

    # "She tries to collect herself, a task that looks almost pitiable in how plain it is to see how distant her thoughts are."
    "リリーが冷静になろうと努力している。それが彼女の感情とかけ離れていることは明らかで、その様子は見ていてかわいそうに感じるほどだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1956
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_ce32458c:

    # li "Sorry, Hisao. You said the bus would be coming soon, right?"
    li "すみません、久夫さん。バスはもうすぐ来るのでしたね？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1958
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_0535be30:

    # hi "That's right."
    hi "そうだよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1960
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_d7babee2:

    # "But now that she says that, I have an idea."
    "でも、リリーがそう言った時、俺はあることを思いつく。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1962
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_66c80454:

    # hi "Actually, do you have anything to do later today?"
    hi "そうだな、リリーはこの後何か予定ある？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1967
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_f67f3e1f:

    # li "I… don't believe so. Why do you ask?"
    li "いえ……特には。どうしてですか？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1969
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_bb8b3ad5:

    # hi "This is the point where I'd normally take your hand and rush you somewhere, but even without that, you'll have to trust me. Okay?"
    hi "今こそリリーの手を取ってどこかに連れ去る時じゃないか、って思ってさ。まあ、そんなことはしないけど、俺を信用してくれる？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1974
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_ee151d4e:

    # "I take her hand and gently lead her on, her distant face replaced by one of mild surprise and curiosity."
    "俺はリリーの手を取り、それを引く。すると彼女のうつろな表情が軽い驚きと好奇心の混じった表情に変わる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1984
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_4a17895c:

    # "As the waitress sets the cup of tea and cup of coffee that I'd ordered onto the table, I thank her before she takes her leave."
    "ウェイトレスが俺の頼んだ紅茶とコーヒーをテーブルに置く。俺は立ち去ろうとする彼女に軽くお礼を言う。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1986
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_77091fb6:

    # "Truth be told, I really lucked out in finding this café. I didn't really know where I was going, rather I was just looking for any café that looked relatively nice."
    "実をいうと、この喫茶店を見つけたのは本当にラッキーだった。俺はどこに行くべきかを考えあぐねていた。いや、むしろ俺はどこかによさそうな雰囲気の喫茶店がないかを探していたんだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1988
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_abb48791:

    # "Having managed to recover a little, Lilly tentatively sips at her cup as I take a long gulp of the coffee in front of me."
    "リリーは少し元気を取り戻した様子で、コーヒーをごくごく飲んでいる俺の前でカップから一口だけ試し飲みする。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1990
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_29acdac3:

    # "As I hoped, her face lights up as she realizes what flavor it is."
    "俺が望んだとおり、リリーはその味に気づくと、ぱっと表情を輝かせる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1996
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_22d5a471:

    # li "Ah… this is wonderful!"
    li "まあ……素敵！"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2001
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_e265768f:

    # li "Hisao, how did you know that this was…?"
    li "久夫さん、どうしてこれだと……？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2003
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_3b897709:

    # "I'd asked for French vanilla black tea, hedging my bets that it would be her favorite flavor, or at least one she liked. While I don't really know much about tea, it sounded like one she might appreciate."
    "きっとリリーのお気に入り、いや少なくとも好みではあるんじゃないかと思って、俺はフレンチバニラティーのストレートを注文していた。紅茶のことはよく知らないけど、その名前から彼女が喜びそうな気はしていた。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2005
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_a8829ee8:

    # "…on the basis of her liking vanilla ice cream. A tea connoisseur I am definitely not."
    "……リリーがバニラアイス好きだから、って理由だけど。俺は間違いなく紅茶通じゃないな。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2007
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_2d964f9a:

    # hi "It was a lucky guess. You really like tea, don't you?"
    hi "まぐれ当たりだよ。本当に紅茶好きなんだな？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2012
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_b1345a5b:

    # "She puts her teacup down and gives a tiny nod, that familiar small smile thankfully perched on her face once again."
    "リリーはティーカップを机に置くと、小さくうなずく。幸いなことに彼女はいつもの微笑みを取り戻している。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2017
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_12e9cf41:

    # li "Drinking tea is… calming, I think."
    li "紅茶を飲むと……なんだか落ち着くんです"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2019
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_51e7b0cc:

    # hi "With the amount you drink, are you sure you're not addicted to it? Caffeine addiction's pretty common nowadays."
    hi "そんなに飲んで、中毒になってない？　カフェイン中毒ってのは最近よくあるけどさ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2024
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_b30e208a:

    # li "Did I ever say I wasn't?"
    li "あら、私が中毒だって言いませんでしたっけ？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2026
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_936dff74:

    # "She lets out a giggle as my head drops. We all have our vices, I suppose, and there are worse things to be addicted to."
    "俺が顔を伏せるとリリーがくすくすと笑う。誰にでも悪癖の一つや二つはあるもんだ。世の中にはもっと悪い中毒だってあるんだし。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2028
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_2e070d24:

    # hi "French vanilla black tea, huh? I'll have to remember that."
    hi "フレンチバニラティーのストレート、か。覚えとかなきゃな"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2033
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_71e1f370:

    # "For a while, we both silently drink. It's comforting to have someone like her nearby in such new surroundings, even if it's just the two of us sitting in silence."
    "しばらくのあいだ、黙ったままそれぞれの飲み物を飲む。慣れない環境にいる俺にとって、リリーみたいな人が近くにいてくれるだけでとても心落ち着く。たとえ何もしゃべらず座っているだけでも。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2035
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_5536af7b:

    # "I begin to wonder if this feeling is the same for her, until she sets down her cup."
    "リリーもそう思ってくれてるかなあ、と考え始めた時、彼女がカップを置く。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2040
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_0ff494cf:

    # li "Hisao, do you mind if I ask you a slightly odd question?"
    li "久夫さん、少しおかしなことを聞いてもいいですか？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2042
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_a4af47e0:

    # hi "That depends on the question, I guess."
    hi "質問にもよると思うけど"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2047
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_3aeabe83:

    # li "I was wondering… what your favorite color is. Everyone has one, after all."
    li "久夫さんは……何色が好きなのかしら、って。誰にでも好きな色があるものだから"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2049
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_4856898d:

    # "I almost reply before realizing why the seemingly mundane question is actually quite strange."
    "それに答えようとした時、俺はこのありふれているかに思える質問が実はとても奇妙なものであることに気づく。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2051
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_62925a18:

    # hi "My favorite color? But…"
    hi "好きな色？　でも……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2056
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_5a56accf:

    # "She gives a pouting look, wanting me to answer anyway. While the answer seems unavoidably wasted on her, there isn't any harm in giving it."
    "リリーが頬を膨らませる。いいから答えなさいとでも言いたげだ。そんなことを知っても彼女には何の役にも立たないだろうけど、別に教えたって害にはならない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2058
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_08acb58c:

    # hi "I've always had a thing for green. I'd say that's my favorite."
    hi "いつも緑に魅かれてたな。たぶんそれが俺の好きな色だ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2063
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_53ffc04a:

    # li "Green, is it? What things do you think of when contemplating that color?"
    li "緑ですね？　その色のことを考えるとき、久夫さんはどんなものを連想しますか？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2065
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_a7cc9ef5:

    # hi "I suppose… grass fields and trees in summer. The Army as well, with camouflage."
    hi "たぶん……夏の芝生や木々かな。あと、軍もだな。迷彩色なんだ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2070
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_897f2eef:

    # li "Men always seem to like the military."
    li "男の人って、皆軍隊が好きなようですね"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2075
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_a407c4e6:

    # li "But… that sounds like a nice color. A very nice color."
    li "だけど……素敵な色のようですね。とても素敵な色"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2077
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_b9b05c8a:

    # "She nods her head a little, as if approving of the choice. Considering how foreign the concept of color is to her mind, labeling it by association seems reasonable enough."
    "リリーが俺の選択を受け入れるかのように小さくうなずく。彼女の中にある色の概念が俺のものとは全く違うということを考えると、それを具体的なものと関連付けるのは確かに理にかなっている気がする。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2079
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_7ba99119:

    # hi "If everyone has a favorite color, then what's yours?"
    hi "もし誰でも好きな色を持ってるならさ、リリーの好きな色は何だ？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2084
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_42845ccf:

    # li "White. I'm told that's the color of snow, and of ice cream."
    li "白。雪の色、それからアイスクリームの色だと教えられました"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2086
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_4b68c477:

    # hi "You're no better than me then, if you only like that color because of a favorite food. I guess white is nice too, though."
    hi "それじゃ俺とあんまり変わらないな。好きな食べ物の色だから、って理由だし。でもまあ、白もいい色だと思うよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2088
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_d50fde3e:

    # hi "And speaking of colors, it'll be getting dark soon. Let me help you up."
    hi "色といえば、ここももうすぐ暗くなるな。立つの手伝うよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2096
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_948e820f:

    # "Lilly offers her hand, which I take in mine to help lever her up from her seat at the table. Its softness compared to mine takes me off guard, as I'm really not used to such casual contact."
    "リリーが手を差し出す。俺はその手を取って席から立ち上がるのを手伝う。こんな何気ない触れあいには慣れていないおかげで、自分のとは比べ物にならない彼女の手の柔らかさに思わずはっとしてしまう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2098
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_e794b1f3:

    # "It doesn't seem to bother her at all though. While it seems obvious why, it feels like just one more ladylike aspect to her."
    "だけど、リリーがそれを気にする様子はない。理由は明らかな気もするけど、一方ではそれも彼女の上品な物腰の現れのように思える。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2100
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_dab722c4:

    # "As her hand moves to her pocket, I quickly cut her off."
    "リリーが自分のポケットに手を忍ばせようとするのを見て、俺は急いでそれを引き止める。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2102
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_9311fcda:

    # hi "Don't worry, I'll pay for this."
    hi "ああ、いいよ。俺が払う"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2107
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_0bb57d0e:

    # li "Oh. Thank you, Hisao."
    li "まあ、ありがとうございます、久夫さん"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2109
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_75a98ac2:

    # "She gives an earnest smile at the gesture, a reward much greater than that of her words."
    "リリーの心の底からの笑顔を見て、お礼の言葉をもらうよりもはるかに大きな見返りを得た気分になる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2119
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_034dcd61:

    # "By the time we step off the bus, it's well and truly dark."
    "俺たちがバスを降りるころには、辺りはもう真っ暗になっている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2126
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_4e3e8f00:

    # "We make our way up the hill in silence, both of us behaving a little awkwardly, probably because of the day's events."
    "俺とリリーは無言のまま丘を登っていく。たぶん今日過ごした時間のせいか、俺たちは２人とも少しぎこちなく振る舞っている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2128
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_387bbdd6:

    # "While I'm still concerned over Lilly's withdrawn nature after meeting with her sister, the fact I managed to cheer her up even slightly feels like a personal victory."
    "リリーが晃さんに会った後に浮かない態度を見せていたのは気になるけど、ほんの少しであっても彼女を励ますことができたという事実を思い出し、なんだか勝ち誇った気分になる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2130
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_72ab849a:

    # "But… it feels like the air between us has changed. Maybe it's only a bit, but it's something I don't think either of us realized before."
    "だけど……２人の間の空気が変わってしまったような気がする。ほんの少しだけかもしれないけど、俺たちのどちらも今までそのことを自覚していなかった。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2135
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_693720f8:

    # li "That was… a date, wasn't it?"
    li "これって……デート、ですよね？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2137
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_8b8caef5:

    # "It was. That doesn't elude either of us, the question's answer being so self-evident as to be rhetorical."
    "そうだ。そのことは２人とも理解している。その問いに対する答えは、修辞的とさえ言えるくらいに明白だ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2139
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_18a7bfe1:

    # "Awkward as it may be, I don't think this feeling is bad. In fact, quite the opposite. I don't know what it is, I certainly can't be sure, but it feels like something a little more than friendship."
    "なんだか気まずいような気もするけど、そんなに悪い気分じゃない。いや、むしろ正反対だ。どういえばいいのか分からないし、もちろんはっきりとは言えないけど、ほんの少し友達以上の何か、という感じがする。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2141
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_b07797a2:

    # "Understanding? Empathy? Searching for words to adequately describe it is difficult. Nonetheless…"
    "理解？　共感？　なかなか適当な言葉が見つからない。それでも……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2143
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_d31b3ffc:

    # hi "Would you like do this again sometime, Lilly? Without shopping for presents?"
    hi "リリー、また今度一緒に行こうか？　プレゼントを買いに行くんじゃなくてさ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2148
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_1eceff28:

    # "The tentative question is met with the same look from Lilly as before. Her pale skin makes the rosy tint of her cheeks just slightly more noticeable and her face, though still pointed to the street ahead of her, lowers. Just a little."
    "試しに聞いてみても、リリーの様子は変わらない。ただ、その頬がわずかに赤く染まっているのが色白な肌のおかげでかろうじて分かる。そして目の前の道路に向けたままの顔を下げる。ほんの少しだけ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2153
translate jp a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_595c3d64:

    # li "…Okay."
    li "……ええ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2171
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_68e52ddb:

    # "I walk down the hall of the girls' dormitories, my schoolbag in hand."
    "学校のかばんを手に、俺は女子寮へと向かう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2173
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_fe917c86:

    # "A doll lies inside, carefully placed on top of a small box. I've been carrying the box in there for a while now, still not sure of what to do with it."
    "かばんの中には、小さな箱と、その上に注意深く置かれた人形。しばらくかばんに入れっぱなしにしているけど、この箱をどう扱えばいいのか、まだよく分からずにいる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2175
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_2d4a5a3e:

    # "This whole situation, come to think of it, is bizarre."
    "考えてみれば、奇妙な状況だ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2177
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_c0a8fa50:

    # "While I've known of Hanako's upcoming birthday party for a while now, I had no idea of exactly what the celebrations would be until I found a single note left in the abandoned tea room earlier today."
    "華子の誕生パーティーが近づいていることは分かっていたけど、しばらく前に誰もいない紅茶部屋で小さなメモ書きを見つけるまでは、それが一体どんなものになるのか見当もついていなかった。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2179
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_962f26b0:

    # "I hold it up and read it again, doublechecking the instructions. The plain black handwriting's fairly legible despite Lilly's blindness, clearly thanks to considerable effort and care."
    "もう一度手に取り、メモの内容を確認する。目が見えないリリーが書いたとは思えないほどすごく読みやすいシンプルな黒色の手書き。これが彼女の多大な努力と注意の賜物であることは明らかだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2183
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_c1ddb7fb:

    # "Not reassured, I continue walking down the hallway until I reach Lilly's dormitory room. I hesitate for a second, but eventually give three sharp taps on the door."
    "俺はおどおどしながら廊下を進み、リリーの部屋の前まで来る。少しためらったけど、ついに決心してドアを鋭く３回ノックする。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2189
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_01d246e5:

    # "A brief and muffled exchange of words can be heard from the other side. Listening closer, I can just pick out Hanako and Lilly's voices."
    "ドアの向こうで短いくぐもった言葉が交わされるのが聞こえる。耳を凝らすと、華子とリリーの声だということが分かる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2191
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_b59589d4:

    # "As they finish, Lilly calls out."
    "会話が終わり、リリーが俺に呼びかける。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2193
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_5056f26f:

    # li "Might that be Hisao?"
    li "久夫さんですね？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2195
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_139514f9:

    # hi "Yep. I got the note you left for me."
    hi "うん。書き置き見たよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2197
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_fc11b9b1:

    # li "You can come in, the door is unlocked."
    li "どうぞ。鍵は開いていますよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2199
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_a7b95d2b:

    # "Glad that I managed to get the right room, I press down on the handle and let myself in."
    "部屋を間違えていなかったことにほっとした俺は、ドアの取っ手を下げて部屋の中へ入っていく。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2203
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_a95d169d:

    # "As the door swings open, my greeting to them is stolen from my mouth."
    "ドアが開いた時、挨拶しようとしていた俺は息を呑む。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2213
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_55426388:

    # "Lilly sits at a low table in the center of the room in her pajamas, while on the other side sits Hanako in a nightgown. Being dressed in only my normal school clothes, I feel quite out of place."
    "パジャマに身を包んだリリーが部屋の真ん中にあるローテーブルのそばに座り、その向かいにはナイトガウンを着た華子が座っている。制服姿でしかない俺はひどく場違いな気持ちになる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2215
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_d9dd8877:

    # "I steal a quick glance at the lovely sight of the two, my eyes tearing themselves from Lilly's long, thin and pale legs only with a measure of reluctance."
    "２人の可愛らしい姿をちらりと盗み見て、不本意ながらもリリーの細長い色白の脚から視線を引きはがす。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2217
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_d8f9b4b8:

    # hi "H-hi. I… think I brought everything that was needed."
    hi "や、やあ。俺……必要な物、全部持ってきたと思うけど"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2224
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_d0796007:

    # "She smiles and nods. I wonder if she's even aware of the pleasant sight she makes. The thin dark blue silk of her pajamas really suits her, accentuating both her eyes and her curves."
    "リリーが微笑んでうなずく。自分がこんなに色っぽい姿をしていることに、本人は気づいているんだろうか。ダークブルーの薄いシルクのパジャマがよく似合い、それが彼女の目と体の曲線をさらに際立たせている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2226
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_8e422385:

    # "The look of her last night, that tentative and almost shy demeanor, seems all but replaced by her coy nature. It's nice to see her confidence returned, though I can't help casting my mind back to how she looked back then."
    "昨夜のリリーの曖昧でためらうかのような様子は、いつもの挑発的な性格に取って代わられたみたいだ。彼女が自信を取り戻したのはいいことだけど、あの時の様子がどうしても頭に浮かんでしまう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2233
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_ad727bdb:

    # "I look to Hanako, who nervously sits opposite her in her gown. It isn't a surprise that she'd wear something so conservative, though it definitely looks cute."
    "華子のほうを見ると、緊張した面持ちでリリーの向かいに座っている。こんなに地味な寝巻きを着ているのも別に驚くことじゃないけど、とても可愛く見える。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2235
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_03ef6630:

    # hi "Hi, Hanako. Happy birthday."
    hi "やあ、華子。誕生日おめでとう"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2237
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_3158b324:

    # ha "Ah… th-thank you."
    ha "えっと……あ、ありがとうございます"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2239
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_00df23f1:

    # "She's unusually skittish, despite the fact that she's warmed up to me considerably over the weeks we've come to know each other. This is a pretty unusual situation, I guess."
    "華子はすごくおどおどしている。知り合った時よりも俺にかなり打ち解けた態度を見せるようになってきた彼女だけど、たぶん今みたいな状況には慣れていないんだろう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2244
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_66d11420:

    # li "Feel free to take a seat, Hisao. I'll just pour you two some tea."
    li "久夫さん、どうぞ座ってください。すぐにお茶を入れますね"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2246
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_0527a675:

    # hi "Sure thing."
    hi "じゃあ遠慮なく"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2253
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_90daa391:

    # "Lilly takes the steaming red teapot from the side of the table and gently pours its contents into our teacups as I take a seat beside them, setting my bag against the nearby wall."
    "俺が近くの壁際にかばんを置いて座ろうとするあいだ、リリーは机の脇から湯気の立つ赤色のティーポットを手に取り、それぞれのティーカップに中身を注ぐ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2255
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_0c5bfc12:

    # "With my senses returned and hormones somewhat calmer, I realize that this is the first time I've ever been in Lilly's room."
    "大分落ち着きを取り戻してきて、俺は自分がリリーの部屋に来るのはこれが初めてだということを思い出す。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2257
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_827e071d:

    # "The first thing I notice is the ambient smell, just slightly different from that in mine… probably faint perfume, or nail polish. It could be anything of a girl's, really."
    "最初に気づくのは、部屋の中に立ち込めるほのかな香り。俺の部屋のものとは何となく違う……たぶんかすかな香水か、マニキュアだろう。何にせよ女の子の持ち物っぽい香りがする。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2259
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_3eb3cd63:

    # "Another is the plain nature of the room, visually. Beige walls, a smart yet unadorned cabinet, the lack of posters or wall hangings. It's distinctly utilitarian, something I should have anticipated given her blindness."
    "それと、リリーの部屋は見た目が地味だ。ベージュ色の壁に、機能的だけど簡素な収納棚。ポスターや壁掛けの類いは見当たらない。際立って実用的だけど、リリーは目が見えないのだから当然のことだろう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2261
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_9a5dfeb6:

    # "The only thing that really seems out of the ordinary is several piles of books sitting on the floor, each reaching from roughly knee height to waist height. Some of them have printed titles, others are entirely blank except for dots of Braille."
    "俺が唯一不自然に感じたのが、床の上にうず高く積まれているいくつかの本の山だ。どれも膝から腰の高さまである。何冊かの表紙にはタイトルが書いてあるけど、他の本には点字以外に何も書かれていない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2263
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_c6a8a73a:

    # "The fact that the ones with printed titles are uniformly in English is interesting, though not completely unexpected. She did mention her parents impressing the language upon her and Akira, after all."
    "文字として印刷されているタイトルも例外なく英字なのが興味深いけど、全く予想外ってわけじゃない。そういえば以前、リリーの両親が彼女と晃さんに英語を教えたと言ってたっけ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2265
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_62e8bb22:

    # hi "Your room looks nice, Lilly."
    hi "いい部屋だな、リリー"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2272
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_d6f065cd:

    # "I hear a call of thanks from beside my shoulder. Looking back to Hanako, her gaze is fixed on her lap and her hands are nervously clutching her gown."
    "肩越しにお礼の言葉を聞く。華子のほうを振り返ると、自分の膝元をじっと見据えながら、神経質そうに自分の寝巻きを手でぎゅっと掴んでいる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2274
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_2278cbd8:

    # "It's now that I notice why. With these clothes on, the extent of her scarring is far more visible; reaching down her neck and out to cover her right shoulder."
    "その理由に今になって気づく。この姿だと華子のやけどの跡が普段よりもはるかにはっきりと見えてしまうからだ。やけどの跡は首元にまで達していて、さらに右肩の全体を覆っている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2276
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_dc49cb38:

    # "Considering this is a party for her, she doesn't really look like she's enjoying the experience now that I'm here."
    "華子のためのパーティーだというのに、当の本人は俺がいるせいで全然楽しめていないようだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2278
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_7ae4585f:

    # hi "So how old are you turning? Eighteen?"
    hi "それで、何歳になった？　１８歳？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2283
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_86e6325d:

    # "Her look of surprise, not at all helped by her total lack of skill at hiding her feelings, shows that she was trying to mentally tune me out. This is really quite awkward."
    "感情を隠すのが苦手な華子の驚いた様子からすると、どうやら彼女は俺の存在を頭の中で消し去ろうとしていたようだ。なんだかすごく気まずいな。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2285
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_13b7ab07:

    # ha "Y-yes."
    ha "は、はい"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2287
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_9ead570a:

    # hi "On the plus side, there's only two more years till you can drink. So who's older? You or Lilly?"
    hi "いいことといえば、あと二年で酒が飲めるってことだな。それで、どっちが年上？　華子、それともリリー？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2292
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_fdf2a662:

    # ha "Lilly. She had her birthday in… F-February. What about… yours?"
    ha "リリーです。に、二月が……誕生日だったから。久夫くん……は？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2294
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_2f1e18bc:

    # hi "Earlier this year, so it's already passed."
    hi "今年のしばらく前だよ。もう過ぎちゃったな"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2296
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_86a57921:

    # "Unstated is that it passed while I was stuck in the hospital. That was… a particularly low point of the experience."
    "俺が病院に閉じ込められている間に過ぎてしまったってことは言わないでおく。あの時は……人生のどん底だった。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2314
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_cc32dd9f:

    # "Conversation with her dries up as quickly as expected. It isn't long before Lilly's finished preparing our drinks, setting down the three teacups in front of us."
    "予想通り、会話はすぐに途切れてしまう。その直後にリリーが飲み物を支度し終えて、３人分のティーカップを並べる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2316
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_18470a38:

    # "I pick mine up, immediately noticing a much stronger aroma and taste than the tea we've been having."
    "自分のカップを取ってすぐ、今まで飲んでいた紅茶よりもはるかに強い香りと味がすることに気づく。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2318
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_b2d2205b:

    # hi "Huh, it tastes different than the tea we have in school."
    hi "あれ、学校で飲む紅茶と味が違うな"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2323
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_c4ab4262:

    # li "It's a different variety, rather than the kind we've been having there. You've never tasted Orange Jaipur before?"
    li "あそこで飲むのとはまた違う種類のお茶ですよ。オレンジジャイプールを飲むのは初めてですか？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2325
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_a94411a6:

    # hi "Not… that I can remember. I usually drink coffee after all, like when we were in town. This is nice, though."
    hi "覚えてる……限りは。そもそも普段はコーヒーを飲んでるからな。この前街に行った時みたいにさ。でも、これもいけるな"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2330
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_58ed2f38:

    # "As we settle down and sip, Hanako seems to become more relaxed, or at least a bit less tense about my presence."
    "落ち着いて紅茶を飲んでいると、華子がだんだんリラックスしてきたようだ。少なくとも俺がいることに対する緊張はほぐれている気がする。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2332
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_61e4a532:

    # "We all finish our cups at about the same time, with Hanako failing rather badly at hiding her anticipation for the cake that's sitting to the side, begging to be eaten."
    "３人ともほぼ同時にそれを飲み終える。華子の脇に、食べろと言わんばかりにケーキが置いてある。華子はそのケーキへの期待を隠すことができない様子だ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2336
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_11b6b2dd:

    # "Come to think of it, I'm feeling very eager myself. First things first, though."
    "よく考えてみたら、俺だってケーキをとても楽しみにしているんだ。だけど、まず先にやるべきことがある。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2338
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_2eecae53:

    # hi "Lilly?"
    hi "リリー？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2343
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_a8c505d1:

    # li "Yes, now is good."
    li "ええ、いい頃合いですね"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2345
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_e99597ad:

    # "Each of us knowing exactly what the other means, I lean sideways and dig around in my bag for the doll I bought Hanako as Lilly gets up and retrieves her gift."
    "２人ともそれぞれが何を考えているのかよく分かっている。リリーが立ち上がって彼女の贈り物を持ってくると同時に、俺も体を横に傾けてかばんの中から華子のために買った人形を探り出す。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2347
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_35b20d6a:

    # "Hiding our gifts in our hands, we present them both on the table at the same time."
    "そして、それぞれ隠し持った贈り物を同時に机の上に置く。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2355
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_fcd65adb:

    # "Hanako silently sits looking at them for seconds on end, out of sheer surprise."
    "華子はただただ驚き、しばらくそれを見つめたまま無言で座っている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2357
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_f323351a:

    # "My little wooden doll, replete with Victorian-era dress and little hat, lies next to a light brown and fluffy stuffed bear from Lilly."
    "俺のビクトリア朝ドレスと小さな帽子に身を包んだ木製の小さな人形が、リリーの薄茶色のふっくらしたクマのぬいぐるみと並んで置かれている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2362
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_dab77af1:

    # "She clutches at her gown as she moves to speak, not taking her eyes off the modest presents."
    "華子がそのささやかなプレゼントから目を離すことなく、自分の寝巻をぎゅっとつかみながら言葉を発する。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2367
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_c92542d7:

    # ha "Th… thank you… Lilly and… Hisao…"
    ha "あ…ありがとう……リリー、それに……久夫くんも……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2381
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_c9677256:

    # "Her voice begins to crack as Lilly reaches forward, wrapping her in a soft embrace."
    "リリーが前に出て華子を柔らかく抱きしめる。華子の声がうわずり出す。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2383
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_8d7b7b7f:

    # "The sight of Hanako holding Lilly so tightly is heartwarming, so much so that I couldn't wipe the smile off my face even if I wanted to."
    "リリーにぎゅっとしがみつく華子を見て、胸の奥が暖かくなるのを感じる。俺はその光景を前に笑顔を隠したくても隠すことができない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2385
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_302497ca:

    # "As Lilly gently rests her face on Hanako's head, she speaks so quietly and softly that I can barely hear."
    "リリーが華子の頭に自分の顔を優しくあてがい、俺にはほとんど聞こえない、とても静かな柔らかい声でささやく。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2387
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_5d2b877b:

    # li "Happy birthday, Hanako."
    li "お誕生日おめでとう、華ちゃん"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2389
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_de4373e6:

    # hi "Happy birthday."
    hi "誕生日おめでとう"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2391
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_90d234c2:

    # "Hanako gives a small nod, holding on to Lilly for a time before breaking off and wiping an eye."
    "華子は小さくうなずき、しばらくリリーの胸元にすがってから体を離して目をぬぐう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2393
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_8b8b4504:

    # "I guess that for Hanako simply having someone, anyone, to be there and love her would be special. The fact that Lilly and I can now share that role for her is something I think I will always be grateful for."
    "誰かが、いや誰であっても、そばにいて愛してくれる。華子にとってはそれだけで特別なことなんだと思う。今、リリーと俺がその役割を共有している。きっと俺は、そのことをいつまでも感謝し続けるだろう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2398
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_451223be:

    # "Hanako gently takes the doll and teddy bear, holding them both to her chest as she warmly smiles."
    "華子は人形とテディベアを優しく手に取ると、穏やかな笑みを浮かべながらその両方を胸元に引き寄せる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2400
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_426beb68:

    # "For a long time, all three of us simply sit in happy silence. The quiet is not broken until Lilly's soft voice beckons."
    "長いあいだ、３人とも幸せな沈黙に包まれながら、ただ座り続ける。その沈黙はリリーの柔らかい招きの声が発せられるまで続く。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2402
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_f8822123:

    # li "Shall we have at the cake, then?"
    li "では、ケーキを食べましょうか？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2413
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_b7634a6e:

    # "Her proposal is met with two looks of unhidden anticipation."
    "リリーの提案に、俺と華子は期待を隠し切れずに答える。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2415
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_1573559b:

    # hi "No argument from me."
    hi "異議なし"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2417
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_ea2d722a:

    # ha "Okay."
    ha "うん"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2430
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_9a2e09ba:

    # hi "Phew, that was good."
    hi "ふう、うまかった"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2434
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_1b69e2e5:

    # "I contentedly sit back, both Lilly and Hanako looking just as satisfied with the food as I. It took some effort, but we managed to finish off the cake in one go."
    "すっかり満足してくつろぐ。リリーも華子も俺と同じように満足したようだ。ちょっと苦労したけど、俺たちはそのケーキを全部食べ切ることができた。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2439
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_b3328ab5:

    # ha "I don't think I could fit any more in."
    ha "私、もう食べられない"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2444
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_4b3258a4:

    # li "I think next time I'll buy a smaller cake."
    li "次回はもう少し小さなケーキを買ったほうがいいですね"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2449
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_820423fc:

    # "Hanako and I give a chuckle, but I can't help noticing that, come this time next year, we'll have graduated from Yamaku."
    "華子と俺が声を出して笑う。だけど来年の今ごろには俺たちは山久を卒業しているという事実を思わずにはいられない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2451
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_f4c7d10d:

    # "That fact is somewhat depressing, since I finally feel as if my life is starting to get back into some kind of order."
    "俺にとってはある意味がっかりする事実だ。やっと普通らしい生活に戻り始めた気がしているところなのだから。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2453
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_cbbb3103:

    # "Idly looking around Lilly's neat and orderly room, her books catch my eye once again."
    "リリーのこざっぱりした秩序ある部屋をぼんやり見回していると、再び彼女の本の山が俺の目に飛び込んでくる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2455
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_221cc495:

    # "This may be a little impetuous, but my curiosity gets the better of me. Besides, I don't think she'll mind in any case."
    "ちょっと軽はずみかもしれないけど、俺は好奇心を抑えることができない。それに、リリーだって断ったりはしないだろう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2457
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_4af6d51b:

    # hi "Hey Lilly, do you mind if I take a look at one of your books?"
    hi "なあ、リリー。リリーの本、見せてもらってもいい？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2462
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_66346526:

    # li "You're quite welcome to, Hisao."
    li "ええ、もちろんです、久夫さん"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2467
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_91eec1f1:

    # li "That said, if you can overcome two language barriers I will be quite impressed."
    li "ですけど、もし久夫さんが二つの言葉の壁を克服できたら、とても驚きですよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2469
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_1e206f19:

    # hi "Two? Braille and… oh right, English."
    hi "二つ？　点字と……ああ分かった、英語か"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2474
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_efae91a6:

    # "She gives a nod."
    "リリーがうなずく。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2476
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_e4976665:

    # hi "I knew you were studying English, but I'm still amazed that you're this proficient at it."
    hi "リリーが英語を勉強してるってのは知ってたけど、まさかここまでのレベルだとは思わなかったよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2481
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_7d138bf8:

    # li "One could say it's a perfect way to avoid people borrowing my collection."
    li "他の人が私のコレクションを借りてしまうのを防ぐ完璧な方法といえますね"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2483
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_8c21ba61:

    # "She says it in jest, but I am a little disappointed. Having all these books around me with no way of reading them feels like one big tease."
    "リリーは冗談交じりにそう言うけど、それを聞いて俺は少し失望する。周りにこれだけたくさん本があるのにそれを読むすべがないというのは、まるでからかわれているみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2485
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_521a2aab:

    # "Hanako giggles quietly as I reach over the closest pile, plucking the topmost book with only a cursory glance. 'Death on the Nile,' in large letters on the cover, is the only printed text to be seen."
    "華子が静かにくすくす笑う間、俺は一番近い本の山に手を伸ばして、ちらりと見ただけで一番上の本を取り上げる。『Death on the Nile』、表紙に大きく書かれたその文字だけが、印刷されている唯一の文字だ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2494
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_277a697d:

    # "I sit down for a while with the book open on my lap as Lilly and Hanako talk."
    "リリーと華子が話し込んでいるあいだ、俺は膝の上で本を開き、しばらく座り込む。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2496
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_68052d49:

    # "Try as I might to feel out the dots of Braille printed on each page, they seem to blend into one another and become indistinct."
    "それぞれのページに打ち付けられた点たちを感じ分けようとしても、それらはお互いに混ざり合ってしまい、俺には全く区別できないように思える。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2498
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_a48268d0:

    # "I'd thought this to be a lot easier than it actually is. With some practice though, I could see someone with a better sense of touch than mine managing to read at a pretty fast speed."
    "もっと簡単なものだと思っていた。だけど多少訓練すれば、俺より優れた触覚の持ち主なら点字をかなりの速さで読み取れるようになるだろう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2511
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_90bc09d6:

    # "Noticing a silence that had probably begun earlier, I look up from the dotted pages to see Lilly smiling as Hanako sips another cup of tea."
    "たぶんさっきから続いていたであろう沈黙に気づいて点字のページから目を上げると、華子はおかわりした紅茶を飲み、リリーは微笑んでいる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2513
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_9dbd43ff:

    # hi "Is something wrong?"
    hi "なんかおかしい？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2518
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_16ad9b4b:

    # li "Quite the opposite, your curiosity's quite endearing."
    li "いいえ、その逆です。久夫さんの探究心はとても愛らしいですよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2520
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_a57ae9d4:

    # "I am inordinately pleased by the praise, though I can feel my cheeks heating up a little."
    "その言葉を聞いて、俺は異常に嬉しくなる。同時に自分の頬が少し熱くなるのを感じたけど。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2522
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_dc80870f:

    # hi "Thanks, but I don't know how else I could act."
    hi "ありがと。でも、他にやり方が分かんないよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2527
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_ff0ebb4d:

    # li "To be honest, I wasn't altogether sure of how you saw us, since you were a new transfer student from another school."
    li "本当のことを言うと、別の学校から転入してきた久夫さんが私たちをどう見ていたのか、よく分からなかったんです"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2534
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_b31eb343:

    # li "If you'd pitied us, I would have been quite offended."
    li "もし久夫さんが私たちに同情の目を向けていたら、私はきっととても傷ついたと思います"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2539
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_63122353:

    # "There's a certain edge to Lilly's voice, one that I'd quite possibly place as pride. Glancing over to Hanako, she seems even more subdued than usual, looking towards Lilly rather than me."
    "リリーの声が鋭さを帯びる。きっとそれは彼女のプライドから来ているに違いない。華子をちらっと見ると、彼女はいつもよりも感情を押し殺した様子で、俺ではなくリリーの方を見ている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2541
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_4b6d0e3a:

    # hi "I wouldn't worry about that. Considering the position I've found myself in, I'm perhaps the last person that should be dispensing pity on others."
    hi "心配ないよ。俺だって自分の置かれた立場を考えたら、他人の同情なんかできるわけないし"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2543
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_e4e14992:

    # hi "My parents' first interactions with me after my heart attack… I wouldn't want anyone to see that kind of face."
    hi "俺が発作を起こした後、俺に最初に会いに来た時の親の顔なんかさ……あんな顔、誰にも見てほしくないよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2549
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_bc4df9d5:

    # "I catch myself from going any further, but not soon enough. Both of the girls seem to be put off, Lilly especially."
    "これ以上話すのはやめようと自重するけど、もう手遅れだ。目の前の２人とも、特にリリーが、困惑した様子を見せる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2555
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_c963a449:

    # li "I'm… sorry. I shouldn't have gone that far…"
    li "ごめん……なさい。そんなに深く聞くつもりは……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2563
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_2198c715:

    # "An awkward silence reigns for a few beats, thankfully ended as Lilly's head perks up in a gesture I've come to easily recognize."
    "少しの間、気まずい沈黙がその場を支配する。ありがたいことに、俺も簡単に気づけるほどのしぐさでリリーがはっと顔を上げて、沈黙が終わる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2565
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_108f0dd0:

    # hi "Hear something?"
    hi "なんか聞こえる？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2570
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_251af332:

    # li "The door…"
    li "ドアが……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2583
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_d523cca1:

    # "Everyone looks towards it, trusting in Lilly's senses. True enough, the door handle shudders and turns, a flash of yellow and black slipping through."
    "リリーの言葉を頼りに、皆いっせいにドアに注目する。彼女の言う通り、ドアのレバーが音を立てながら回り、黄色と黒の閃光が部屋に滑り込んでくる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2597
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_3d640b09:

    # aki "Akira Satou is in the house! Happy birthday, Hanako!"
    aki "砂藤晃、ここに参上！　誕生日おめでとう、華子！"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2602
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_83a15294:

    # ha "Ah… thank you…"
    ha "えっと……ありがとうございます……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2608
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_361021ff:

    # "Akira takes a seat at the table as she plops her tall bag beside her. She has her trademark boisterous air about her, making no small deal of her entrance."
    "脇に背の高い袋をどさりと置きながら、晃さんが机のそばに座る。トレードマークである陽気な空気を振り撒いて、登場するのも大騒ぎだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2613
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_2a8db01d:

    # "Hanako clutches her gown to steady herself, but doesn't appear too shaken after she settles down. I guess she must have met Akira before, not a huge surprise given how close Akira and Lilly are."
    "寝巻をぎゅっと掴んでいる華子も、落ち着きを取り戻すにつれ震えがおさまる。彼女は前にも晃さんに会ったことがあるはずだ。晃さんとリリーの関係がどれだけ近いかを考えれば別に驚くことじゃない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2615
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_1149cfe5:

    # "Akira doesn't seem to be the least bit put off by Hanako's scarring, despite its prominence, but she also doesn't pull any punches in how she acts despite Hanako's shy nature."
    "晃さんは、ひときわ目立つ華子のやけどの跡を微塵も気にしていない様子だ。だけど同時に、華子のシャイな性格に気を使っているようなそぶりも全くない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2620
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_8c7b4aa8:

    # li "I thought you said you'd have to work, Akira. Did you manage to get off for a while?"
    li "姉さん、お仕事があるって言っていた気がするけれど。しばらく抜け出すことができたの？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2626
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_53f47f02:

    # aki "Eh, kinda. I feel bad about ditching the guys doing overtime, so I gotta get back soon."
    aki "あー、まあね。残業してる連中をほっとくのも気が引けるから、すぐ帰らなきゃいけないけど"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2631
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_16b74a2b:

    # aki "But I felt bad about not coming to your cute little Hanako's birthday too, so for now I'm here."
    aki "でも、可愛い華子お嬢ちゃんの誕生日に来ないのも気が引けてさ、それで今こうしてここにいるわけさ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2636
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_4bf06053:

    # "She grins widely at Hanako, who flowers into a full blush as she pins her eyes downwards toward her lap. Her mouth seems to widen and retract over and over, as if she was trying to suppress a smile out of embarrassment."
    "晃さんが華子に向かってにんまり笑うと、華子がかあっと赤くなりながら自分の膝に目を落とす。恥ずかしくて笑顔を抑えようとしているのか、何度も口を開いたり閉じたりしている様子だ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2638
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_7dbff2e2:

    # "It's a little strange how her reaction seems to be more immediate and forceful than when she's embarrassed by the way she looks. All she manages to give in return is a tiny nod, failing to hide her appreciation to any great extent."
    "その反応が、自分の外見を恥ずかしがるときよりも素早く力強い反応に見えて、ちょっと奇妙だ。華子はお礼に小さくうなずくのがやっとだったけど、それには感謝の気持ちが余すところなく現れている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2640
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_5ea654a9:

    # "Not that many people give her positive attention, I suppose. It makes me respect how well Akira can handle her, making her so happy, compared to what little I could do."
    "きっと、華子の注意を前向きな意味で引くことができる人は数えるほどしかいないだろう。俺に比べてはるかにうまく華子を扱い喜ばせることができる晃さんを尊敬してしまう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2645
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_35d5bfae:

    # aki "Now then, before I go…"
    aki "さてと、帰る前に……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2649
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_b780b25f:

    # "She reaches into the bag beside her and grandly displays its contents."
    "晃さんは脇に置いてある袋に手を伸ばすと、その中身を華々しく披露する。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2657
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_91e0c4a1:

    # "Out come two large glass bottles, both with long French names on the labels."
    "それは二本のガラス瓶で、その両方とも貼られているラベルに長ったらしいフランス語名が書かれている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2662
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_9ed318b5:

    # "Hanako's expression is an odd mix of surprise and curiosity, and I suspect mine's no different. Lilly, not seeing the proceedings, is oblivious to what's going on."
    "華子が驚きと好奇心の混じったおかしな表情を見せる。たぶん俺も同じ表情をしているだろう。ことの成り行きを見ていないリリーは、なにが起こっているのかに気づいていない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2667
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_98279e99:

    # ha "Akira… this isn't…"
    ha "晃さん……これはちょっと……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2672
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_d78581af:

    # li "What is it?"
    li "何ですか？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2674
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_b9681f1d:

    # hi "Wine. One red, one white."
    hi "ワインだよ。赤一本、白一本"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2679
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_10b721d3:

    # li "A-Akira! That's…!"
    li "ね、姉さん！　それは……！"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2690
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_5e6a7f9f:

    # aki "Relax, relax, it's not like Shizune's here to scold you."
    aki "まあまあ。静音がここにいて責め立てるわけでもあるまいし"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2692
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_5943ab32:

    # hi "Lilly has a point, that's not exactly allowed on campus."
    hi "リリーの言う通りですよ。校内の飲酒は禁止です"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2694
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_8b8f2eef:

    # hi "…or anywhere, really. We're still short of the legal drinking age, remember?"
    hi "……というか、校外でもですよ。俺たちがまだ未成年だってこと忘れたんですか？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2699
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_3bdb21ba:

    # aki "Rich words for someone practically drooling as he examines a bottle."
    aki "よく言うよ、ボトルを持ったまま飲みたくてしょうがないって顔してるくせに"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2701
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_87b41be4:

    # "She got me there. I am genuinely interested in trying some, even just a little. While Hanako may not be handling one herself, her look does tell me that she's far from opposed to the notion as well."
    "一本取られたな。俺は純粋にほんの少しだけでも試してみたい。華子はボトルを手にしてはいないけど、反対からはほど遠い気持ちであることはその表情から明らかだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2706
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_8d7a892a:

    # "Lilly rubs her forehead, giving up the fight that she knows Akira would win due to simply not caring enough about those funny 'rules' and 'regulations.'"
    "リリーは手で額をさすり、晃さんへの反論をあきらめる。おかしな『規則』と『規制』など気にも留めない晃さんには何を言っても無駄だとわかっているんだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2711
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_d8af269e:

    # li "Just don't breathe a word of this to anyone in the school, please. I beg of you."
    li "校内の誰にもそんなこと絶対に言わないでね。お願いだから"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2716
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_d6bc784e:

    # aki "I'm not stupid, don't worry."
    aki "あたしもバカじゃないよ。心配すんなって"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2721
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_f08e18d6:

    # aki "That said, I gotta get back to work pretty soon."
    aki "そうだ、もうすぐ仕事に戻んなきゃ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2726
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_aead2be2:

    # li "So soon? But you only just arrived…"
    li "そんなに早く？　今来たばかりなのに……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2731
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_571688e4:

    # aki "Sorry, Lilly. Good to see you two again though, and you Hisao."
    aki "ごめんよ、リリー。でも、２人の顔を見れてよかったよ。久夫、君もね"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2733
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_b0895212:

    # hi "See you later, then."
    hi "じゃあ、また"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2735
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_3411f5c5:

    # ha "Um… g-goodbye… Akira…"
    ha "あの……さ、さようなら……晃さん……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2744
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_976f2e57:

    # "She levers herself up with a grunt and waltzes out of the room, leaving us alone with the two items on the table."
    "晃さんはよいしょと立ち上がると、俺たちと机上の二本の品をその場に残して部屋の外へと躍り出る。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2755
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_d480160c:

    # hi "…Interesting."
    hi "……面白いな"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2761
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_4b24f138:

    # "Lilly gives a nervous giggle at her sister's antics as Hanako takes a wine bottle."
    "ワインボトルを手に取る華子の横で、リリーが姉のおふざけに苦笑する。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2766
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_33e1c2d5:

    # ha "So…"
    ha "それで……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2768
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_548e3224:

    # hi "What do you think, Lilly?"
    hi "どう思う、リリー？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2773
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_57e69965:

    # "She rests her elbow on the table and pinches the bridge of her nose, thinking things through. She really doesn't seem to be able to keep up with her sister."
    "リリーは机にひじをついて、鼻筋を押さえながらどうすべきか考えている。自分の姉の思考に全く付いていけないようだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2780
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_475dc263:

    # li "Well… it's already here. We may as well have some."
    li "そうですね……もうここにあるのだし。少しいただきましょうか"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2782
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_1ed1d01c:

    # "No sooner does she say it that I take a quick glance around the room for glasses."
    "リリーがそう言うと同時に、俺は部屋の中を見回してコップのありかを探す。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2789
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_bd952d96:

    # "A small groan above me reminds me that Lilly retired to rest on her bed for a bit a few minutes ago."
    "頭上からの小さなうめき声を聞いて、俺はリリーが数分前に少しベッドで体を休めるために飲酒を切り上げたのを思い出す。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2791
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_48d8e434:

    # "Almost completely drained of energy, I manage to stand up and drag myself to the side of the bed, sitting down and leaning my back against it."
    "精根尽き果てた俺は、ようやく立ち上がると身を引きずるようにベッドの脇まで移動して、そこにもたれかかるように座り込む。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2803
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_87f991d4:

    # hi "Good God."
    hi "なんてこった"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2810
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_5414d71e:

    # li "Eugh…"
    li "うぇ……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2812
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_f0d2de39:

    # "Lilly's groan sounds lifeless."
    "リリーのうめき声は生気を失っているかのようだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2814
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_097e65fa:

    # hi "Too much to drink?"
    hi "飲み過ぎじゃないか？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2819
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_0c425f2a:

    # li "My head hurts."
    li "頭が痛いです"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2821
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_2423825f:

    # hi "Yeah, too much to drink."
    hi "ほら、やっぱり飲みすぎだよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2823
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_3ef68f50:

    # "I rest my head back and idly stare at the ceiling. What an unmitigated disaster."
    "俺は頭を後ろにもたれかけ、ぼんやりと天井を見つめる。まったく、なんて災難だ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2825
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_ec61ff3f:

    # "Like proper idiots, we all drank the night away with one glass after another. Hanako simply fell to the side asleep, and it's a miracle I don't feel as ill as Lilly."
    "世間のバカがやるみたいに、俺たちは次々とグラスを空けながら夜を過ごした。華子はただ横に倒れ込んで寝てしまい、俺はリリーほどには気分が悪くない自分を奇跡だと感じている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2830
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_a4ebaa90:

    # li "Hey, Hisao? I'm sorry about today. I… didn't think this would happen."
    li "ねえ、久夫さん？　今夜のこと、すみません。こんな……ことになるなんて"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2832
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_3100de6a:

    # hi "It's fine, Lilly. To tell the truth, I had a lot of fun today."
    hi "大丈夫だよ、リリー。正直、すごく楽しかったし"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2837
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_de0bfc95:

    # li "Really?"
    li "本当ですか？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2839
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_4c933fe5:

    # hi "Mmm. I think Hanako did too. No, she certainly did."
    hi "うーん。たぶん華子もそうだよ。いや、絶対"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2844
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_259aa7c3:

    # "There's a short silence, before another groan resounds from the supine Lilly."
    "短い沈黙の後、仰向けのリリーが再びうめき声を上げる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2846
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_57b93a1c:

    # hi "You okay?"
    hi "大丈夫か？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2851
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_f0c19eef:

    # li "As you said, I just drank too much. What's the time?"
    li "久夫さんの言う通り、飲みすぎました。何時ですか？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2853
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_faea1407:

    # hi "The time? Uh, it's…"
    hi "時間？　ええと、今は……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2855
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_06d211d2:

    # "I quickly look at my wristwatch, its numerals barely legible in the gloom."
    "俺はすばやく腕時計を見る。視界がぼやけて数字をほとんど読み取れない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2857
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_d13148a4:

    # hi "About midnight."
    hi "夜中過ぎだ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2862
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_217b371a:

    # li "Curfew's in effect, then."
    li "では、もう門限は過ぎていますね"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2864
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_8cb85026:

    # hi "Yeah, guessed as much. We'll all have to sleep here for tonight."
    hi "ああ、そうだろうな。今夜はここで寝なきゃな"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2866
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_09c64c6f:

    # "As soon as I say it, I hear the sheets moving as Lilly starts to sit up."
    "それを言い終わると同時に、俺は起き上がろうとするリリーからシーツがずり落ちる音を聞く。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2871
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_9beb4157:

    # li "Hanako…"
    li "華ちゃん……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2873
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_561e2508:

    # hi "Ah, no, go back to sleep, don't try to get up."
    hi "あっ、いや、寝てろって。起きなくていいから"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2878
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_3687e298:

    # li "Hisao, I have to…"
    li "久夫さん、私が……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2880
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_31500935:

    # hi "You're in worse shape than me by any stretch. Get some rest."
    hi "どう見ても俺よりリリーの方が具合悪そうだぞ。ちょっと休めって"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2885
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_d12512e5:

    # li "But what about…"
    li "でも、華ちゃんが……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2887
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_292495a9:

    # hi "I'll grab some spare blankets and put them over her, don't worry."
    hi "俺が予備の毛布を華子にかけとくから。心配すんなって"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2892
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_4df4ef4f:

    # "As I give a deep yawn and stand to retrieve them, I hear her lie back down with a soft thud."
    "大あくびをしながら毛布を取るために立ち上がると、柔らかな衣擦れの音を立てながらリリーがまた横になる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2894
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_10354753:

    # li "Thank you, Hisao."
    li "ありがとうございます、久夫さん"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2896
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_9deea8c4:

    # hi "No problem, it's the least I can do. You look outright wasted."
    hi "いいよ。こんなことぐらいしかできないからな。リリーも完全に酔っぱらってるな"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2898
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_da5ce0bd:

    # li "I'm not… wasted… just a little bit… tired."
    li "酔ってなんか……いませんよぅ……ちょっと疲れた……らけでぇ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2900
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_d44a3463:

    # "She starts pouting, a slight slur beginning to distort her words as the alcohol takes hold of her again. I grab a couple of blankets rolled up at the end of her bed."
    "リリーが頬を膨らませ始める。また彼女に酔いが回り、ろれつが回らなくなってきている。俺はベッドの隅に丸めて置いてある毛布を何枚か掴む。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2902
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_fc431f4b:

    # "Quietly walking over to Hanako, I carefully lay the blankets over her peacefully sleeping figure, making sure not to wake her up."
    "静かに華子の元に歩み寄り、起こさないように気をつけながら穏やかに眠る華子の体に毛布をかける。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2904
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_388eacca:

    # "The thick smell of alcohol coming off her breath makes me doubt she'd wake up no matter what I did, though."
    "もっとも、こんなに酒臭い華子に俺が何をしても彼女が起きることはないだろう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2906
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_2cf7db94:

    # "I stand and take one last measure of the room."
    "その場に立って、部屋の状況を最終確認する。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2910
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_ff5052ce:

    # "Two girls, both very drunk, and one guy sleeping overnight with them in the female students' dorm. What a scandal that'd be if it broke out."
    "泥酔した２人の少女に、女子寮で彼女たちと一晩一緒に寝る野郎が１人。こんなことがばれたら大スキャンダルになることは必至だ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2912
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_ff1e96e6:

    # "As I move to sit back down at the side of the bed, I steal one last glance at Lilly."
    "ベッドの脇に戻りそこに座りながら、最後に一度だけリリーをちらりと見る。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2914
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_ce41eb06:

    # "Her sprawling, disheveled figure lies resting peacefully, slightly turned to the side."
    "手足を投げ出しただらしない格好でほんの少し横を向いて、穏やかに身を横たえている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2916
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_4c170dc0:

    # "I crouch down to get a better look."
    "リリーがよく見えるよう彼女のほうに身をかがませる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2926
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_ccc7789a:

    # "Her white skin blends in with the white pillow of the bed, a look of slumber-born peacefulness on her face."
    "リリーの白い肌がベッド上の枕の白に溶け込み、彼女の顔にはまどろみから来る安らかな表情が浮かんでいる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2928
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_d6b51eb8:

    # "Usually she seems so confident and forward, always there and caring for Hanako. Now, though, she seems painfully delicate."
    "普段は自信に満ちて、前向きで、華子の面倒だってしっかり見ているリリーだけど、今の彼女は痛々しいほど繊細に見える。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2930
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_efb604ed:

    # "I think back to Hanako's presents."
    "俺は、華子が受け取ったプレゼントのことを思い返す。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2932
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_898b4ff3:

    # "I thought it'd be a nice occasion for her, but I'd hardly expected it to be so moving."
    "華子にとって素晴らしい機会になるだろうと予想はしていたけど、こんなに感動的だとは思いもしなかった。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2934
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_ae88318f:

    # "One birthday after another, year after year."
    "誕生日が来るたびに、毎年毎年。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2936
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_8b82fed0:

    # "Just she and Lilly, all alone."
    "華子とリリー、２人っきり。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2938
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_747e0b22:

    # "…I guess it wasn't just the presents she liked."
    "……きっと、華子が喜んだのはプレゼントのせいだけじゃない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2943
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_222a138b:

    # "Resigning myself to an uncomfortable sleep, I sit down at the side of the bed once again and rest my tired arms beside me."
    "俺は心地の悪い眠りを受け入れるため再びベッドの脇に座り、疲れた腕を体の横にだらりと垂らす。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2945
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_368d5020:

    # li "Hey, Hisao."
    li "ねえ、久夫さん"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2947
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_e3f0d902:

    # "Lilly's voice is so quiet I can barely hear it. She must be on the verge of sleep."
    "リリーがほとんど聞こえないぐらいの小さな声で俺を呼ぶ。もう半分寝ているに違いない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2952
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_eb28cbfe:

    # hi "Yeah?"
    hi "なんだ？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2957
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_58cff27e:

    # li "Thank you."
    li "ありがとうございます"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2959
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_72e48d84:

    # hi "Thank you? For what?"
    hi "ありがとう？　何が？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2961
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_41588125:

    # li "For being here."
    li "ここにいてくれて"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2963
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_bad6fc01:

    # hi "…That's okay."
    hi "……いいよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2968
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_ef204385:

    # "As I hear a deep breath, it's obvious Lilly's gone to sleep."
    "深い寝息を聞き、リリーが完全に眠ってしまったことを知る。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2970
translate jp a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_11bc6d56:

    # "After closing my eyes, it doesn't take long for slumber to take me as well."
    "俺も目を閉じると、ほどなく眠りに落ちる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2985
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_43b7d705:

    # mystery "Hisao?"
    mystery "久夫さん？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2987
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_660c9db3:

    # mystery "Hisao, are you…?"
    mystery "久夫さん、大丈……？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2989
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_dbb266a5:

    # "The soft, barely audible voice lingering in my ears slowly wakes me. I wish I could be awoken like this more often."
    "柔らかい、ほとんど聞こえないぐらいの小さな声が俺の耳をくすぐり、俺はゆっくり目を覚ます。いつもこういう目覚めだったらいいのに。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2991
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_620b629a:

    # "With a mumble, I slowly open my…"
    "まどろみながら、俺はゆっくりと目を……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3013
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_2177d4cb:

    # "Taken by surprise at the face hovering curiously mere millimeters from mine, I make our heads collide with a harsh thud. The impact of our foreheads causes both of us to fall backwards and yelp in pain, Lilly sounding more like a squeak toy than a person."
    "目と鼻の先で物珍しそうに様子をうかがうリリーに驚いて、俺は大きな音を立ててリリーに頭をぶつけてしまう。衝撃で２人してひっくり返り、痛みに悲鳴を上げる。リリーのは悲鳴というより、音の出る玩具みたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3015
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_328d62cb:

    # hi "Ow, ow, ow."
    hi "あいててて"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3019
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_2dd1abac:

    # "I slowly rub my forehead with one hand, supporting myself with the other. Lilly lies a few feet ahead doing just the same, her face obviously pained."
    "俺は片方の手で自分の体を支えながら、もう片方の手でゆっくりと額をさする。リリーは少し離れたところで、明らかに痛がっている表情で俺と同じことをしている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3021
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_d2928569:

    # hi "Ah… sorry. Your face was kinda close and I acted on reflex. You okay?"
    hi "うう……ごめん。リリーの顔がなんか近かったからさ、反射的に動いちゃって。大丈夫？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3028
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_40b98f79:

    # li "My head…"
    li "頭が……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3030
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_7a003701:

    # "It seems she's not actually okay. Come to think of it, I doubt that the impact alone is what's causing her head so much pain."
    "大丈夫じゃないみたいだ。よく考えたら、リリーの激しい頭痛の原因は俺とぶつかったからだけじゃないはずだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3032
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_3657c4e9:

    # hi "Hangover? You drank a fair bit, last night."
    hi "二日酔いか？　昨日の夜はすごく飲んでたからな"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3038
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_3cac2239:

    # "She silently nods in confirmation as I lever myself up."
    "俺が起き上がるあいだ、リリーが俺の言ったことを認めて静かにうなずく。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3045
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_36477042:

    # "I offer a hand to her, and help her back onto her feet. Glancing behind her, I find that Hanako's still fast asleep."
    "俺はリリーに手を差し出し、彼女が立ち上がるのを助ける。彼女の後ろをちらりと見ると、華子がまだ眠りこけている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3050
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_d160f86c:

    # li "It's not fair… I only drank as much as you did…"
    li "こんなの不公平です……久夫さんと同じくらい飲んだだけなのに……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3052
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_bfa2befd:

    # hi "That's very different from what I remember. And anyway, girls have a lower tolerance than men."
    hi "なんかそれって俺の記憶と全然違うぞ。それに、女の子は男よりもアルコール耐性が低いんだし"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3057
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_42da9e3f:

    # li "That doesn't help."
    li "そんなの慰めになりません"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3059
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_fe1c4783:

    # hi "Fine, I'll get you a glass of water. Just be careful not to trip over Hanako."
    hi "分かったよ。水くんでくるから。華子につまずかないように気を付けろよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3064
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_abf0d6f4:

    # "I rub the sleep out of my eyes, or at least some of it, as I walk to the counter. Tending to someone with a hangover isn't the way I like to spend a morning."
    "流しのほうに向かいながら、いくらかでも眠気を覚まそうと目をこする。二日酔いの誰かを介抱するなんて、あまりいい朝の過ごしかたとは言えないな。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3066
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_685e2229:

    # "It only takes a few seconds for the glass to fill, the clear water reflecting the sliver of light that makes it through the thin curtains."
    "コップに水を満たすのに数秒しかかからない。澄んだ水は薄いカーテン越しに差し込む細い光をきらきらと反射している。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3068
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_f604624b:

    # "It looks like Lilly's taken a seat on the side of the bed. I walk over to her while taking care to step over the peacefully sleeping Hanako, and place the glass into her outstretched hands."
    "リリーはベッドの脇に腰を下ろしているようだ。俺は安らかな寝息を立てる華子を踏まないように気を付けながらリリーに近寄り、彼女が伸ばした手にコップを握らせる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3075
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_58cff27e:

    # li "Thank you."
    li "ありがとうございます"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3077
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_11a6e6fb:

    # hi "No problem."
    hi "どういたしまして"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3081
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_1c6e1983:

    # "I take a seat next to her, the soft bed having a surprising amount of give."
    "俺はリリーの隣に腰掛ける。柔らかなベッドは驚くほど深く沈み込む。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3083
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_3905d9e0:

    # "She drinks slowly and methodically. A long silence passes with only Hanako's soft breathing to be heard."
    "リリーが几帳面なしぐさでゆっくり水を飲む。沈黙が長く続き、華子の柔らかな寝息だけが聞こえる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3088
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_9a3334a1:

    # "With some measure of guilt, I look at Lilly's face and attempt to read her expression. Her brow is furrowed, and she looks to be lost in thought."
    "いくばくかの罪悪感を感じながらも、俺はリリーの顔をうかがい表情を読み取ろうとする。彼女は眉間にしわを寄せ、何か考えごとをしているようだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3093
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_fc22f25c:

    # "For a moment I hesitate, but eventually place a hand on her shoulder in an attempt to reassure her. I didn't expect her to flinch rather noticeably at that, though."
    "しばらくためらったけど、俺はついに決心してリリーを元気づけようと彼女の肩に手を置く。それに対してリリーが目に見えるほどたじろいだのは予想外だったけど。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3095
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_729735e8:

    # hi "Ah, sorry. I didn't mean to—"
    hi "あっ、いや、ごめん。そんなつもりじゃなくて――"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3100
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_70090ade:

    # "Lilly quickly shakes her head, in a manner somewhat more violent than usual for her."
    "リリーが、彼女にしては激しすぎると思える様子で素早く頭を振る。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3102
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_05547475:

    # "She takes a long breath to steady herself before letting her head sink."
    "そして、自分を落ち着かせるために深呼吸をして、うなだれる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3107
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_5b37784c:

    # li "I must look terrible right now…"
    li "今の私、おかしく見えるでしょうね……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3109
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_567ffde9:

    # "I move to protest, but quickly realize that it would be futile to do so. That said, I want her to open up more."
    "それを否定しようとして、すぐにそれは無意味なことだと気づく。そうは言っても、俺は彼女にもっと心を開いて欲しいんだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3111
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_d381466d:

    # hi "If you want to talk about anything, I'm here."
    hi "相談したいことがあるなら、何でも言ってよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3116
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_64ed19d6:

    # "Lilly gives a self-deprecating snort, as if to mock her own emotions."
    "自分の感情を見下げるかのように、リリーが自嘲の笑みを漏らす。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3121
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_aa1db038:

    # li "There's just… a lot happening right now."
    li "ただ……いろいろなことがあって"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3126
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_1f982b95:

    # li "I'm sorry for being so strange recently, especially back when we were in town. Even now I'm a bit confused about everything."
    li "最近、とりわけ街から帰る時に、おかしな態度を見せてしまって、すみません。今でも少し混乱しているんです"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3128
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_d9e34bf1:

    # hi "Believe me, I know how that feels."
    hi "その気持ち分かるよ、本当に"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3133
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_fb5e6a11:

    # "She smiles wistfully, resting a cheek on the backs of her fingers."
    "リリーが思わせぶりな笑みをこぼしながら指の背に頬を乗せる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3135
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_4a86b490:

    # li "We're a couple of broken young fools, aren't we?"
    li "駄目になった２人の愚かな若者、ですね"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3137
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_83a22dc4:

    # hi "Come on, don't say that. Come graduation, we'll be back out into the real world."
    hi "おいおい、そんなこと言うなよ。ここを卒業したら、俺もリリーも実世界に戻るんだし"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3139
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_bee4722f:

    # "The real world? Sometimes I surprise myself with the way I think about things. I guess the strange, divorced feeling of Yamaku and the surrounding town compared to the outside world still hasn't become natural."
    "実世界？　俺は時々、自分の思考に驚いてしまう。外の世界と比べたときに感じる、山久と周りの町の奇妙な隔絶感に、俺はまだなじんでいないんだろう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3141
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_9fb93df1:

    # "Maybe it never will. It's strange, in hindsight; being isolated from society like this doesn't feel as bad as it probably should. A wry grin on her face, Lilly seems to share the same sense of amusement at the idea."
    "これからもなじむことはないのかもな。考えてみれば変な話だ。こんな形で社会から隔離されるのも、思ったほど悪くはない気がする。皮肉な笑みを浮かべるリリーも、俺と同じように面白さを感じているみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3143
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_72f2973e:

    # "Eventually, though, her smile drops."
    "だけど結局、リリーの顔から完全に笑みが消えてしまう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3148
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_fbb073a4:

    # li "I'll be going back to Scotland for a week or two, soon."
    li "もうすぐ私、一、二週間ほどスコットランドに戻るんです"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3150
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_0012205f:

    # hi "Is that why we had to reschedule Hanako's birthday party?"
    hi "だから華子の誕生パーティーの日を変更したのか？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3152
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_18c86061:

    # "She gives an affirmative nod."
    "リリーがそれを認めるようにうなずく。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3154
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_eee919bc:

    # hi "You'll be able to see your family again, at least. You're not looking forward to it?"
    hi "でも、少なくとも家族と再会できるんだし。楽しみじゃないの？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3159
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_a4134599:

    # li "I haven't met my family in six years. I don't even know how to act around them any more."
    li "家族とは６年間会っていません。もう、どう接していいのかさえ分からないんです"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3161
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_c0d019bb:

    # "Wait… what? My mouth hangs open as I try to process what she said."
    "ちょっと待った……何だって？　俺は口をぽかんと開けたままリリーの言ったことを理解しようとする。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3165
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_9b293399:

    # "If she's eighteen, that means she'd have been only twelve when they left. I may have seen very little of my parents, what with them both working long hours, but that's…"
    "リリーが今１８歳なら、つまり両親と離ればなれになったときはまだ１２歳ってことだ。俺だって共働きの両親と過ごす時間はそんなに多くなかった、でもリリーのは……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3167
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_a560e373:

    # "I feel utterly useless as I struggle to find some way to respond."
    "気の利いた返事を見つけようとしながら、俺は途方もない無力感に襲われる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3169
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_b5a26fb7:

    # hi "That's… but, why?"
    hi "それって……でも、何で？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3174
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_5f3014a7:

    # li "Why did they leave, or why are they inviting Akira and me back?"
    li "なぜ家族が日本を去ったのか、それとも、なぜ今になって姉さんと私が呼ばれるのか、ですか？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3176
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_0270e7b5:

    # hi "Both, I suppose."
    hi "たぶん、両方"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3181
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_e3fcc65f:

    # li "My father's business has its headquarters in Scotland, and an executive position became available for him there. In the end, he had to move permanently."
    li "父が勤める会社は本社がスコットランドにあるんです。父が取締役になったので、最終的にそこに永住しなければならなくなりました"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3183
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_c2f73d53:

    # li "My mother followed him, but Akira and I stayed in Japan for the sake of both Akira's job within the Japanese branch of my father's company, and my education."
    li "母は父に付いて行きましたが、姉さんは父の会社の日本支社に勤めるために、そして私は教育のために、日本に残ることになりました"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3188
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_5c368bc0:

    # li "As for the latter… one of my aunts is gravely sick."
    li "もう一つの質問ですが……おばが危篤になってしまって"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3190
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_b01de102:

    # hi "Ah. I'm… sorry."
    hi "えっ。それは……お気の毒に"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3195
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_219f6d4d:

    # li "Don't be. It feels strange, really. We're being summoned there for her, yet we've barely met before. I can't even remember the sound of her voice."
    li "いえ。なんだかおかしな気持ちです。私たちはおばのために呼ばれたのですが、ほとんど会ったことがないので。声さえも覚えていません"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3197
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_628028f0:

    # "Equally strange is the total lack of antipathy she feels towards her family for doing such a thing. I can't help feeling slightly humbled."
    "いや、おかしいのはそれだけじゃない。リリーはこんな仕打ちをする家族に対して何の反感も示さない。俺はなんだか恐縮してしまう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3199
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_a20c4662:

    # "That said, her wistful exterior is just hiding her emotions. Seeing her like this is depressing."
    "とはいえ、物思いに沈むリリーは自分の感情を押し殺しているだけだ。こんなリリーを見るのはつらい。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3203
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_8447abea:

    # "Knowing what to do, I lift myself off the bed. Lilly notices the bed's movements, her head perking up and her hand reaching sideways to feel where I was."
    "俺は何をすべきか思いつき、ベッドから立ち上がる。リリーがベッドの動きに気づき、はっと頭を上げながら俺を確認するために自分の横へと手を伸ばす。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3208
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_0bbd4169:

    # li "Hisao…?"
    li "久夫さん……？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3212
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_ba68fae8:

    # "I walk over to my bag, still leaning against the wall. Unbuckling the front flap and retrieving the opaque bag from within, I take the small, plain box in my hands."
    "俺は今も壁にもたれかかっている自分のかばんに歩み寄る。かばんの前面を上にめくると、中から半透明の袋を取り出し、そして小さな飾り気のない箱を手に取る。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3214
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_4c4a98b4:

    # hi "Hold your hands out, Lilly."
    hi "手を出して、リリー"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3219
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_e75e00f7:

    # "She looks surprised for a moment, but eventually acquiesces."
    "彼女はしばらく驚いた表情を見せるけど、やがて俺の言う通りにする。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3237
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_bc9cf76f:

    # "I'm amused by her look of curiosity when I place the music box into her open palms, her typically delicate way of handling it making it seem as if it were fragile enough to break if breathed on."
    "リリーの手のひらにオルゴールを置くと、物珍しそうな表情になるのが面白い。いつもの繊細な手つきで触れるのを見ていると、それがまるで息を吹きかけるだけで壊れるような華奢なもののように思えてくる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3241
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_59233d55:

    # "She wordlessly brings it in front of her face, her slender fingers feeling out its contours and patterning."
    "リリーが無言のままオルゴールを顔の前まで持っていき、その外形とつくりを細い指で感じ取る。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3243
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_b1603c02:

    # "Eventually her fingers find the recessed line between the lid and body of the box, and her thumb effortlessly pops open the lid."
    "そしてついにリリーの指が箱の本体とふたの境目を見つける。彼女の親指によって、ふたは何の苦労もなく開く。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3251
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_abbb046f:

    # "I take a seat on the bed next to her, watching her face silently and intently."
    "俺はベッド上のリリーの隣に座り、静かに、真剣に、彼女の顔を見つめる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3253
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_e06336f7:

    # "She sits completely motionless as she listens to the diminutive tinny melody, her mouth just slightly open."
    "ちっぽけな金属音の旋律に耳を傾けるあいだ、リリーはぴくりともせず座り続ける。ただ、彼女の口がほんの少しだけ開いている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3278
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_fae40668:

    # "It takes a long while before she closes the lid with a small snap, bringing the curtain down on the miniature performance playing in her hands."
    "長い時間が過ぎた後、リリーは小さな音をたてて箱のふたを閉じる。彼女の手の中の小さな演奏会に幕が下ろされる瞬間。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3280
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_bc92fa40:

    # "The smile on her face, gentle and wistful, shows that I made the right decision."
    "その優しく哀愁に満ちた笑顔は、俺が正しい決断をしたことの表れだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3282
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_274d89be:

    # hi "Think of it as a going away present for your trip to Scotland."
    hi "スコットランドへの旅の餞別だと思ってくれ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3287
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_9ba32b45:

    # li "I will…"
    li "ええ……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3297
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_20097bca:

    # "A restless shuffling can be heard from the floor in front of us, the sound having woken Hanako."
    "その時、俺とリリーの前の床でがさがさとせわしない音がする。華子が目を覚ます音だ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3309
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_ed5f27ec:

    # "She climbs out of the blankets I put over her, looking befuddled and wiping the sleep from her eyes."
    "華子は昨日俺がかけた毛布からはい出すと、ぼーっと前を見つめ、眠気を払うために目をこする。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3311
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_40e9e54d:

    # hi "I see you're finally up."
    hi "やっと起きたな"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3316
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_936a2342:

    # ha "Hmm? What?"
    ha "うぅん？　何？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3321
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_fec3b271:

    # "Hanako looks around the room with her eyes only half open, her mind far from being as awake as her body. Her dazed state makes me and Lilly chuckle."
    "華子が半分目を閉じたまま部屋の中を見回す。体は起きても頭の中はまだ寝ているようだ。そんな華子の寝ぼけ姿を見て、俺とリリーはくすくすと笑う。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3329
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_48bc9480:

    # "As Lilly gets off the bed and tends to Hanako, I take one last look around the room."
    "リリーがベッドから立ち上がって華子をいたわる。俺は最後にもう一度部屋の中を見回す。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3331
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_4c62e9da:

    # hi "I guess I'd better get going, then. There'll be questions if I am seen leaving the girls' dormitories in the morning."
    hi "じゃあ、俺はもう出てった方がいいな。女子寮からの朝帰りなんて、誰かに見られたら質問攻めにあっちゃうだろうし"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3336
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_2650b55a:

    # li "Goodbye, Hisao."
    li "さようなら、久夫さん"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3341
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_713b3435:

    # ha "Oh… goodbye."
    ha "あの……さようなら"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3343
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_6e028f92:

    # "I stand and walk to the door, picking up my somewhat lighter bag along the way."
    "俺は立ち上がって少し軽くなったかばんを手に取ると、ドアに向かって歩き出す。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3348
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_00934ed0:

    # "After I leave the room and enter the hallway, though, I hear Lilly's footsteps behind me."
    "だけど部屋から廊下に出た時、背後からリリーの足音が聞こえてくる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3350
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_784b50e4:

    # hi "Hmm? What's wrong?"
    hi "ん？　どうした？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3360
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_f91c7120:

    # "Without a word, she strides up to me. I freeze as I feel her hand slide onto my cheek, seemingly every nerve taking in the feeling of her fingers and palm upon it."
    "何も言わず、リリーは俺のほうに体を伸ばす。彼女の手を自分の頬に感じ、俺の体が固まる。それは、俺の頬の全神経が彼女の指と手のひらを捉えているかのような感覚。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3364
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_a4320b3c:

    # "Immediately after, her face slowly moves next to mine, a light, momentary touch of her lips brushing against my other cheek."
    "その直後、リリーの顔が俺の顔に近づく。軽く、ほんのひと時だけ、彼女の唇が俺のもう一方の頬に触れる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3366
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_f99ee165:

    # "For a moment, everything seems to stand still. I absentmindedly bring my fingers to my cheek, as if to try and recapture that fleeting feeling."
    "しばらくのあいだ、時が止まる。俺はぼんやりとしながら、そのはかない感覚を取り戻そうとするかのように頬に手を当てる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3368
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_5e04a1b9:

    # hi "Lilly…"
    hi "リリー……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3373
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_9fc830fc:

    # li "That's my thank you, Hisao."
    li "私からのお礼です、久夫さん"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3375
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_6f205422:

    # hi "Thank you…?"
    hi "お礼……？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3380
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_d1e1b050:

    # li "For your present. Have a nice day in school."
    li "プレゼントの。よい一日を"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3389
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_9a2629a1:

    # "And with that, she disappears behind her door and gently closes it, the muffled voices of her and Hanako audible through it much as they were yesterday night."
    "そう言い残して、リリーがドアの向こうに消え、ドアが優しく閉じられる。彼女と華子のくぐもった声が昨日の夜と同じ調子で聞こえてくる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3391
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3393
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_b5405bcf:

    # "…I think I'd be hard pressed not to have a nice day, after that."
    "……こんなことを経験した日が、いい日にならないわけないじゃないか。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3398
translate jp a2_lilly_the_day_after_3aeb9a27:

    # "I walk away with a certain spring to my step. I think there were some people around that glanced at me emerging from the girl's dormitory building, but I find it difficult to care."
    "俺は軽やかな足取りでその場を去る。女子寮から出てくる俺をちらりと見た人が何人かいた気がするけど、そんなもの気にするほうが難しい。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3411
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_56656f40:

    # mi "Hicchan~."
    mi "ひっちゃ～ん"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3413
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_f1e2ae52:

    # hi "Go away."
    hi "あっちいけよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3415
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_56656f40_1:

    # mi "Hicchan~."
    mi "ひっちゃ～ん"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3417
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_0fff2552:

    # hi "Leave me alone."
    hi "ほっといてくれ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3419
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_918ac9f9:

    # mi "Come on, Hicchan~."
    mi "ちょっと、ひっちゃんてば～"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3421
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_575c307b:

    # hi "Hmph, let me sleep."
    hi "だから、寝かせといてくれってのに"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3423
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_9db5c6b2:

    # "After two nights of not being able to sleep at all, the last thing I want is to be woken when I finally manage to."
    "二晩の不眠を経た後の俺が最も嫌うことといえば、こうしてようやく眠りにつこうとしている時に誰かに叩き起こされることだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3425
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_406f8c63:

    # "It may be the last period of class, with a textbook as my pillow, but I'll take whatever sleep I can get by this point."
    "たぶん今は最後の授業中だろう。教科書を枕にしているけど、今となっては眠れるならどんな睡眠だってかまわない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3427
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_bea5a7a0:

    # mi "See Hicchan, even Shicchan wants you to get up~!"
    mi "ほら、ひっちゃん。しっちゃんだって起きてほしいんだってさ～！"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3429
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_d1af3f3c:

    # "I don't care what Shizune wants, leave me alone."
    "静音のことなんかどうでもいいよ。ほっといてくれ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3431
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_acc3c830:

    # mi "Geez, Hicchan, I'll just have to wake…"
    mi "もう、ひっちゃんってば、じゃあ、強引に起こさないと……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3433
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_a50f2a4c:

    # "Wait, Misha's going to…?"
    "ん、待て、ミーシャが何か……？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3435
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_00c1be2e:

    # mi "…you…"
    mi "……ね……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3437
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_c46960eb:

    # "This is bad!"
    "ヤバい！"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3445
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_10d0fe90:

    # hi "I'M UP!, I'M UP! YOU DON'T… have to…"
    hi "起きた！　起きた！　起こさなく……ても……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3447
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_08a1c4fb:

    # "I can feel my face flowering into a scarlet red blush."
    "自分の顔が真っ赤に上気しているのがはっきりと分かる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3449
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_d2b084cd:

    # "The students still in class are sitting bolt upright and staring at the shouting fool who was sleeping just moments before."
    "授業中の周りの生徒たちは今でも背筋をぴんと伸ばしたまま席に座り、ついさっきまで寝ていた騒がしいバカをじろりと見ている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3451
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_5ffc9abc:

    # hi "…Dammit."
    hi "……くそっ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3456
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_fa79cdcc:

    # "I let my head smack back down on the table with a noticeable thud."
    "俺は頭を振り降ろし、ごつんと音をたてながら机に額を打ちつける。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3461
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_2272a033:

    # mi "Wahahahahaha~!"
    mi "わははははは～！"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3463
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_db9748ca:

    # "Misha's trademark uncontrolled laughter reverberates through the classroom."
    "ミーシャのトレードマークである抑制不能な笑い声が教室中に響き渡る。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3476
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_057a3cf7:

    # "As I turn my mournful eyes to the bespectacled Shizune beside her, she carefully adjusts her glasses, desperately trying to maintain a look of serious disapproval."
    "ミーシャのそばにいる眼鏡姿の静音に悲しみの目を向けると、彼女は眼鏡の位置をくいっと直し、必死になって俺への真剣な非難の表情を保とうとしている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3478
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_bf45b8b6:

    # "Narrowing my eyes, I can see the badly-hidden grin spreading across her face."
    "よく見ると、顔のニヤつきは隠し切れていない様子だ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3480
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_fbf62840:

    # hi "Et tu, Shizune?"
    hi "静音よ、お前もか？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3485
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_8bc5c30d:

    # "Shizune looks away quickly as she crosses her arms tightly, barely on the edge of her control."
    "静音はこらえきれなくなった様子で腕を固く組むと素早くそっぽを向く。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3490
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_c37bf51c:

    # mi "Wahahahahahaha~!"
    mi "わはははははは～！"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3492
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_87867d37:

    # "Misha's laughter doubles in volume as she glances at Shizune. All I can do is drag my hand down my face in resignation."
    "ミーシャが静音をちらりと見て二倍の音量で笑う。俺はあきらめの表情で頭を垂れることしかできない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3494
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_c1f7f998:

    # hi "You two…"
    hi "２人とも……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3499
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_75ccbc9c:

    # mi "Who was the one who slept in class, Hicchan~?"
    mi "授業中に寝てたの誰だっけ、ひっちゃ～ん？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3501
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_20a3410f:

    # hi "Yeah, yeah, it was me."
    hi "はいはい、俺ですよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3506
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_2db9ec3b:

    # mi "Poor Shicchan was having a fit trying to wake you up. Weren't you?"
    mi "かわいそうなしっちゃんはひっちゃんを起こそうと骨折ってたんだから。ねえ？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3511
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_5705ffaf:

    # "I move my eyes back to the standoffish Shizune, who with a single huff of confirmation returns to looking away with her arms crossed."
    "俺は冷淡な表情の静音に目を戻す。静音は腕を組んで、追い打ちをかけるようにふんっと鼻を鳴らして再びそっぽを向く。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3513
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_27d33e03:

    # hi "Why was Shizune trying to wake me up?"
    hi "なんで静音が俺を起こそうとするんだよ？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3518
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_40cc0f51:

    # mi "Shicchan wanted to give you the handouts the substitute teacher gave out while Hicchan was sleeping."
    mi "しっちゃんは、ひっちゃんが寝てるあいだに代理の先生が配ったプリントを渡したかったのよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3520
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_2fe13430:

    # hi "Handouts?"
    hi "プリント？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3528
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_07b92199:

    # "I suddenly find two sheets of paper thrust down in front of my face."
    "その時突然、俺の目の前にプリントが二枚突き出される。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3534
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_a4388b8f:

    # "Following the hand holding them, I see the still-pouting figure looking down at me with a distinct scowl. I guess I really am in the wrong here."
    "プリントを持つ手に沿って視線を這わせると、俺をぎろりと見下ろすふくれっ面の人物の姿がそこにある。この状況は非常にまずい気がする。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3536
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_9a4acbaa:

    # hi "…Ah. Um, sorry about that."
    hi "……へえ。ええと、悪かったよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3540
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_9473f1f5:

    # "No dice. Her irritated face still holds. I clasp my hands together and flick my head downwards in apology."
    "ダメか。静音はまだいらついた表情をしている。俺は両手を合わせると頭を下に振って謝罪する。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3542
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_03ff4492:

    # hi "Very, very sorry."
    hi "本当に、本当に、すみませんでした"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3554
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_ebdef7f4:

    # "She huffs and simply drops the papers on the desk."
    "静音は立腹したまま、ただプリントを俺の机の上に落とす。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3556
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_4bf99ed5:

    # hi "Damn."
    hi "くっそー"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3562
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_31757b6a:

    # "I look up over my hands to see Shizune and Misha signing frantically to each other, a look of frustration on Shizune's face."
    "俺は自分の手の向こう側で狂ったように手話を交わしている静音とミーシャを見上げる。静音は相当いらついているようだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3567
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_b33ba1f7:

    # shi "…!"
    shi "……！"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3569
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_67dec14e:

    # "It looks to be less of a dialogue and more of a tirade, punctuated with sidelong glances at me. To say it's unsettling is an understatement."
    "会話というよりは糾弾演説の様相で、時々それを中断して横目で俺を見る。その様子は見ていて冷や冷やするどころじゃない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3571
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_aabbd89d:

    # hi "Um…"
    hi "ええと……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3577
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_4f5acc60:

    # "The two suddenly stop signing and look at me in unison, both having exactly the same look of disapproval. In one fluid motion, Misha's hand suddenly extends high above me and comes rocketing down."
    "２人が突然手話を中断して、一斉に全く同じ非難の表情を俺に向ける。ミーシャが突然、流れるような動きで俺の頭上に手を振り上げ、それを閃光の如く振り降ろす。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3584
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_f1a52daa:

    # "Before I can even hope to react, my head is sent bouncing up and down like a jack-in-the-box." with vpunch
    "反応する暇もなく、俺の頭がびっくり箱人形のように上下に振れる。" with vpunch

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3586
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_9e538298:

    # "I quickly bring my hands to my head, more out of reflex than actual pain."
    "俺は痛みを感じるよりも早く、反射的に手を頭に当てる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3588
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_015aafc7:

    # hi "Ow! What was that for!?"
    hi "いてっ！　何すんだよ！？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3595
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_7a387540:

    # "I open my eyes to see the two grinning at each other while exchanging an enthusiastic thumbs-up."
    "俺が目を開けると、静音とミーシャがニヤニヤしながらお互いにぐっと親指を突き立てている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3601
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_50c5b004:

    # mi "Shicchan says she forgives you now, Hicchan~!"
    mi "しっちゃんが許してあげるって言ってるよ、ひっちゃん～！"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3603
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_00e7fea7:

    # hi "Could you forgive me with a little less force next time?"
    hi "次はもうちょっと非暴力的に許してくれないか？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3608
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_cb5680f2:

    # mi "Wahahahaha~!"
    mi "わはははは～！"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3610
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_de7d4748:

    # "I look at the two with a blank face. Misha and Shizune: one, Hisao: nil."
    "俺は呆然としながら２人を見る。ミーシャと静音：１点、久夫：０点。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3615
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_ef2b123c:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3620
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_1197fc0f:

    # mi "Oh, Shicchan also says that you should check your student mail more often~!"
    mi "あっ、しっちゃんが郵便受けももっとチェックしてって言ってるよ～！"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3630
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_d28b865a:

    # "She produces a bright yellow envelope and hands it over with an exuberant grin."
    "明るい黄色の封筒を取り出して、はち切れんばかりの笑顔とともに俺に渡す。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3632
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_b0a6dae5:

    # "Strange. Who could have written me a letter? Now is not the time and most definitely not the place to find out, though."
    "変だな。俺に手紙なんて、誰が書いたんだ？　でもそれを確認するのにこのタイミングと、何よりこの場はふさわしくない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3641
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_5471717f:

    # "Giving up on the nap so cruelly stolen from me, I rub my forehead and slowly get up, putting the sheets and envelope in my bag before swinging it over my shoulder."
    "無残にも奪い去られた居眠りの時間をあきらめ、俺は額をこすりながらゆっくりと立ち上がる。プリントと封筒をかばんに入れて、肩にかける。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3649
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_fc57d361:

    # "I take a step back and move to depart with a small bow, while Misha clutches her sides laughing and Shizune nods back in a curt farewell."
    "そのまま一歩下がり、軽く会釈しながらその場を離れる。ミーシャは腰に手を当てて笑い続け、静音は俺に会釈を返してそっけなく別れを告げる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3658
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_b57fd2d5:

    # "I join the flow of students exiting the open door, and turn the corner into the hallway."
    "開かれたドアから出ていく生徒たちの波に交じって、俺は廊下に出るために角を曲がる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3665
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_b77ae1d7:

    # "…only to end up face to face with Hanako."
    "……そこで華子と鉢合わせになる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3667
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_3cd5c53c:

    # hi "Whoa. Uh, hey Hanako."
    hi "わっ。ええと、よう華子"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3672
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_398bdfe8:

    # ha "Good afternoon… Hisao."
    ha "こんにちは……久夫くん"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3677
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_df0d65a1:

    # "Silence falls between us as busily chatting students pass us by. She's fidgeting constantly, her eyes drawn to her rather unremarkable footwear."
    "忙しくおしゃべりする生徒たちが通り過ぎる中、俺と華子の間には沈黙の空気が流れる。華子は絶えずもじもじしながら、地味な自分の上履きに目を落としている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3679
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_bd441f57:

    # "I take the bridge of my nose in my fingers while I blink my eyes heavily in an attempt to make things seem clearer. I'm barely staying awake as it is."
    "俺は状況をはっきりさせようと、鼻筋を押さえながら目をぱちぱちさせる。ただでさえ眠くて仕方ないのに。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3681
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_7ce4fd25:

    # hi "Hanako, you want to say something. What is it?"
    hi "何か用があるんだろ、華子。何だ？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3686
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_6a729400:

    # ha "U-um… I wanted to… give you this…"
    ha "え、えっと……これを……渡したくて……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3688
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_34d1d59d:

    # hi "Hmm?"
    hi "え？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3693
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_2bc43c90:

    # "She holds out a small rectangular piece of paper. I blink again to make out the text through barely open eyes, slowly starting to make out what's written."
    "華子が小さな四角い紙を俺に差し出す。俺はもう一度まばたきをしながら、そこに書かれている内容をゆっくりと読み取る。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3699
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_29b04a72:

    # hi "…A shopping list?"
    hi "……買い物リスト？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3701
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_149fba9e:

    # "I look upwards, raising an eyebrow."
    "俺はびっくりして上を向く。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3706
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_0d7192af:

    # ha "I usually go shopping with Lilly but I can't come, so…"
    ha "いつもリリーと一緒に行くんだけど、行けないから、それで……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3708
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_9e829355:

    # hi "You want me to run errands for you?"
    hi "俺にお使いを頼みたいのか？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3713
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_bc79b556:

    # ha "I-it's okay if you don't want to! I just thought that, maybe, um…"
    ha "い、嫌ならいいの！　ただ私、たぶん、えっと……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3715
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_542407a0:

    # "She's panicking. I sigh. Yet another battle lost, though this time by a weakly-fought surrender."
    "華子がパニックに陥る。俺はため息をつく。また負けか。今回は不戦敗だけど。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3717
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_9d00727a:

    # "I smile tiredly and rest a hand on her head to calm her down."
    "俺はやれやれと笑いながら華子の頭にぽんと手を乗せ、彼女を落ち着かせる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3719
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_e1a0fa8a:

    # hi "It's fine, I was going to go anyway. Just the stuff on this list?"
    hi "いいよ。俺も行こうと思ってたんだ。ここに書いてあるものだけでいいのか？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3724
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_1ab2d4ad:

    # "She nods then bows deeply, twice, as if to make her gratitude perfectly clear."
    "華子はうなずくと、今度は深くおじぎをする。それも二回、感謝の意をはっきりと示すかのように。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3729
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_37a687bb:

    # ha "W-we were going to meet outside the school gates at six… thank you, I was going to get it, but I need to study for the test tomorrow."
    ha "こ、校門の外で６時に会う予定だったの……ありがとう、自分で買いに行くつもりだったんだけど、明日のテストのために勉強しなきゃいけないから"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3731
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_c1692ba6:

    # hi "Test? Ah, that's right, science. How're you doing with it?"
    hi "テスト？　ああそうだ、科学か。勉強の調子はどうだ？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3736
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_43435734:

    # "She brightens ever so slightly."
    "華子の表情がほんの少しだけ明るくなる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3741
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_68dd8dff:

    # ha "I've been… spending more time on it than before. I think I can do… okay."
    ha "前よりも……たくさん勉強してるから。たぶん……大丈夫です"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3743
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_de1dd8da:

    # hi "Good work, then."
    hi "そうか、がんばってるな"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3748
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_ad66c6db:

    # "She too starts smiling, and much more earnestly than I at that."
    "華子も笑い始める。俺のよりもはるかに心のこもった笑顔だ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3750
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_5a95ffe4:

    # "I have full confidence that I can do fine in it without any extra studying, but the fact that she's putting in the effort instead of just reading in the library is heartening."
    "俺にはこれ以上テスト勉強をしなくても大丈夫だという完璧な自信がある。だけど、華子が図書室で読書に没頭する代わりにテストのための努力をしているという事実を知って、胸が熱くなる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3752
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_8e218da8:

    # hi "I'll grab your stuff and take it to your dorm in the evening. Seeya."
    hi "買ってきたら夜にでも部屋に持っていくよ。じゃあな"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3760
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_eccdced4:

    # "With a small wave, we part ways."
    "俺は軽く手を振って華子と別れる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3762
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_d41f8cf9:

    # "I'll go do my homework before meeting Lilly. I should be able to take care of it in time."
    "リリーに会う前に、宿題をやっとこう。時間までにはできるはずだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3771
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_42391cd6:

    # "Wrangling with a particularly complicated math problem has caused me to be a little bit late for my meeting with Lilly."
    "やたら難解な数学の問題と格闘していて、リリーと会うことになっている時間を少し過ぎてしまう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3773
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_25bd684a:

    # "Only a couple of minutes, but enough to make me step smartly out into the courtyard and to the school gate."
    "ほんの数分だけど、俺を慌てさせるのに十分な遅刻だ。俺は校庭へと飛び出し、校門を出る。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3778
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_69fd5d75:

    # "I make a right turn and start my way towards the small town below, leaving a few students turning the other way to the bus station."
    "そこで右に曲がり、坂の下にある小さな町へと向かう。他の生徒が何人かバス停に向かって逆方向に歩いていく。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3780
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_3fde32e7:

    # "I slip my right hand into my pocket as I walk in the orange sunlight of dusk."
    "俺は右手をポケットに突っ込み、夕暮れのオレンジ色の光の中を歩いていく。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3782
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_8d44efc8:

    # "Thankfully the sweltering summer heat's started to die down, making way for a pleasant cool breeze."
    "ありがたいことに、うだるような夏の暑さは和らぎ始めていて、涼しいそよ風が吹き抜けている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3788
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_b5efbfe1:

    # "When I stretch my hands high above my head, a familiar figure takes form, cane in her right hand."
    "手を頭上に高くかざした時、俺は右手に杖を持つ見慣れた人物の姿を捉える。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3790
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_6ccdbfa9:

    # hi "Ah, Lilly."
    hi "あ、リリー"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3796
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_716d8d47:

    # "She stops and turns around, swiveling her head slightly to try and work out exactly where the voice came from."
    "リリーが立ち止まり、後ろを振り返る。彼女は頭をわずかに振りながら、声の正確な位置を探り当てようとしている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3798
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_452195d5:

    # hi "Hey. It's me."
    hi "やあ、俺だよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3800
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_9294c7b3:

    # "I quickly catch up to her, coming in beside her and matching her slow pace as we resume walking."
    "俺はすばやくリリーに追いつくと、彼女の横に並ぶ。そして彼女のゆっくりとしたペースに合わせるようにして再び一緒に歩き始める。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3805
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_09b2b4f1:

    # li "Good afternoon, Hisao."
    li "ごきげんよう、久夫さん"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3807
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_adfacf09:

    # hi "Hi there."
    hi "こんちは"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3814
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_3048d166:

    # "I glance up at the sky."
    "俺は空を見上げる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3816
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_6db93071:

    # "A distinct tinge of orange discolors the clouds, washing the footpath in its light. Long shadows from the trees fall across the wide road down the hill."
    "オレンジのはっきりとした色合いが雲に映え、歩道をもその光で満たす。木々の作り出す長い影が下り坂の道路へと伸びる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3822
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_3372b531:

    # li "So, Hisao, what brings you here?"
    li "それで久夫さん、どうしたんですか？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3824
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_be581ac2:

    # hi "Just going to town to grab some groceries. Hanako sent me."
    hi "下まで行って買い物しようと思ってさ。華子が俺を使いに出したんだ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3829
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_bdfccf3f:

    # li "Hanako sent you?"
    li "華ちゃんが、ですか？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3831
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_a0adb89e:

    # hi "Yeah, said she needed to study for a test tomorrow. I was going to come down anyway, so I'll just buy her stuff as well."
    hi "ああ、明日のテスト勉強があるからって。俺も行こうと思ってたから、華子のもついでに買ってくるつもり"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3833
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_2f836cb4:

    # "Unspoken is that Lilly really could use some help to get food, but it's an obvious fact that neither of us needs to state."
    "リリーももちろん俺の手を借りられるよ、とは言わなかったけど、２人とも暗黙の了解としてそれが分かっている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3838
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_17ca0b34:

    # li "It's good to hear she's studying for it."
    li "華ちゃんが勉強していると聞いて、嬉しいですよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3840
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_ed68a402:

    # hi "I thought the same thing when she asked me to come with you."
    hi "華子が俺にお使いを頼んだ時、俺も同じこと思ったよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3845
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_5f3ba4a5:

    # "We continue walking down the street, the familiar sound of her cane echoing through the air as we go. Except for the occasional passing car and the leaves whispering in the branches, there's a blissful silence."
    "俺とリリーは坂を下り続ける。道すがら、聞き慣れたリリーの杖の音が周りにこだまする。時々通り過ぎる車の音や枝葉のざわめきを除けば、至福にも感じられる静けさだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3847
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_c641880b:

    # "Thank God I can finally relax for the first time today."
    "ああ、俺はようやく今日最初の安らぎを得ることができる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3859
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_75434c45:

    # "I glance over at Lilly."
    "俺はリリーのほうを見る。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3861
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_8745a9ae:

    # "That porcelain face of hers never seems to lack that air of relaxed confidence. I guess the same could be said of her personality, too."
    "その透き通った表情からは落ち着いた自信あふれる空気が決して失われないように思える。彼女の人柄についてもたぶん同じことが言えるだろう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3863
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_aa80a94e:

    # "As she silently walks, her face remaining pointed to the street ahead of her, I look ahead and savor the cool air blowing over my face."
    "リリーは正面に伸びる道路を向いたまま、静かに歩き続ける。俺は目を上げて、顔に当たるひんやりとした空気を味わう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3865
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_53ae037b:

    # "This is probably the calmest moment I've had since the about-face my life took so recently."
    "ついこの間に人生の転機を迎えて以来、こんなに心安まる気持ちになった瞬間はたぶんないだろう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3867
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_c297bed3:

    # "To have it while walking to get some groceries. What a weird life."
    "その瞬間が、買い物に行く途中なんて。おかしな人生だよな。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3874
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_b953049b:

    # "I feel the crumpled-up note rubbing against my hand in my pocket, and pull it out to check its contents."
    "ポケットの中でくしゃくしゃになったメモ書きが手に当たるのを感じ、俺は内容を確認するためにそれを取り出す。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3876
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_d1f78157:

    # hi "Let's see here… eggs, bread, cereal, thyme, lettuce, shaved ham…"
    hi "ええと、なになに……卵、パン、シリアル、タイム、レタス、薄切りハム……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3881
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_7d23dc59:

    # li "That sounds like quite a bit to carry back along with your own."
    li "なんだか久夫さんの買い物のついでにしては量が多いようですね"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3883
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_d20c0fdc:

    # hi "Yeah. Just how much does this girl eat anyway?"
    hi "ああ。あの子、どんだけ食ってるんだ？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3885
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_1f51cac7:

    # "My mind suddenly clicks that yes, there actually is a person beside me."
    "そう言って、突然我に返る。そうだ、すぐそばに人がいるんだった。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3887
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_011dd1ad:

    # hi "W-wait, I mean…"
    hi "い、いや、つまりその……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3892
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_7d154311:

    # "She laughs wholeheartedly."
    "リリーが心底おかしそうに笑う。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3897
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_07dc4ff3:

    # li "My my, Hisao."
    li "あらあら、久夫さんったら"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3899
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_a5630c95:

    # "Her giggles punctuate her words, though she's making little effort to suppress them."
    "忍び笑いが言葉に混じる。でもリリーはその笑いを抑えようとはしない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3904
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_34b046cb:

    # li "Quite direct today, aren't we?"
    li "今日の久夫さんは、ずいぶんはっきりと言いますね？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3906
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_d457e996:

    # hi "Yeah, you got me there. Still, it is quite a bit."
    hi "ああ、まいったな。でもさ、やっぱり多いよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3911
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_0665d233:

    # li "Usually I go shopping with Hanako, so I know what she buys. It's the same thing every week."
    li "普段は私と華ちゃんで一緒に買い物に行くので、華ちゃんが何を買うのか知っています。毎週同じものですよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3913
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_c3026676:

    # hi "Huh. She a good cook?"
    hi "へえ。華子は料理うまいの？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3918
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_cfd26a7b:

    # "She gives a nervous giggle."
    "リリーが苦笑する。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3920
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_b42c8967:

    # li "It's usually me who ends up cooking. I used to do so for Akira, so it's no problem doing it for Hanako as well."
    li "だいたいは私が作ることになります。姉さんのためにお料理をしていたので、華ちゃんのために作るのも問題はありません"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3922
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_160b8e85:

    # hi "You can cook? But…"
    hi "リリーが料理を？　でも……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3927
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_2eeacef7:

    # "A short hum with an amused lilt emanates from beside me. I wonder if the fact that she seems amused by my comments so often is actually genuine, or rather just from a want to make me more comfortable in addressing her blindness?"
    "愉快そうな、陽気なハミングが俺の横から聞こえてくる。俺の言葉をしょっちゅう面白がってくれているのは、純粋にそうなのか、それとも彼女の目が見えないことに触れる俺を気遣っているだけなのか？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3932
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_15bf6568:

    # li "There are ways around it. Some meals are more difficult to cook than others because of being unable to see what I'm doing, but it usually only takes a little more time. Fingers can double as very useful measurement tools, for example."
    li "コツがあるんです。見えないために作るのが難しいお料理も確かにありますが、ほとんどはほんの少し余計に時間がかかるだけですよ。例えば、指はとても便利な計量器具として使えますし"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3934
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_b27105a5:

    # "It makes sense, but she'd have to be pretty careful not to hurt herself. I wonder how many times that's happened, given that it sounds like she's cooked alone for possibly years while Akira worked and her parents were gone."
    "それは分かるけど、でも自分を傷つけないよう相当気をつけなきゃいけないはずだ。晃さんは働き、両親もいない間、リリーは何年も１人で料理を作ってきたみたいだ。何回くらいそんなことが起きただろうと思う。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3936
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_1417aabb:

    # "With that, the conversation trails off."
    "会話はそこで途切れてしまう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3938
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_6864a99b:

    # "Compared to the awkward silences of Hanako, Lilly seems genuinely content to say what she thinks and stay quiet when there's nothing to say."
    "華子といるときの気まずい沈黙と比べると、リリーは自分の考えていることを話し、言うべきことがない時には沈黙を守ることに満足しているみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3940
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_a034634e:

    # "The slick road under my feet is bathed in an orange glow, the occasional fallen leaf crunching underfoot as we walk. I let out a deep yawn, my lack of sleep coming back to haunt me."
    "足元の滑らかな道路はオレンジ色の光で照らされ、ときおり落ちている葉っぱが踏み歩く俺の下でぱりぱりと音を立てる。また睡眠不足に苛まれて、俺は大あくびを漏らす。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3945
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_28fd2af4:

    # li "Did you not get much sleep last night?"
    li "昨日の夜はよく眠れなかったんですか？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3947
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_ed399d51:

    # hi "I couldn't sleep at all for the last two nights. Probably insomnia."
    hi "二晩全然寝れなかったよ。たぶん不眠症だな"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3954
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_1dff58e8:

    # "Lilly's face suddenly becomes worried. It feels like a personal failure every time she gets worried about my well-being, even if it's genuinely nice to know someone cares."
    "リリーが急に心配そうな顔をする。誰かが心配してくれるのは純粋に嬉しいけど、リリーが俺の健康を心配する時はいつも俺に落ち度があるような気がする。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3956
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_da7bbb21:

    # li "You have insomnia? Aren't you going to see the nurse about it?"
    li "不眠症なんですか？　ナースさんに診てもらわないんですか？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3958
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_3e1040b8:

    # hi "Nah, no real need. It's happened before a few times. My meds screw with my sleeping occasionally."
    hi "いや、必要ないって。前にも何度かこういうことがあったしさ。薬のせいで時々眠れなくなるんだ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3963
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_c26fa9ff:

    # li "…Ah. I'm… sorry."
    li "……ああ。あの……すみません"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3965
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_e8f3cbd3:

    # hi "Come on, it's not your fault. At least I shouldn't have any trouble getting to sleep tonight."
    hi "おいおい、リリーのせいじゃないだろ。少なくとも今夜は不眠の心配はなさそうだし"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3970
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_a8b9c62c:

    # li "You do worry me sometimes."
    li "時々、久夫さんのことが心配になります"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3972
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_d4ff12b9:

    # hi "I… worry you?"
    hi "俺のことが……心配？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3974
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_0cd9d769:

    # "I reach around and scratch the back of my neck. I kind of want to address this."
    "俺は手を回して首の後ろをかく。これははっきりさせといたほうがいいな。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3976
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_466b47b5:

    # hi "Hey, Lilly…"
    hi "なあ、リリー……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3981
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_16b10efa:

    # li "Hmm?"
    li "はい？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3983
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_f056deb6:

    # hi "I don't mean to sound weird, but… please try to forget about my heart condition."
    hi "変なこと言うようだけどさ……俺の心臓のことは忘れてくれないかな"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3988
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_17e30856:

    # "She looks kind of lost. I hardly blame her."
    "リリーが困惑した様子を見せる。無理もない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3990
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_443e1de5:

    # hi "I guess what I'm trying to get at is… just don't treat me differently because of it."
    hi "つまり、何が言いたいかっていうと……そのことで俺を特別扱いしないでほしいんだ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3995
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_ac8d3fd8:

    # "She bows her head slightly, her white cheeks reddening almost imperceptibly."
    "リリーがほんの少し首をかしげる。彼女の白い頬が、ほとんど気づかないぐらいほのかに赤く染まる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3997
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_8dbebeb2:

    # li "It's only natural to worry about those around you…"
    li "でも、久夫さんの身の周りのことを心配するのは自然なことですよ……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3999
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_bed869bd:

    # hi "Well, it's still nice to know there's someone like that out there."
    hi "いや、まあ、俺を気遣ってくれる人がいるんだって分かるのは嬉しいけどさ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4004
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_4a6c8612:

    # "It may be somewhat embarrassing to say, but it's the truth. Lilly takes a breath to regain her composure and manages a gentle smile, though her cheeks remain flushed."
    "こんなことを言うのはちょっと恥ずかしいけど、でも本心だ。リリーは冷静さを取り戻すためにひと呼吸置いて、優しく微笑む。頬は今も染まったままだけど。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4006
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_1d82ca4b:

    # "The final downhill walk to the store passes in silence."
    "店への最後の下り坂を、沈黙を保ちながら歩く。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4013
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_9dcc8766:

    # "Storewoman" "Welcome!"
    "女性店員" "いらっしゃいませ！"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4015
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_990b2716:

    # hi "I suppose I'll get my stuff first and Hanako's on the second round."
    hi "まず俺が買うものを取って、それから華子のものを探そうかな"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4020
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_d0f35177:

    # "I grab two well-worn red baskets from the stack beside the entrance and pass one to Lilly."
    "入口そばの買い物かご置き場から使いこまれた赤いかごを二つ取ると、その一つをリリーに渡す。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4032
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_a1ddab84:

    # "Just as she did before, she lays it on the ground and slides her retracted cane between the basket's handles before picking it back up with her right hand."
    "リリーはこの前と同じように買い物かごを床に置き、縮めた杖を取っ手の間に滑り込ませてから、再びかごを右手で持ち上げる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4043
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_12330940:

    # "When she takes hold of my arm in her own, I'm surprised at just how fast this kind of casual contact became so natural. Mostly due to necessity, no doubt."
    "リリーが俺の腕に自分の腕を添える。短い間にこんなにも自然に触れあえるようになるなんて、自分でも驚きだ。必要に迫られたからだろうな、きっと。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4048
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_6452ac38:

    # li "Shall we?"
    li "行きましょうか？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4052
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_21ce94c5:

    # hi "Sure."
    hi "だろうな"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4054
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_5576141e:

    # "While we navigate around the store, the odd person occasionally passing us pays us no heed at all. It's nice, compared to the stares and whispers around the city."
    "俺とリリーが店内を見て回るあいだ、たまにそばを通り過ぎる人は俺たちを全く気に留めない。俺たちをじろじろ見てひそひそ話をする街の人々とは大違いだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4059
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_f14ab533:

    # "As we reach each aisle, I quickly check with Lilly what she needs and grab it along with what I want, putting our items into their respective baskets."
    "売り場の通路を順に通りながら、俺はリリーが必要なものを彼女に素早く確認し、それを俺の欲しいものと一緒に取ってそれぞれのかごに入れる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4061
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_08b195ba:

    # "It's an odd feeling, to be depended on so much for something so basic as shopping. Hanako would be practically a necessity for her to pick out what she wants, after all."
    "買い物みたいな、すごく簡単なことでこんなにも頼られるなんて、おかしな気分だ。やっぱり、リリーが必要なものを選び出すには華子がいないとまず無理なんだろう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4063
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_6de5cccf:

    # hi "Right, I'm pretty much done with both my stuff and Hanako's. You needing anything else, Lilly?"
    hi "よし、俺と華子の買い物、両方とも終わったよ。リリーは他に何か欲しいものある？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4068
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_37f84067:

    # li "No, this should be everything."
    li "いえ、これで全部です"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4070
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_efb676c2:

    # hi "Off we go, then."
    hi "じゃあ、行くか"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4072
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_aa1a8a4c:

    # "Oddly, there's a queue a mile long. Considering the store's only large enough to warrant one counter, seems like it'll take a while."
    "おかしなことに、レジの前には長い列ができている。店の大きさからレジが一カ所しかないことを考えると、これはしばらく時間がかかりそうだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4074
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_4bf99ed5_1:

    # hi "Damn."
    hi "くっそー"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4079
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_98d0de8c:

    # "Lilly gives an inquisitive look, unable to see the reason for my complaint."
    "俺の不満の原因を見ることができないリリーが、それを知りたそうな面持ちでこちらを見る。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4081
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_43727403:

    # hi "The queue's really long. Looks like we'll have to wait."
    hi "レジ待ちがいっぱいいるよ。けっこう待たなきゃいけないみたいだな"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4086
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_25828eea:

    # li "How strange."
    li "おかしなこともあるものですね"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4088
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_5c6c741e:

    # "Sharing the same mood of resignation, we reluctantly take our place at the end of the line."
    "俺とリリーはあきらめの心境で、しぶしぶ列の一番後ろに並ぶ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4092
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_3f8dccf5:

    # "One person finishes, the line moves up. Another person finishes, the line moves up."
    "１人終わり、列が動く。もう１人終わり、また列が動く。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4094
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_124c39e9:

    # "By the time we finally reach the head of the line, I'm so close to dozing off that Lilly has to gently pat me on the back for me to move up."
    "俺とリリーが列の先頭に来るころには、俺はほとんど眠りこけてしまう。リリーが俺の背中を優しく叩き、動くよう俺に促す。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4099
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_44d14e70:

    # li "Hisao… Hisao!"
    li "久夫さん……久夫さん！"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4103
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_90256f2c:

    # hi "Hmm? Ah, sorry."
    hi "ん？　ああ、ごめん"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4108
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_0de25e28:

    # "She gives a short sigh of consternation as I move up, getting the groceries for Hanako and me put into separate bags."
    "俺が動くと、リリーがはっと息をのむ。俺は華子と自分の物をそれぞれ別の袋に分ける。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4110
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_7ff8d8cd:

    # "Storewoman" "Thank you, please come again!"
    "女性店員" "ありがとうございました、またお越しくださいませ！"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4118
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_e32fa01b:

    # "By the time we emerge from the store, Lilly's holding a single bag while I struggle to carry four, both hands well and truly full. It's a lot of work, but thankfully the items in them are light."
    "店から出るころには、リリーは買い物袋を１袋持ち、俺は両手を完全にふさぐ４袋と格闘している。持ち歩くのは大変だけど、ありがたいことに中身はそんなに重くない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4120
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_4cc243c5:

    # "Even without looking skyward it's obvious that a surprising amount of time's passed, the road outside being dark and lit by streetlamps."
    "買い物に長い時間がかかったことは空を見上げるまでもなく明らかだ。道路は暗闇に包まれ、街灯がそれを照らしている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4125
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_4c021530:

    # "Once Lilly retrieves her cane, we set out back to the dormitories the way we came, leaving the welcoming warm glow of the store."
    "リリーが杖を元の長さに伸ばすと、俺たちは誘い込むような光を放つ店を背に、来た道を寮に向かって引き返す。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4132
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_bfcff13a:

    # "Despite the road being empty of cars, the full bags abundantly make up for the lack of noise, constantly clunking and squeaking together."
    "車は全く通らないけど、こすれ合ってガサガサ鳴り続ける俺の買い物袋がその静けさを派手に打ち破る。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4137
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_b8c62053:

    # li "My my, Hisao, it's good to find that you're eating well."
    li "あらあら、久夫さんがたくさん食べていると分かって嬉しいですよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4139
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_c136f60b:

    # hi "I'm a growing guy after all, I need to eat all I can!"
    hi "俺だって育ち盛りだし、食えるものはなんでも食わなきゃ！"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4144
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_8f4eab61:

    # li "Hmm… it must be nice, being a man."
    li "ふぅん……男の人になれたら、素敵でしょうね"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4146
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_3798bf3f:

    # hi "W-what?"
    hi "な、何だって？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4148
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_eb3d38f0:

    # "Seemingly not noticing, or ignoring, my surprise at the completely out-of-left-field comment, she continues on without missing a beat."
    "思いがけない言葉にすっとんきょうな声を上げて驚く俺に気づいていないのか、それとも無視しているのか、リリーが調子を変えずに言葉を継ぐ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4153
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_88eca837:

    # li "Weight doesn't really bother you when eating, most of the time."
    li "だって、食べている時でも体重をほとんど気にしなくていいですし"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4155
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_c408f346:

    # hi "I get what you mean. Women tend to worry about stuff like that more than we do, I guess."
    hi "ああ、そういうことか。まあ、女性は俺たち男よりもそういうこと気にするみたいだな"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4160
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_77396e19:

    # li "Exactly. It makes me somewhat envious, to be honest."
    li "そうですよ。正直言って、少しうらやましいです"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4162
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_29792541:

    # hi "Well, it's not like we can outright ignore it."
    hi "いや、俺たちだって体重のこと全く無視できるってわけじゃないよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4164
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_500a35f5:

    # "With an affirmative nod, we continue on our walk."
    "リリーが同意するようにうなずき、俺たちは歩き続ける。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4166
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_ef765caa:

    # hi "Huh, that's right."
    hi "ああ、そうだ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4171
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_d78581af:

    # li "What is it?"
    li "何ですか？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4173
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_c1aab370:

    # hi "Hanako mentioned your birthday was earlier this year. Do anything special for it?"
    hi "華子が、リリーの誕生日は年の初めだって言ってたな。なにか特別なことはやった？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4178
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_3a7dadec:

    # "She gives a long pause, lost in thought for a few seconds as she recalls the event."
    "リリーが黙り込み、しばらくその出来事を思い返している。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4183
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_d73a329c:

    # li "Not really. It was just Hanako and me having a little party during the night after school."
    li "いいえ、特には。夜に華ちゃんと私で小さなパーティーをしたくらいです"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4185
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_4fadebeb:

    # hi "Your birthday's supposed to be a big event, you know."
    hi "でも、リリーの誕生日って大イベントじゃないか"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4187
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_075cdabd:

    # "Sounds like a pretty lonely way to spend a birthday, just her and Hanako staying overnight."
    "華子と２人っきりで夜を過ごすなんて、誕生日の過ごし方としてはとても寂しく聞こえる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4189
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_aa952473:

    # "Birthdays always felt like a family occasion for me. They were a time when, in spite of their full-time jobs, both my parents would make an effort to be there for the day or at least for a party beforehand."
    "俺にとって誕生日は、家族との触れ合いの機会だ。２人とも働いているにもかかわらず、両親は誕生日には俺と一緒に過ごそうと努力してくれたし、それができなくても、少なくとも事前にパーティーは開いてくれた。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4191
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_c46631b1:

    # "It reminds me of how Lilly mentioned she hadn't seen her family in such a long time, and even ended up moving away from Akira's house afterwards."
    "そこまで考えて、リリーが長いあいだ家族と会っていないと言っていたことを思い出す。彼女はその後も晃さんとさえ別れて暮らさなければならなくなったんだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4193
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_d0e1bfaf:

    # "But I guess it's the same in situations as mundane as these. Considering her inability to read the packaging, just getting groceries would be a pain without somebody else around."
    "でも、買い物みたいなありふれた状況にも同じことが言えるんじゃないか。外装に書かれていることを読めないリリーにとって、単なる買い物だけでも誰かの手助けなしでは大変だろう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4195
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_1bee66fd:

    # "In the end, she just has Hanako and me, and Akira when she's off from work."
    "結局、今のリリーには華子と俺、そして仕事をしていない時の晃さんしかいないんだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4197
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_65faf027:

    # "Be that as it may, she still seems to have many more distant friends among the students, not to mention people like Yuuko."
    "そうは言っても、リリーには俺たち以外にも普通の友達がたくさんいるように見える。優子さんみたいな人たちは言わずもがなだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4199
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_0e59f486:

    # "It seems to be her own choice that there's such a separation between those who are close to her, and those who she only socializes with."
    "親密な付き合いをする人と表面的な付き合いをするだけの人、リリーはそれを彼女自身で選り分けて区別しているようだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4201
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_b7937c23:

    # "It humbles me a little to see how much Lilly seems to have her life set up and going just as she wants."
    "自分の人生をしっかりと保ち、自分の意思を持って生きているように見えるリリーに、俺は少し気後れしてしまう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4203
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_fcf05cfa:

    # "Yet Hanako is there for her to celebrate her birthday, and I'm here helping her with shopping. It's a weird kind of symbiosis, I suppose."
    "それでも、華子はリリーと誕生日を一緒に祝い、俺はこうしてリリーの買い物を手伝っている。おかしな共生関係、なんだろうな。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4208
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_f712ac2b:

    # li "Are you all right, Hisao?"
    li "久夫さん、大丈夫ですか？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4210
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_47b6c948:

    # hi "Sorry?"
    hi "えっ、何で？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4212
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_91a64b97:

    # li "You just seemed to go very quiet, that's all."
    li "いえ、ただ、久夫さんがとても静かに思えたので"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4214
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_29370ca7:

    # hi "Ah, sorry. I was just thinking."
    hi "ああ、ごめん。考えごとしてたんだ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4219
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_ff06eaa7:

    # li "Oh?"
    li "あら？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4239
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_8fd2fb11:

    # "Eventually we get to the girl's dormitories, both my arms aching from the weight of two sets of groceries."
    "ついに俺とリリーは女子寮にたどり着く。二つの買い物袋の束のせいで両腕がずきずきする。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4241
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_a8bd7764:

    # hi "Hah… we're finally here. Phew."
    hi "はあはあ……ようやく着いたな。ふう"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4251
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_f66bd1eb:

    # "I bend down to wipe my forehead with the back of my hand. Lilly stops in front of her door and sets down her bag, fishing around in her pocket for the key."
    "俺は手の甲で額を拭うために前かがみになる。リリーは自室のドアの前に立ち止まると買い物袋を床に置き、ポケットの中のカギを探っている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4256
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_e2967411:

    # li "Thank you, Hisao. I really appreciate your help."
    li "ありがとうございます、久夫さん。本当に助かりました"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4258
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_935469e8:

    # hi "Ah, this is nothing."
    hi "いや、こんなの何でもないよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4263
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_e460ead2:

    # li "It might be nothing to you, but it's… definitely something for me."
    li "久夫さんにとっては何でもなくても……私にとってはとても大きなことですよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4274
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_616d9289:

    # "And with that, she steps through her door, closing it behind her."
    "そんな言葉を残し、リリーは閉まるドアの向こう側に消える。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4276
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_c9e3031e:

    # "I blink. Those were nothing but honest thanks, but I can't help feeling something different about them."
    "俺は目をぱちくりさせる。ただの真摯な感謝以外の何物でもない言葉だけど、なにか別の意味があるような気がしてしょうがない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4278
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_150a3fda:

    # "Anyway, I have something else to do before I can mull on that at my leisure."
    "とにかく今は、そんなことを考えている暇はない。俺にはまだやることがある。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4290
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_91e36db1:

    # "I turn back to the door to Hanako's room and proceed to knock twice in quick succession, the bags still in my hand rustling together."
    "俺は後ろを振り返り、華子の部屋のドアを立て続けに二度ノックする。今も手に持っている買い物袋がガサガサと音を立てる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4298
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_8469acb7:

    # "After a couple of seconds, the door slowly opens. If one weren't looking closely, they could be forgiven for thinking it hadn't moved at all."
    "数秒後、ドアがゆっくりと開く。よく見ていなかったら、ドアが動いたことさえ気づかないぐらいだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4300
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_25dce765:

    # "I twist my head to the side to try and peer through the tiny sliver of a gap between the door and the doorframe."
    "俺は頭を横にひねり、ドアとドア枠の間にほんの少しできた細長い隙間を覗こうとする。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4302
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_de0e367f:

    # hi "Hey Hanako, I've got your stuff."
    hi "やあ華子、買ってきたぞ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4308
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_730fbd1d:

    # ha "Ah!"
    ha "ああ！"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4315
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_309f9190:

    # "With that, she opens the door completely, making her plain room visible over her shoulder. Sparsely decorated, it's probably even more unremarkable than my room."
    "その声とともに、ドアが完全に開く。華子の肩越しには彼女の地味な部屋の様子がうかがえる。ほとんど飾りっ気のない、たぶん俺の部屋よりももっと平凡な部屋だ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4317
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_0e628dc8:

    # "I hold out my right arm, both bags almost pulling it straight back down with their weight."
    "俺は右腕を差し伸ばす。持った買い物袋がその重さで俺の腕にのしかかる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4322
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_4267d6cc:

    # ha "Th-thank you, Hisao."
    ha "あ、ありがとう、久夫くん"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4327
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_6b7942b1:

    # ha "I'm sorry to make you… carry them all this way."
    ha "ここまでずっと運ばせてしまって……ごめんなさい"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4329
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_b2a4ffeb:

    # hi "It's fine, don't worry. Just don't make me do it every day, okay?"
    hi "いいよ、気にすんなって。でも毎日は勘弁だぞ、いいな？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4334
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_b4655e25:

    # "I pass the bags to her as I give a lighthearted chuckle. After the initial transfer of weight she manages to take them easily."
    "俺は陽気に笑いながら買い物袋を華子に渡す。ゆっくりと重みを伝えるように渡すと、華子はそれを苦もなく受け取る。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4336
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_ad86357c:

    # hi "I'll be off then. 'Night, Hanako."
    hi "じゃあ行くよ。おやすみ、華子"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4341
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_d01bac3a:

    # ha "Good night. Um, s-see you in class… tomorrow…"
    ha "おやすみなさい。えっと、ま、また明日……教室で……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4348
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_0e4b04a5:

    # "With a deep bow, her groceries still held in both hands, she steps back and shuts the door."
    "華子は両手に買い物袋を持ったまま深いおじぎをし、部屋の中に下がってドアを閉める。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4355
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_626096e5:

    # "Making my way back to my own dorm, I put one bag into my other hand to balance them out."
    "バランスを取るため買い物袋を一つずつ両手に持ち、自分の寮へ戻る。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4357
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_36cac368:

    # "Even as I do so, I can't get Lilly's lighthearted smile out of my mind. When I'd first met her, it would have been nearly impossible to imagine her like that."
    "そうしているあいだも、リリーの陽気な笑顔が俺の頭から離れない。あんなリリーは、俺が最初に彼女に出会った時には想像すらできなかった。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4359
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_1095c053:

    # "Indeed, it feels like we've become closer in the past few weeks since I first got to know both her and Hanako."
    "確かに、俺がリリーと華子に出会ってからの数週間、俺とリリーの距離はどんどん近くなっているように思える。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4361
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_a4f22b42:

    # "The time that I spend with her each day. The small exchanges of happiness we share. Those small moments of joy as I get closer to her."
    "俺が毎日リリーと過ごす時間。俺たちが共有する幸福のほんの少しの交換。リリーとの距離が縮むにつれて得られる、そんな小さな喜びの瞬間たち。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4363
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_fb454ff6:

    # "I'm far from certain, but I don't think these are just the normal feelings of friendship."
    "確信は全然ないけど、この気持ちはただの友情ってわけじゃないような気がする。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4368
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_d4fcca5b:

    # "Once I return to my room, I store away my groceries and begin getting ready for the night."
    "自分の部屋に戻ると俺は買ってきたものをしまい、夜に備える。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4378
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_23d9a7aa:

    # "I swap the school books in my bag for those I'll need tomorrow, pulling out the yellow envelope Misha gave me earlier in the process."
    "明日の時間割で必要な教科書とノートをかばんに入れかえている時、放課後にミーシャから受け取った黄色い封筒が出てくる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4380
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_075af758:

    # "I got so sidetracked by one thing after another that I couldn't deal with it earlier. Who could have written me, I wonder?"
    "次々と起こる出来事に気を取られて中身を見ることができなかった手紙だ。一体誰が書いたんだろう？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4382
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_51fbc4ee:

    # "The name neatly adorning the back of the envelope freezes me in my tracks. It's been so long since I've seen her writing, there's little chance I could have identified it as hers otherwise."
    "封筒の裏側にきれいに書かれた名前を見て、俺はその場で固まってしまう。彼女の字を見るのは本当に久しぶりだ。そうじゃなかったら、これが彼女の筆跡であることを見過ごすはずがない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4384
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_a9c40d09:

    # "'Iwanako.'"
    "『岩魚子』"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4386
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_7511a44e:

    # "Why… should she have written me? I can't think of any good reason for her to do this."
    "どうして……俺に手紙なんか？　彼女がそんなことをする特別な理由が俺には思いつかない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4388
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_7a7545fa:

    # "I almost don't open the letter, but there'd be little point to that. If I just left it alone, its mere existence would gnaw at me until I did something about it."
    "開けないでおこうとするけど、それも意味のないことだ。もしこのままにしておいたら、俺が手紙に手を付けるまでの間もその存在自体が俺を悩ませ続けるだろう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4395
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_daecc507:

    # "I look down at the piece of paper on my desk, its bright and summery decoration beaming happily at me."
    "俺は机に広げられた便せんに目を落とす。そこに描かれた明るくて夏っぽい装飾が幸せそうに輝きを放っている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4397
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_8adb0ce8:

    # "The lettering is in pink, jarring badly with the yellow sunflower border on the card. The handwriting is neat, the characters having been written thoughtfully and with an unusual amount of care."
    "ピンク色でつづられている文字は、便せんに引かれた黄色いひまわりの線とはひどく不釣り合いだ。手書きはきれいで、その一文字一文字が行き過ぎなほどの丁寧さで思慮深く書かれている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4399
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_b620de73:

    # "I'd barely given the letter a second thought when it was given to me, but now I can't get its contents out of my mind."
    "この手紙が渡された時、俺はそれをほとんど気にも留めなかった。だけど今は、この手紙の内容が俺の頭から離れようとしない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4401
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4404
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_511e7377:

    # n "{vspace=90}While I'd like to say that I don't know why she used such an old-fashioned method of communication, considering a phone call or an email would be both much faster and easier, the answer feels obvious enough given the content."
    n "\n\n\n電話や電子メールの方がもっとてっとり早くて簡単だろう。岩魚子がどうして俺とのやりとりにこんな時代遅れな手段を使ったのか真意は分からないけど、その答えは手紙の内容を読めば十分明白な気もする。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4406
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_1c007415:

    # n "A letter leaves a comfortable distance between the sender and the recipient. Unlike a phone, it isn't required that you engage in conversation, and unlike email, there is less expectation of an immediate reply."
    n "手紙を使えば差出人と受取人の距離を適切に保つことができる。電話と違って会話に直接加わる必要もないし、電子メールと違って迅速な返事を期待されることもない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4408
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_c81f1e35:

    # n "{vspace=30}Statements such as 'the third-years seem to be very anxious about the final exams,' and 'it's so weird to think we are already seniors, isn't it?' are just smalltalk. Smalltalk that could have been achieved by simply replying to any of the messages I'd sent her while in hospital."
    n "\n『３年生になって、みんな卒業試験のことで頭がいっぱいになっています』とか『私たちがもう最高学年だっていうのが、とても変な感じだと思わない？』とかいう記述はただの世間話だ。俺が病院にいた時でも岩魚子に向けたどんな話題からも引き出せたような世間話。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4410
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_76ba8aef:

    # n "The ending, though, is the true reason she sent this. The last couple of lines, added almost as an afterthought."
    n "だけど、手紙の最後の部分、これこそ岩魚子がこの手紙を送った本当の理由だ。思い付きで書き加えられたかのような、最後の数行。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4412
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4422
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_58f09731:

    # n "{vspace=210}'I wonder if we will meet again. Perhaps it's for the best if we don't?'"
    n "\n\n\n\n\n\n\n『もう一度会うことはできるのかな。もしかしたら、会わないほうがいいのかも？』"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4424
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_727474c6:

    # n "It's a statement that should hurt. I've always heard breakups are nasty stuff, but it feels like this is simply a reaffirmation of what we both already knew instead."
    n "本来なら心が痛むはずの一文だ。別れっていうのは厄介なものだといつも耳にしていたけど、これはお互いがとっくに分かっていたことを再確認しているだけのように思える。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4426
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_ad4e15d3:

    # n "It's the preceding text, no more than smalltalk, that makes me feel most uneasy. I can't figure out why, no matter how long I sit here and look down at this bright and summery piece of paper."
    n "世間話に過ぎない前置きの文章こそ俺が一番傷ついた部分だ。それがどうしてなのかは、どれだけ長く座って明るく夏っぽい便せんに目を落としていても分からない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4428
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_2b06ee39:

    # nvl clear
    # n "{vspace=240}'If you would like to correspond with me, by all means write me back.'"
    nvl clear
    n "\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n『もし連絡を取りたいと思ったら、ぜひお返事ください』"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4432
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_236438f2:

    # n "It's plainly obvious that this is not the type of letter to be replied to. In the end, this letter is no more than a simple abdication of responsibility; a final statement to reassure herself that our relationship is over."
    n "これが返事を返すようなたぐいの手紙じゃないのは明らかだ。結局、この手紙はただのやっかい払いでしかない。俺たちの関係が終わったことを岩魚子が自分自身に念押しするための最終通告なんだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4437
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_76b2fe88_2:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4442
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_87109222:

    # "As such, I find I have little problem in scrunching the letter and envelope into a ball and tossing it into the wastebin, ridding myself of its existence."
    "そんなわけで、俺はほとんどためらうことなくその便せんと封筒をくしゃくしゃに丸めてゴミ箱の中に投げ捨て、その存在を消し去ってしまう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4444
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_164d2fe6:

    # "I go to bed with mixed feelings, cheated out of a pleasant evening by this intruder from the past."
    "過去からの邪魔が入ったおかげで今日の楽しかった夜も台無しだ。複雑な思いを抱えたまま、俺はベッドにもぐり込む。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4446
translate jp a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_b149940b:

    # "Ironically, it takes a while before I can manage to sleep."
    "皮肉なことに、眠りにつくまでしばらく時間がかかってしまう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4459
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_cf393bd8:

    # n "{vspace=120}I sweat profusely, awaiting the dreaded moment."
    n "\n\n\n\n汗をびっしょりかきながら、恐怖の瞬間を待つ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4464
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_2c6c44df:

    # n "Each tick of the clock tenses my muscles that much more, every minute making more hairs stand on end."
    n "時計がカチカチとなるたびに全身の筋肉がこわばり、毎分ごとに髪の毛がどんどん逆立ってくる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4466
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_a96b8f51:

    # n "It's coming for me, I can feel it."
    n "それがやって来る。俺には分かる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4470
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_38ff58c0:

    # n "{vspace=60}{image=vfx/reddash.png}{color=#FF0000}{b}Death.{/b}{/color}"
    n "\n\n{image=vfx/reddash.png}{color=#FF0000}{b}死。{/b}{/color}"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4472
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_53617801:

    # n "{vspace=60}Death in the form of a single sheet of paper."
    n "死がやって来る。一枚の紙という形を取って。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4476
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4482
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_c80a94cd:

    # "I take the small pile of papers from the student in front of me and pass it backwards after plucking off the top piece."
    "俺は前の席の生徒から回ってくる紙の束を受け取り、そこから一番上の一枚を取って残りを後ろに回す。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4484
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_bd04f9e8:

    # "Looking to the top right of the page, I find my fears realized within that small red circle."
    "紙の右上を見て、恐れていたものがその小さな赤丸の中で現実のものとなったことを知る。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4490
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_dc2619ca:

    # "Forty-three."
    "４３点。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4492
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_38928e64:

    # "I hang my head and sigh in resignation. Cursing under my breath, I can feel the aura of a similar sentiment rising from the entire class. It's strange, but that fact lifts my mood by a minuscule amount."
    "俺はうなだれ、あきらめのため息を漏らす。小声で悪態をつくと、似たようなオーラが教室全体から伝わってくる。おかしなことだけど、それによってほんの少しだけ気が楽になる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4494
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_ab4d7549:

    # "Misery loves company, I suppose."
    "同病相憐れむ、ってやつか。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4496
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_915cc5de:

    # "As the teacher opens her mouth, the room braces for the inevitable onslaught…"
    "先生が口を開く。クラスの全員が避けようのない猛攻撃に身構え……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4502
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_ba13a641:

    # "…only to be saved at the last minute."
    "……だがしかし、土壇場で命拾いをする。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4504
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_41848011:

    # "We quickly move to collect our bags and leave for lunch post-haste, but the teacher delivers a parting broadside."
    "誰もが急いでかばんを取り、昼休みのために大慌てで教室を出て行く。だけど、先生が捨て台詞を吐くように言う。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4506
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_9496a65d:

    # "Teacher" "We'll be discussing the test scores next lesson. Needless to say, there will be quite some discussion to be had."
    "教師" "この結果については次の時間に話をするからな。言わんでも分かるだろうが、話すことはたっぷりとあるぞ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4508
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_36ebe3fc:

    # "A collective groan resounds from the class, now reduced to shuffling out dejectedly."
    "うめくような声が教室内で一斉に漏れ、その声を残して皆が落胆したように教室を出て行く。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4513
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_cb7f3439:

    # "I push the sheet into my bag as I walk along the hallway, crumpling it in the process. It's enough that such a troublesome letter ended up on my desk yesterday, and now this."
    "俺は廊下を歩きながら、紙をかばんの中にくしゃくしゃと押し込む。ただでさえ昨日は厄介な手紙を受け取るはめになったってのに、今度はこれかよ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4515
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_e8ce3abe:

    # hi "I hate English…"
    hi "英語なんて嫌いだ……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4519
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_0acb53ba:

    # mystery "HI—{w=0.3}SA—{w=0.3}O!"
    mystery "ひ――{w=0.3}さ――{w=0.3}お！"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4521
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_bbd6f2e8:

    # "A stern female voice gruffly calls out from behind me."
    "いかつい女性の声が俺の背後から荒々しく呼びつける。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4525
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_aaca95cd:

    # "I freeze on the spot, my face becoming like stone. It's as if I can feel my brain disconnecting from my body."
    "俺はその場で凍りつき、顔から血の気が引く。まるで俺の脳みそが体から切り離されてしまったかのようだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4527
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_8971236b:

    # "My eyes slowly shift right, trying to catch a glimpse of the disembodied voice."
    "俺は正体不明の声の主を探ろうと、目だけをゆっくりと右に向ける。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4531
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_e8eadcf9:

    # "…nothing?"
    "……誰もいない？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4533
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_bc3bd82d:

    # "My face begins to slip as time passes, and I decide to risk turning my head. Ever so slowly, I twist it to the—"
    "やがて俺の顔もそちらに向き始め、そしてついに振り返る決心をする。ゆっくり、ゆっくりと、俺はそちらの方に顔を向け――"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4537
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_22d6f8a7:

    # hi "GYAAAAH!" with vpunch
    hi "ぎゃあああああ！" with vpunch

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4539
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_2305000c:

    # "I jump into the air and drop my bag, yelling out in surprise."
    "俺はあまりの驚きに声を張り上げ、かばんを落として飛び上がる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4541
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_7f626672:

    # "As I recover and regain my composure, I turn to see… I should have known."
    "やがて平静を取り戻し、振り返ると……俺も気づけていたはずなんだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4543
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_b18cd80c:

    # hi "Emi."
    hi "笑美"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4550
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_a87e7265:

    # emi "Gotcha, Hisao."
    emi "びっくりしたでしょ、久夫くん"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4552
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_5db94be3:

    # "She stands there with a mischievous grin on her face, hands forward and fingers pointed inwards. She was the one who jabbed my ribs with her fingers."
    "いたずらっぽい笑顔でそこに立ち、手を差し伸ばして指を内側に突き出している。俺の肋骨を指で突っついたのは笑美だったんだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4554
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_a22fca09:

    # "I look down at her with a grimace, rubbing my hair in frustration."
    "俺は顔をしかめ、いら立ちに髪をかきむしりながら笑美を見下ろす。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4556
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_c3e042eb:

    # hi "That's no way to greet someone, you know."
    hi "こんな挨拶ってありえないだろ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4561
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_377973b9:

    # emi "You have no sense of humor."
    emi "もぅ、ノリが悪いんだから"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4563
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_61a866a5:

    # hi "I left my sense of humor in my English class. Complain to the teacher if you want it given back to me."
    hi "そんなもの、英語の授業に置いてきたよ。俺にノリを取り戻してほしいなら英語の先生に言ってくれ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4568
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_56b94a94:

    # "She pulls her best puppy-dog eyes on me as she pouts. Lilly's managed to build up my resistance to the tactic, but Emi's short stature adds enough to the effect to make me relent."
    "笑美がぷうっと膨れながら子犬のような目で俺を見つめる。リリーのおかげでこの手に耐えられるようにはなったけど、笑美の背が小さいことも加わって、結局俺の気分は和んでしまう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4570
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_3a1d852f:

    # hi "So, how are things? I haven't seen you around for a while."
    hi "それで、調子はどうだ？　しばらく見なかったけど"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4575
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_e5a8c96f:

    # emi "Same old, same old. I run so fast, nobody wants to join me on my morning runs."
    emi "相変わらずよ。あたしの走りが速すぎちゃって、誰も朝練に付き合ってくれないし"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4580
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_3edeb4aa:

    # emi "It's a real pain."
    emi "ほんと、寂しいわよね"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4582
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_9935e964:

    # "Her modesty never fails to amuse me."
    "笑美のこういう謙虚なところはいつ見ても面白いな。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4587
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_46afa957:

    # emi "Although…"
    emi "だけどさ……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4589
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_12c320ca:

    # "Uh oh."
    "ヤバい。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4594
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_589c4751:

    # emi "You know what I'm thinking, don't you Hisao?"
    emi "あたしの考えてること、分かるよね、久夫くん？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4596
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_89442612:

    # "Wearing my emotions on my sleeve is one of my worst habits. She's seen right through me."
    "感情がすぐに表に現れるのは俺の一番悪い癖だ。笑美はすぐにそれを見て取る。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4598
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_f33cc201:

    # "Fortunately, I see somebody else approaching us that will give me an out."
    "ラッキーなことに、この場を抜け出すチャンスをくれそうなある人物が近づいてくるのに気づく。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4600
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_42a0e457:

    # hi "Oh, hi Hanako."
    hi "あっ、やあ、華子"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4609
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_605c983d:

    # "I give her a welcoming wave, and try my best at looking like I haven't noticed Emi's pouting face. She gives a small wave back."
    "笑美の膨れっ面に最大限気づかないふりをしながら、俺は華子を呼び寄せようと手を振る。華子が小さく手を振り返す。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4614
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_f1c59e8c:

    # ha "H-hello, Hisao… Emi."
    ha "こ、こんにちは、久夫くん……笑美ちゃん"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4619
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_79af79c5:

    # emi "Hey Hanako."
    emi "やっ、華子"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4621
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_7f1332b1:

    # hi "I'll join you and Lilly in a sec."
    hi "すぐ華子とリリーの所に行くから"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4623
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_f57ce7ca:

    # hi "Actually, speaking of lunchtime company, it's odd to see you without Rin, Emi."
    hi "そういやさ、笑美。昼休みの連れといえば、琳が一緒にいないのは珍しいな"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4629
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_a3e85df2:

    # emi "Ah! Rin!"
    emi "あっ！　琳！"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4636
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_f3f6fcc4:

    # "Without a second word, she forgets all about us and bolts off up the hallway. She must've forgotten she was waiting for her."
    "それきり一言の挨拶もなく、笑美は俺たちのことを放り出して廊下を走り去ってしまう。琳が待っていることを忘れていたに違いない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4638
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_6edfe935:

    # "Hanako and I stand speechless, only able to helplessly stand and watch this ball of seemingly boundless energy dash off."
    "華子と俺は無言で立ち尽くす。ただ呆然と、果てしないエネルギーを持つとも思えるあの物体が走り去るのを見守るしかない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4648
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_c74ed047:

    # emi "Oh yeah, Hisao…"
    emi "あっ、そうだ、久夫くん……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4650
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_b390c175:

    # "She suddenly stops herself just before vanishing around the corner to the rooftop staircase, spinning around to meet our bemused faces."
    "屋上への階段に向かう廊下の角に消える直前、笑美が突然ブレーキをかけるとくるっと振り向いて、あっけにとられている俺と華子に向き合う。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4655
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_aeb04147:

    # emi "I hate English too."
    emi "あたしも英語嫌いなんだ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4664
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_bc6a3772:

    # "And with that, she disappears."
    "その言葉を残し、消え去る。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4666
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_05238884:

    # "All I can do is hang my head and give a long sigh, thoroughly left in the dust."
    "俺は完全に煙に巻かれてしまったような気持ちで、うなだれて大きなため息をつくことしかできない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4671
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_530de478:

    # "As I hear a short giggle coming from behind me, I turn to see Hanako smiling at the corner my attacker rounded."
    "背後からの小さなくすくす笑いを聞いて俺が振り返ると、笑美がいた場所で華子が微笑んでいる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4679
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_c961089c:

    # "I pick up my dropped bag from the floor and quickly dust it off."
    "俺は床に落ちている自分のかばんを拾うと、素早くほこりを払い落す。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4681
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_c4feb367:

    # hi "Afternoon. Been busy?"
    hi "こんちは。忙しい？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4686
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_0ced8f99:

    # ha "You don't… like English?"
    ha "英語……嫌いなの？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4688
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_984f3a3b:

    # hi "Hmm? Oh, uh, nah. I had a test on it a while back, and Emi caught me brooding about the results."
    hi "えっ？　ああ、ええと、いや。こないだの英語のテストのことでさ。点のことでくさってたら笑美に見られちゃって"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4693
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_45940ae1:

    # ha "Ah, sorry…"
    ha "ああ、ごめんなさい……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4695
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_658ae0c3:

    # "She averts her gaze, guilt written onto her face. A casual observer would think she'd just accidentally reminded me of a dead relative."
    "きまりの悪そうな表情で華子が顔をそむける。傍から見れば、まるで彼女が俺にうっかり死んだ家族の話題を振ってしまったかのような光景だろう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4697
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_3382a9ba:

    # hi "Come on, it's not your fault. How're you doing in it?"
    hi "おいおい、華子のせいじゃないよ。華子はどうだった？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4702
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_d4ce6237:

    # "She looks up, though still avoids meeting my eyes."
    "華子が上目づかいで俺を見る。俺と目を合わせないようにしているけど。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4707
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_37138615:

    # ha "All right, I… suppose."
    ha "まあまあ……かな"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4709
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_025b84b6:

    # "An awkward silence passes. They seem all too common around Hanako."
    "気まずい沈黙が流れる。華子の周囲ではいつものことだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4714
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_07dfe828:

    # ha "Oh, Lilly asked if… you'd like to join us for lunch on the roof."
    ha "あっ、リリーが……屋上でお昼一緒にどう、って"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4716
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_6508177d:

    # "I guess I don't exactly have any pressing engagements to attend to."
    "まあ、他に取り立てて重要な用事もないか。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4718
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_599ae248:

    # hi "Sure, I'll be right up."
    hi "もちろん。すぐ行くよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4723
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_dde0ee91:

    # ha "Um, I'll… go get my lunch from the cafeteria now… then."
    ha "えっと、私……食堂でお昼買ってくる……から"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4725
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_927d43d5:

    # hi "Go on. You don't need my approval to leave, you know."
    hi "行ってきなよ。別に俺に許可取らなくてもいいんだぞ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4730
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_198655f4:

    # ha "O-okay. I'll… be going then."
    ha "わ、分かった。行って……きます"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4737
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_d82f88a4:

    # "She gives a skittish reply, a small nod and quickly makes off towards the cafeteria."
    "華子がおどおどしながら返事をして、それから小さくうなずくと食堂のほうへと急いでいく。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4753
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_e5a3182e:

    # "I guess she must've forgotten to bring lunch today. As I walk through the hallways, more and more students start to come out of classrooms and pass me, going in the same direction as Hanako went."
    "華子は今日の昼飯を持ってこなかったんだろう。廊下を歩いていると、教室から出てくる生徒の数がどんどん増えていき、俺とすれ違いながら華子が向かったのと同じ方向へ歩いていく。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4755
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_f939d98d:

    # "By the time I manage to make it to the stairs, I'm having to push my way past a busily chatting throng of students."
    "俺が屋上への階段へと向かうころには、忙しくおしゃべりする人だかりを押しのけないと前に進めないほどの混み具合になっている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4765
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_116fd64a:

    # "I finally manage to get past the last of the crowd and round the staircase, slumping slightly in relief and slowing my pace before I open the door to the roof."
    "俺はついに最後の人ごみをかき分け、階段を上る。ほっとして少し前かがみになり、息を整えてから屋上へとつながるドアを開ける。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4774
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_dcbf2b27:

    # hi "Ah, damn!"
    hi "うわっ、くそっ！"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4776
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_ca0e48fa:

    # "I momentarily avert my eyes, all but blinded by the harsh summer sun."
    "夏の強い日差しで何も見えなくなり、俺は瞬時に目を横にそらす。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4794
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_74df9be6:

    # mystery "Hmm?"
    mystery "ん？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4798
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_4eb993a0:

    # "As I slowly regain my vision, the surroundings finally take form."
    "ゆっくりと視界が戻り、やがて周りにいる人物の姿がはっきりしてくる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4800
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_76623e59:

    # "Lilly, Emi and Rin sit together on the rooftop, the top of the hilltop forest around Yamaku visible past the fence around them, as if to frame the view."
    "リリー、笑美、琳が屋上で一緒に座っている。学園周りの丘の頂上に茂る森が彼女たちの周りにあるフェンス越しに見える。その様子はまるで額縁のようだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4805
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_9c84d970:

    # emi "Ah, Hisao!"
    emi "あっ、久夫くん！"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4811
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_dc3baf73:

    # "Lilly and Rin give a quick nod of acknowledgment and a deep nod of greeting respectively."
    "リリーと琳が気づいたかのように軽くうなずき、それからそれぞれが深い会釈をする。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4813
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_8c193b67:

    # "I start walking towards the rather mismatched trio, and can't help marveling at the speed with which Emi devours the rest of her half-eaten banana."
    "どこかおかしな組み合わせの３人に向かって俺は歩き出す。そのあいだも笑美が食べかけのバナナの残りを平らげるスピードに驚愕せずにはいられない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4815
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_fc819a6b:

    # hi "Hey. Strange to see you three together like this."
    hi "やあ。３人が一緒にいるの見ると、なんか変な感じだな"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4820
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_e02583f1:

    # li "It seems to have been quite the day of coincidences; Emi and Rin decided to eat on the roof just as Hanako and I decided to."
    li "今日は奇遇が重なる日のようですね。笑美ちゃんと琳さんも、私や華ちゃんと同じように屋上で昼食を取ろうとしていたので"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4825
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_32f554a8:

    # emi "You stole it! This spot was ours!"
    emi "そっちが盗ったんじゃない！　この場所はあたしたちのだったのに！"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4827
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_f558f1e1:

    # hi "Simmer down, you can't steal a place in the school."
    hi "落ち着けよ。学校の場所は盗めないだろ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4829
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_7b758fcc:

    # "I plonk myself down beside Lilly, the four of us creating a semicircle."
    "俺はリリーのそばにどさっと腰を下ろし、四人が半円の形で向き合う。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4834
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_b4c194b0:

    # rin "I think she is right."
    rin "笑美は正しいと思うけど"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4836
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_48218b6b:

    # hi "You too?"
    hi "琳もそう思うのか？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4841
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_04b4581d:

    # rin "The butterfly is her accomplice."
    rin "蝶がリリーの共犯者なんだ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4843
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_614e8f0f:

    # hi "The butter…"
    hi "ちょ……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4845
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_9d192438:

    # "As I glance around, sure enough, a small yellow butterfly floats across my field of vision."
    "俺が周りを見回すと、琳の言う通り、小さな黄色い蝶が俺の視界を横切っていく。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4847
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_3dbe61fa:

    # hi "So tell me, how did this butterfly help Lilly 'steal' this spot?"
    hi "じゃあ聞くけどな、その蝶がどうやってリリーがこの場所を『盗む』のを助けたんだ？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4852
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_081d29a9:

    # rin "It scouted out our conversation and told her."
    rin "そいつが私たちの会話を偵察してリリーに教えたんだ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4854
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_7a5f7f56:

    # "I should've known better than to expect sound reasoning from Rin. Regardless, I guess it wouldn't hurt to play along."
    "琳にまともな理屈を期待した俺が間違ってた。まあそれでも、もうしばらく話を合わせてやるのも悪くないだろう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4856
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_562caac5:

    # hi "You're telling me she can talk to butterflies?"
    hi "リリーは蝶と話せる、って言いたいのか？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4861
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_37c9fbbb:

    # rin "There are people who can talk to horses, called horse whisperers."
    rin "馬と話せる人だっているんだよ。ホースウィスパラーっていうんだ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4866
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_608c298f:

    # rin "Lilly must be a butterfly whisperer."
    rin "リリーは蝶ウィスパラーに違いないよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4868
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_33ae872d:

    # "I bury my head in my hands as Emi rounds on her strange companion. She doesn't seem to share Rin's sense of humor."
    "俺は頭を抱える一方で、笑美は琳に食ってかかる。どうやら笑美には琳のユーモアのセンスは通じないらしい。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4873
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_28745091:

    # emi "Whisperers don't work like that."
    emi "ウィスパラーってのはそういうのじゃないでしょ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4875
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_34d0001f:

    # "Emi and Rin continue their banter as I turn to Lilly, who's busily finishing off her small box of curry and rice."
    "笑美と琳が冗談話に花を咲かせるあいだ、俺はリリーの方を振り返る。彼女は小さな弁当箱の中のカレーライスを食べ終えようと懸命に木の箸を動かしている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4877
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_b05883a9:

    # hi "So what brought you up here, anyway?"
    hi "そんなことより、リリーはどうしてここにしたの？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4882
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_29b8a23e:

    # li "A little fresh air every now and again doesn't hurt."
    li "新鮮な空気を時々味わうのも悪くはないですしね"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4887
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_9dde5fe4:

    # emi "Ah!"
    emi "あーっ！"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4889
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_462dce6f:

    # "Emi breaks off from her vain attempts to introduce the concept of logic to Rin."
    "論理の概念を琳に教えようと無駄な努力をしていた笑美がそれを中断する。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4894
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_6eb7897b:

    # emi "That was why we came up here too!"
    emi "あたしたちだって同じ理由で来たのよ！"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4896
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_dd6b669c:

    # "Something tells me it was her idea alone, and that Rin only got dragged up here on Emi's whim. Then again, the same could probably be said of Lilly and Hanako."
    "どうせ笑美ひとりの考えに違いない。琳はただ笑美の気まぐれでここに引っ張って来られただけだ。だけど、それはたぶんリリーと華子にも当てはまるだろう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4901
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_f4686d17:

    # li "Now, now. We can share."
    li "まあまあ。一緒に過ごしましょう"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4912
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_1f9a0da5:

    # "The creaking of the door to the roof can be heard as soon as she says the words. A moment of silence falls over us as everyone's attention focuses on the figure appearing from it."
    "リリーが言葉を発すると同時に、屋上のドアがきしむ音を立てて開く。皆がそこから現れる人物に注目する一瞬のあいだ、沈黙がその場を覆う。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4930
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_080fb3ab:

    # "Hanako slowly walks over to us, her eyes pinned to the ground, silently ruing the attention she's attracting. She tenses, just barely, when her eyes meet Rin's."
    "華子がゆっくりとこちらに向かって来る。目は地面に伏せたまま、注目を浴びたことを静かに悔いている。琳と目が合った時、華子がほんの少しだけこわばった様子を見せる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4932
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_7bfcf171:

    # "I can't help raising an eyebrow as she walks over to us and sits next to me, doing her utmost to avoid looking up even as she brings her cafeteria bread to her mouth."
    "華子がこちらに歩いて来て俺の隣に座り、ほとんど目も上げずに食堂のパンを口に運んでいるのを見て、心配な気分になってくる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4940
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_de5cae52:

    # hi "So how do you and Emi know each other, anyways?"
    hi "そういや、リリーと笑美はどうやって知り合ったんだ？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4948
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_077a5b0a:

    # li "Emi's somewhat well known around the school for her athletic ability. She's the fastest member of the track and field club by some margin, even beating Miki Miura at the track meet last week."
    li "笑美ちゃんの運動能力は校内でもちょっと有名ですからね。陸上部のメンバーの中でも飛び抜けて速くて、先週の競技会では三浦美貴さんにも勝ったほどですよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4950
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_d687e3c4:

    # "Miki Miura… ah, that tanned girl from the front of my class. Considering her height and toned body, being able to beat her is quite an accomplishment."
    "三浦美貴って……ああ、同じクラスで前の席に座ってる日焼けした子か。彼女の身長と引き締まった体を考えたら、あの子に勝てるというのは相当すごいことだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4955
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_9a0f6a6f:

    # "Looking over to Emi, it's very clear she's well aware of this fact as she beams proudly."
    "笑美の方を見やると、自分でもそのことを十分承知しているようで、自慢げに笑っている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4960
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_9fc551e7:

    # emi "So, Hisao. What was your score in English?"
    emi "でさ、久夫くん。英語のテスト何点だったの？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4962
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_1263e952:

    # "Ouch."
    "あちゃ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4967
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_27984b74:

    # hi "No comment."
    hi "ノーコメント"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4973
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_4af384a4:

    # emi "Boo~."
    emi "ぶぅぅ～"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4975
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_98cff811:

    # "She puffs her cheeks and pouts, but it doesn't take long for her to bounce back."
    "笑美が頬を膨らませてむくれるけど、あっという間に元の表情に戻る。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4980
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_3595ebbe:

    # emi "All right, if I tell you mine, you have to tell me yours. Deal?"
    emi "いいわ。あたしの点を教えるから、久夫くんも教える。どう？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4987
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_87be1db0:

    # hi "Fine, fine."
    hi "分かった、分かった"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4993
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_bf4ed537:

    # emi "Okay, on the count of three, we both say our results."
    emi "よーし、３つ数えた後で、いっせいに点を言うのよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4998
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_9c1b62b9:

    # emi "One…{w=1.0} Two…{w=1.0} Three!{w=1.0}{nw}"
    emi "いーち……{w=1.0}　にーぃ……{w=1.0}　さん！{w=1.0}{nw}"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5005
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_ed96174c:

    # "I beam a mischievous grin."
    "俺はいたずらっぽくにやにや笑う。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5017
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_823b4dfc:

    # emi "Ah! Evil! Evil, evil, evil, evil!"
    emi "あーっ！　ずるい！　ずるい、ずるい、ずるい、ずるい！"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5022
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_c3938668:

    # hi "You said it, not me. Still, the fact that you managed an even lower score than me is kind of amazing."
    hi "笑美が言ったんだぞ。俺じゃない。だけどさ、俺よりも低い点を取れるなんて、ちょっと驚きだな"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5028
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_727ac656:

    # emi "Grr~!"
    emi "がるる～！"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5030
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_c699fa5f:

    # "She looks and sounds like a small terrier growling at an intruder. I can't say it's the most threatening sight I've seen."
    "笑美が姿も声も侵入者を威嚇する小型犬のようになる。今まで見た中で最も恐ろしい光景、とはとても言えないけど。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5036
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_1cd74053:

    # li "Either way, scoring higher than thirty-two isn't something to boast about, much less scoring below it. For any subject."
    li "どちらにしても、３２点よりは高得点、というのも自慢できることではありませんよ。それ以下なんてなおさらです。どんな教科であっても"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5041
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_813e264c:

    # hi "Yes, Lilly."
    hi "そうだな、リリー"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5047
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_3d3e7724:

    # emi "Sorry, Lilly."
    emi "ごめんね、リリー"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5052
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_433446e6:

    # li "I could help you with your English, if you'd like. It would be my pleasure to—"
    li "もしよければ、英語のお勉強をお手伝いしますよ。喜んでお助け――"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5057
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_b51102d2:

    # emi "No, no, that's fine. But I appreciate the thought. Really."
    emi "いい、いい、大丈夫。でも、ありがとね。ほんとに"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5064
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_8b5120f2:

    # "Lilly looks slightly deflated, her hopes of imparting her knowledge dashed. Judging from the badly hidden laughter of the rest of us, neither she nor Emi seem to have garnered too much pity."
    "リリーは自分の知識を伝授する望みを打ち砕かれて、少しがっかりしているように見える。彼女以外の全員が笑いを隠しきれずにいるのを見るに、リリーも笑美もあまり同情は得られなかったみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5076
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_505f7434:

    # "As I sit happily laughing though, I feel my voice suddenly cut off as my chest clenches."
    "だけど、愉快に笑いながら座っていると、俺は胸が締め付けられ、自分の声が突然失われるのを感じる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5085
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_529d176d:

    # "I sit in silence for a few seconds, all my concentration forced on my heartbeat. It's only a small pain, but the ache feels like it's growing."
    "俺は数秒のあいだ静かに座り、ただひたすら心臓の鼓動に集中する。ほんの小さな痛みだけど、だんだんひどくなっていく感じがする。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5105
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_f3585eb6:

    # "Breathe deeply… breathe deeply…"
    "深呼吸……深呼吸だ……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5114
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_d664a161:

    # "I glance upward to try and keep at least some of my attention on my surroundings, to see Emi suddenly freezing when she notices the expression of pain on my face out of the corner of her eye."
    "俺は上目づかいで、いくらかでも周囲に注意を向けるように努力する。笑美が彼女の視界の端で俺の苦悶の表情をとらえて、突然固まるのが見える。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5119
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_9cd42848:

    # emi "Hey, Hisao… are you okay?"
    emi "ねえ、久夫くん……大丈夫？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5126
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_20ad7d52:

    # hi "Yeah, I'm… fine…"
    hi "ああ、大……丈夫だ……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5135
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_21252ea2:

    # "I look back down and redouble my efforts to try and stay calm, clenching my fists to try and dull the pain."
    "俺は再び視線を落とし、落ち着きを取り戻そうとさらに努力を重ねる。痛みを和らげるためにこぶしを握り締める。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5155
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_372f958e:

    # "It takes a short time, but the pain, thankfully, begins to fade."
    "ほんの少し時間がかかったけど、ありがたいことに痛みが和らぎ始める。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5159
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_461bb528:

    # "When I look back up, there's only silence and pensive faces to be seen. I guess I'd better explain myself."
    "俺が再び顔を上げると、沈黙と悲痛な面持ちだけが目に入る。たぶん自分の状況を説明した方がいいだろう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5163
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_a7695639:

    # hi "Arrhythmia. I'm fine, it's… just a heart flutter."
    hi "不整脈なんだ。大丈夫、ただの……心臓粗動だから"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5168
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_00a304ff:

    # li "Are you sure? Should we get the nurse?"
    li "本当に大丈夫ですか？　ナースさんを呼びましょうか？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5174
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_8160992b:

    # "Taking her cue, Hanako quickly picks herself up and begins to dash to the door."
    "リリーの言葉を受けて、華子が素早く立ち上がりドアに向かって走り出す。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5176
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_ab71301a:

    # hi "Hanako, stop. Lilly, I'm fine."
    hi "待ってくれ、華子。リリー、大丈夫だ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5181
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_e8ea6dda:

    # rin "You look like a wet, wrinkled tomato."
    rin "君、ジュクジュクでシワシワのトマトみたいだよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5183
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_0f638bea:

    # hi "Huh?"
    hi "えっ？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5185
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_81563327:

    # "As I bring my hand to my forehead, I can feel the beads of sweat gathered on it and dab them off with my cuff."
    "自分の手を額に当てると、汗のしずくでびっしょりになっているのが分かる。俺は袖口でそれを拭い取る。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5187
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_a6063ed1:

    # hi "Thanks. I told you, I'm fine. I'm just kind of… fragile, I guess."
    hi "ありがとう。この通り、大丈夫だよ。ただ俺はちょっと……虚弱、なのかもな"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5201
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_cd4c7e04:

    # "The entire atmosphere's changed from one of gaiety to downcast faces, the situation being too awkward for anyone to know exactly how to react."
    "陽気だった全体の雰囲気がどんよりした空気に変わってしまう。あまりにも気まずくて、誰もがどうふるまったらいいのか分からない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5203
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_ecc06a2a:

    # "And of course, the whole thing is thanks to me. It just had to happen now, around others."
    "そしてもちろん、全ては俺のせいだ。よりによって今、みんなのいる前でこんなことになってしまうなんて。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5210
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_e90e265a:

    # li "Oh, Emi?"
    li "そうだ、笑美ちゃん？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5216
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_19972527:

    # emi "Hmm?"
    emi "へっ？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5218
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_dc457edc:

    # "She looks up, a box of juice halfway to her mouth."
    "笑美がジュースのパックをくわえたまま見上げる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5223
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_d14fe37d:

    # li "I haven't told you of my score yet, have I?"
    li "まだ私の点数を言っていませんでしたね？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5228
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_eb15938a:

    # emi "Yeah, well. You're half-foreign, so your score doesn't count anyway."
    emi "うん、まあ。でもリリーはハーフだからノーカンだよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5230
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_b2be9a7a:

    # "Lifting an eyebrow, I inquisitively turn to Lilly."
    "俺は眉を上げて、詮索するようにリリーのほうを向く。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5235
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_91e803f1:

    # hi "What was your test result, anyway?"
    hi "とにかくさ、リリーは何点だったの？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5239
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_a0119998:

    # "She gives a cheeky grin."
    "リリーがこしゃくな笑みを浮かべる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5245
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_338b4585:

    # li "One hundred percent. Perfect score."
    li "１００点。満点です"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5249
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_bb21fe62:

    # "No way. All I can do is hang my mouth open in wonder."
    "そんなバカな。俺は口をあんぐり開けたままあっけにとられることしかできない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5251
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_4edf4152:

    # "Considering those tests are insane even for some native speakers, I can only imagine she's gone and done something like committing to mind part of the dictionary. A gift for rote memorization, maybe."
    "あのテストは下手をするとネイティブであっても常識外れな難しさだった。それを考えると、リリーは辞書の一部を頭にたたき込むくらいのことをしたとしか思えない。丸暗記の才能があるのかもな。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5256
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_57b69778:

    # hi "That's…"
    hi "な……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5262
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_5fd7d042:

    # emi "See! Only someone part-foreign could get a score that good."
    emi "ほら見てよ！　ハーフじゃなきゃこんないい点は取れないよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5267
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_f818113a:

    # hi "'See'…"
    hi "『見て』……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5273
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_be8d5fe3:

    # emi "Er…"
    emi "あ……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5279
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_94a74791:

    # "Lilly and I grin at Emi's expense, her reaction identical to mine when I'd first tripped on that little landmine. Lilly's foreign ancestry does raise a point, though."
    "笑美の反応を見てリリーと俺がにやりと笑う。俺が最初にその小さな地雷を踏んだ時と同じ反応だ。だけど、リリーの外国の家系で一つ思い出したことがある。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5284
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_3ae4d60e:

    # hi "Ah, that's right. You leave tomorrow for Scotland, don't you?"
    hi "ああ、そうだ。リリーは明日スコットランドに飛ぶんだよね？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5290
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_cb0d3c8c:

    # li "That's correct. Emi heard some rumors about it; it seems word's spreading quickly, considering I only told a friend in my class a couple of days ago."
    li "その通りです。笑美ちゃんも知っていましたよ。数日前同じクラスの友人に話しただけなのに、噂というのはあっという間に広まってしまうようですね"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5295
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_c7ad04db:

    # emi "It must be so nice to go halfway around the world on a holiday."
    emi "休みに世界を半周できるなんて、すごく素敵だよね"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5300
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_6228a829:

    # emi "Hey, could you buy me something while you're there?"
    emi "ねえ、あっちで何かおみやげ買ってきてくれない？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5305
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_7d03870a:

    # hi "Don't be too shy now."
    hi "なんだよ、ずいぶん遠慮してるな"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5310
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_7571ba00:

    # "Lilly gives a lighthearted giggle, evidently fully expecting Emi's bluntness."
    "リリーが陽気にくすくす笑う。明らかに笑美の遠慮のなさを予想していたかのようだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5312
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_bd20579e:

    # "The rest of the lunch continues much the same as before, the jauntiness from before my heart flutter thankfully returning in full."
    "昼休みの残りの時間は今まで通りに続く。ありがたいことに、心臓発作が起きる前の陽気な雰囲気も完全に戻っていた。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5322
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_4b8d9d13:

    # "As everyone files off with the appropriate farewells, only Lilly and I are left."
    "皆適当に挨拶を済ませながら別れていき、リリーと俺だけがこの場に残る。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5324
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_d407bcd4:

    # hi "Hey, Lilly?"
    hi "なあ、リリー？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5326
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_4d2dde6d:

    # "She packs the last of her things into her bag and clips it shut, before perking her head up slightly."
    "リリーはかばんの中に物をしまい終え、かばんを閉めた後でほんの少し顔を上げる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5331
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_16b10efa:

    # li "Hmm?"
    li "はい？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5333
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_43061556:

    # hi "Um… thanks for breaking the silence back there. I kind of wanted to stop it, but didn't really know how to."
    hi "ええと……さっきは助け船を出してくれて、ありがとな。俺も何とかしたかったんだけど、どうしたらいいか分からなくてさ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5335
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_663fb400:

    # "As much as I'd like to sound less morose about it, the letter from yesterday, screwing up a test so badly in class, and now my heart make things very hard indeed."
    "できるだけ無愛想に聞こえないように言おうとする。でも昨日の手紙、テストのひどい結果、それにこの心臓のおかげで、そうするのがとんでもなく難しい。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5340
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_76018c39:

    # "She gives an indulgent smile and nods. I hope she hasn't picked up on it, but knowing her, it's unlikely that she hasn't."
    "リリーが寛大に微笑んでうなずく。気にせずにいてくれればと思うけど、彼女の性格からすれば、そうもいかないだろう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5342
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_2567438c:

    # li "Emi's strong, but only human. We do worry about you, Hisao."
    li "笑美ちゃんは体は丈夫ですが、それでも人間なんです。私たちだってあなたのことは心配しているんですよ、久夫さん"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5344
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_ff33e596:

    # hi "Hold on, why would I worry you?"
    hi "ちょっと待った、なんで俺のことが心配なんだ？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5351
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_b480b763:

    # "Her smiling face collapses, becoming uncomfortably serious."
    "リリーの笑顔が消え、かわりに息がつまるほどの真剣な表情になる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5353
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_2147ce8b:

    # li "Hisao, we are not ignorant of your situation."
    li "久夫さん、私たちはあなたの置かれている状況を知らないわけではないんです"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5355
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_d876827f:

    # li "Unli…"
    li "それは……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5360
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_66fd4e7f:

    # "She suddenly cuts herself short, unsure of whether she should say what she intends to. I give a weak smile and rest my hand on her shoulder."
    "リリーの言葉が突然途切れる。言いたいことを俺に言うべきかどうか迷っているんだ。俺は弱々しく笑うとリリーの肩に手を乗せる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5364
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_72540600:

    # hi "Don't. It's enough that I worry about it. I don't want you all to shoulder my burden."
    hi "やめてくれ。自分が心配するだけで十分だよ。俺の重荷をみんなにも背負わせたくない"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5369
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_25bbf6bb:

    # li "But…"
    li "でも……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5371
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_8ff88e7c:

    # hi "If you all worry about it, I have to worry about your worrying. If… that makes sense."
    hi "もしみんなが俺のことを心配したら、俺はみんなが心配してるってことを心配しなきゃならなくなる。意味……分かるかな"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5373
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_0e454488:

    # hi "I'm fine, okay?"
    hi "俺は大丈夫だよ。分かった？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5378
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_5cc5435d:

    # "For a moment she looks to be lost in thought, carefully pondering how to react."
    "リリーはしばらく考え込んでいるようだ。どう答えるべきかを注意深く探っている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5383
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_de9634ec:

    # li "Hisao, do you have any paper left from your food's packaging?"
    li "久夫さん、お昼ご飯の包み紙は残っていますか？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5385
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_2ecc8e81:

    # hi "I… think so? I'll just check."
    hi "ある……と思うけど？　確かめてみるよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5389
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_1acfffc4:

    # "I rummage around in my bag for the leftovers from lunch, eventually finding a paper square from my sandwich's package."
    "俺はかばんの中を引っかき回して昼食の残りくずを探り、ついにサンドイッチのパックに使われていた正方形の紙を見つける。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5391
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_9ad01c4c:

    # "My eyebrow raised and my expression rather quizzical, I gently place the square into Lilly's hand. Without another word, she brings her fingers around it to feel out its edges."
    "俺は眉をひそめ、いぶかしげな表情さえ浮かべながら、その紙をリリーの手に優しく乗せる。リリーは何もしゃべらず、指で紙の周りをなぞって角の位置を感じ取っている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5396
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_a53bf07c:

    # li "This should be large enough…"
    li "大きさは十分ですね……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5398
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_635ca1cd:

    # "With both of us seated on the roof, the minutes to the lesson ticking away, she proceeds to lay the item on the ground and begin her work in earnest."
    "２人で屋上に座ったまま、午後の授業まで刻一刻と時が迫る。リリーは紙を地面に広げると、真剣な様子で作業を始める。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5403
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_8e8e2bea:

    # "Wrapped in silence, I watch her fingers move about on the small square with amazing dexterity. A small fold here, a larger fold there, her fingertips keep a slow but sure pace."
    "辺りは静寂に包まれる。俺は驚くほど手慣れた様子で正方形の紙の上を動くリリーの指に見とれる。こちらを小さく折り、あちらを大きく折り。リリーの指先はゆっくりと、でも着実に紙を折っていく。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5405
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_b671936c:

    # "Looking up, her expression is calm and placid. The fact her face is pointed well above the sheet in front of her makes the sight of her work all the more curious."
    "顔を上げると、そこにはリリーの落ち着いた穏やかな表情がある。リリーの視線は紙の位置のはるか上を向いていて、そのおかげで彼女の作業姿がいっそう興味深いものに見える。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5407
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_21b98153:

    # "Her shoulders slump a bit after finishing one final fold, her work apparently done. It's only when she holds the item up in her hands that I realize what it is."
    "最後の一折りを終えると、リリーが少し肩の力を抜く。完成したようだ。彼女が手の上に乗せて持ち上げたときになって初めて、俺はそれが何であるかを知る。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5422
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_bbd1334e:

    # "A small origami crane."
    "小さな折鶴。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5424
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_861fb214:

    # "Light brown thanks to the packaging used, the result looks quite delicate and precise."
    "包み紙を使ったおかげで薄茶色のそれは、とても繊細かつ巧妙に見える。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5426
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_35ce8983:

    # hi "You can do origami?"
    hi "折紙折れるんだ？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5428
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_250236f5:

    # li "I taught myself how to do it when I was younger. It improved my dexterity a bit."
    li "小さい頃、自分で習ったんです。このおかげで少し器用になりましたよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5430
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_940a9afc:

    # hi "Huh…"
    hi "へえ……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5432
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_165e21f5:

    # "A little baffled, I carefully take the small bird from her pale cupped hands as if it would break from the slightest breath. It seems to be folded quite well, and holds its shape easily."
    "少しまごつきながら、俺はその小さな鳥をリリーの色白な手のひらから取る。息を吹きかけただけで壊れてしまう物を扱うかのように注意深く。それはとても上手に折られていて、しっかりと形を保っている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5440
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_bb941c83:

    # "We both grab our bags and head out the door, Lilly extending her cane as she does so."
    "俺とリリーはそれぞれのかばんを取り、ドアに向かう。リリーは杖を元の長さに伸ばしている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5447
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_e4fcfde8:

    # "I hold Lilly's handiwork up to my face for further inspection while we walk down the hallway, her hand running along the silver handrails for orientation."
    "２人で廊下を歩いているあいだも、俺はリリーの手作りの品をもっとよく見るためにそれを自分の顔の前に近づける。リリーは方向を定めるために銀色の手すりに手をかけている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5449
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_9b87e334:

    # "If she taught herself origami to improve her dexterity, with the use of her hands meaning so much to her given her condition… ah, so that's it."
    "もし器用さを鍛えるためにリリーが一人で折紙を習ったのなら、彼女の置かれた状況を考えたら手を使うということは大きな意味を持っていて……ああ、そうか。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5451
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_27eda1e3:

    # "I smile as I realize the bird's meaning."
    "俺はこの鳥の持つ意味に気づいて、微笑む。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5453
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_ade2c2cb:

    # "'Everyone here has had to find their own ways of dealing with their conditions. You aren't alone here when you have problems.'"
    "『ここにいる人は誰でも、自分の状況に折り合いをつける方法を自分で見つけないといけないんです。もしここで困ったことがあったとしても、あなたは独りではないんですよ』"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5455
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_37d88425:

    # hi "Thanks, Lilly. I appreciate this."
    hi "ありがとう、リリー。嬉しいよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5460
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_b1493468:

    # "She gives a sweet smile and a nod, not using words where none need be used, in her typical manner."
    "リリーが優しい笑顔で俺にうなずく。いつもの振る舞い通り、余分な言葉を発することもなく。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5465
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_0f6d3107:

    # li "All I ask is that you take care of yourself, Hisao."
    li "久夫さん、私はただ、あなたに体を大切にしてもらいたくて"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5467
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_d5be8d45:

    # hi "Don't worry, I will."
    hi "心配いらないよ、大切にする"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5472
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_1bb7182e:

    # li "Promise?"
    li "約束してくれますか？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5474
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_a316709f:

    # hi "Promise."
    hi "約束する"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5481
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_2138bb24:

    # "And with that, we part ways."
    "こうして、俺たちは別れる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5483
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_86f9924f:

    # "To be honest, I don't know what annoys me more - the fact that I could die at any moment, or the fact that everyone knows that."
    "俺がいつ死んでもおかしくないということ。それを周りの誰もが知っているということ。どっちが俺にとってより不愉快なのか、正直言ってよく分からない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5485
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_30222011:

    # "I guess I'll just take each day as it comes. As the unexpected present in my hand reminds me, I'm not alone here. Even though I may be like this, I'm not alone."
    "俺はその日その日を生きるだけなんだろう。手の中の思いがけないプレゼントを見て、俺は独りじゃないと知る。こんな状況であっても、独りじゃないんだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5487
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_e824f231:

    # "If they worry, if anyone worries, I'll smile."
    "もし皆が、誰かが、俺を心配したら、俺は笑おう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5489
translate jp a2_lilly_little_wing_6aa9a332:

    # "I'll smile enough for all their worries to go away."
    "皆の心配を吹き飛ばしてしまうくらい、俺は笑おう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5506
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_c85844ff:

    # "The moment the bell rings out, a collective sigh of relief comes from everyone."
    "チャイムの音が鳴った瞬間、皆が一斉に安堵のため息をつく。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5510
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_def79e86:

    # "Much of the morning's been taken up by a droning lecture on stoichiometry, a topic entirely unbefitting of the insufferable heat permeating the classroom."
    "午前中のほとんどが延々と続く化学量論の授業に使われていた。うんざりするほどの暑さに覆われている教室で教えるには全くふさわしくないトピックだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5515
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_af882ca2:

    # "Knowing that attempting to teach anything more would be an exercise in futility, Mutou gives up and begins clearing the teaching materials from his desk for the day."
    "これ以上何かを教えようとするのは無益な行為だと知って、武藤先生があきらめた様子で教卓の上にある今日の分の教材を片づけ始める。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5523
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_bd47c786:

    # "As meaningless banter starts filling the classroom, I notice Hanako getting up and coming to my desk. She's been a lot less withdrawn lately, something which gives me a small measure of satisfaction."
    "たわいもない雑談が教室を賑わし始めるころ、俺は華子が席を立ち俺の机にやって来るのに気づく。最近の華子は以前に比べて内気な態度がずっと和らいでいて、俺はそのことに少し満足感を味わっている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5528
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_801c5115:

    # ha "Hello, Hisao."
    ha "こんにちは、久夫くん"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5530
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_66f1df30:

    # hi "Hey. Want to go pick up Lilly, then? It's close to the time when she'd need to get going if she's going to make the flight."
    hi "やあ。じゃあ、リリーを呼びに行くか？　フライト時間を考えたらそろそろ出なきゃいけないころだし"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5535
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_99765578:

    # ha "Um… about that…"
    ha "あの……そのことで……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5540
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_578146dc:

    # ha "She said she might be held up a bit by her classmates."
    ha "リリーがクラスの人たちと少し一緒に過ごすかもしれないって"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5542
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_0dffaa0f:

    # "I suppose that makes sense. Her class usually gets off a little earlier than ours, so Lilly would normally have just come to our classroom. Her class must be sending her off."
    "考えてみればつじつまが合う。リリーのクラスは俺たちのクラスよりもほんの少し早く授業が終わるので、普通なら彼女はもう俺たちの教室に来ているはずだ。リリーのクラスが彼女を見送っているに違いない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5544
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_0e1ad98d:

    # hi "Well, never mind. We can wait outside her classroom for once, right?"
    hi "そっか、まあいいや。俺たちはリリーの教室の外で待ってればいいよな？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5549
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_993c07c8:

    # "She gives a small giggle before nodding, the two of us taking our things and leaving for 3-2's classroom."
    "華子がくすくすと笑い、うなずく。俺と華子はおしゃべりをしながら３－２の教室に向かう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5556
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_60ef2020:

    # "When we reach our destination, I stop in idle amusement at the scene inside."
    "目的地に着いた時、教室の中の何気ない面白い光景が俺の目に留まる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5558
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_b4b1bed0:

    # "One of the shorter girls from the class has Lilly wrapped in an enthusiastic hug, her head no higher than Lilly's chin. Her other friends, of which there are several, are gathered around her as well. Lilly simply smiles kindly and hugs her back."
    "クラスの背の低い女子生徒の一人がリリーをぎゅっと抱きしめている。彼女の背はリリーのあごの位置よりも低い。他の数人の友達もリリーの周りに集まっている。リリーはただ優しく笑い、彼女に抱擁を返している。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5560
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_57bac33f:

    # "I guess Lilly must be pretty popular. Compared to Shizune's harsh but fair dictatorship of 3-3, Lilly seems more like a mother figure for 3-2, to say nothing of her height and looks."
    "リリーはとても人気者らしい。静音の３－３での厳格かつ公平な支配とは対照的に、リリーはいわば３－２の母なる存在のように見える。彼女の身長と容姿については言うまでもない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5562
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_5d2531b5:

    # "Kenji's pointedly cool demeanor as he packs up his things at his seat in the back corner of the classroom is expected. He's no doubt far from a fan of the fuss being made about Lilly's leaving."
    "教室の隅の席で持ち物をかばんにしまっている健二のひときわ目立つクールな態度も予想通りだ。奴がリリーの旅立ちが引き起こす大騒ぎに全く無関心であることは疑うべくもない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5564
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_b09c3b05:

    # "Looking beside me and seeing Hanako following my gaze, I decide to finally enter the room."
    "横をうかがうと、華子が俺が見ていたのと同じ方向に視線を向けている。俺はついに教室に入っていく決心をする。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5574
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_cd874f41:

    # hi "'Afternoon, Lilly. It's just me and Hanako."
    hi "こんちは、リリー。俺と、それから華子だよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5584
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_15141b8a:

    # "Hanako withers noticeably when exposed to the din being made around Lilly. Try as she might, I doubt she'll ever completely get over her social anxiety."
    "リリーの周りにできた人だかりに直面して、華子がひときわうろたえる。華子も努力はしているけど、社会の場に対する不安を完全に克服するのは彼女には難しいだろう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5589
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_a7be5c36:

    # ha "Hello…"
    ha "こんにちは……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5591
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_154e30c8:

    # "Lilly manages to work out our position reasonably well, her classmate detaching herself without a second word. A look of slight exasperation is written on Lilly's face, though I can't say I blame her."
    "リリーが俺と華子の位置をうまく探し当てるけど、クラスメイトがあっという間に再び彼女を俺たちから引き離す。そのときリリーがほんの少しいら立った表情を見せるけど、それも無理はない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5596
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_c4737f71:

    # li "Hello Hisao, Hanako. Do we have much time before the flight leaves?"
    li "こんにちは、久夫さん、華ちゃん。フライトまでまだ時間は十分ありますか？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5598
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_0a131b2c:

    # "I give a quick glance at my watch. Taking the trip to the airport into account, there's a good ten, maybe fifteen minutes left while still allowing for contingencies."
    "俺はちらりと自分の腕時計に目をやる。空港までの移動時間を考えても、どんなハプニングがあったとしても１０分、いやたぶん１５分は余裕がある。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5600
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_0eb4ed18:

    # hi "Yeah, we still have a few minutes to kill. I wouldn't worry about missing it yet."
    hi "ああ、数分は残ってるよ。まだ乗り遅れる心配はないな"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5602
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_c00b3437:

    # "Classmate" "Ah, is this Hanako?"
    "クラスメイト" "あら、池沢さん？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5604
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_ec2d9bb6:

    # "Uh oh. I think we've just inadvertently become entangled in Lilly's social web."
    "あちゃあ。俺たちまでうっかりリリーの社交の輪にまぎれ込んでしまったみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5606
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_77a2fc52:

    # "The girl is probably part of the legally-blind faction of the class like Kenji, given her almost windowpane-like spectacles. Her short, roughly-cut hair gives her a look that fits her excitable expression."
    "その女子生徒は健二のような弱視のグループの一人らしく、牛乳ビンの底のような厚いメガネをかけている。無造作にカットされた短髪は、彼女の興奮した表情によく似合っている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5611
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_5477aa3c:

    # ha "H-hello… um…"
    ha "こ、こんにちは……あの……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5613
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_0c1ba9aa:

    # "She takes Hanako's hand and pulls it up and down enthusiastically. I really don't get how girls can be so social to someone they only know as the friend of a friend."
    "彼女は華子の手を取るとぶんぶんと激しく上下に振る。女の子ってのはどうして友達の友達というだけの関係でこんなに親しくできるのか、俺にはさっぱり分からない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5615
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_db51a7b0:

    # "While Hanako exchanges nervous greetings, I look around the room for my short and overdressed next-door neighbor. Try as I might, he seems to have slipped out of the classroom without anyone noticing."
    "華子が緊張の挨拶を交わしているあいだ、俺は健二の姿を求めて教室の中を見まわす。探してみたけど、奴は誰にも気づかれずに教室を出て行ってしまったようだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5617
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_c81e8a73:

    # "For a moment I try to think of possible career paths that could reasonably benefit from his single skill, before putting my mind to more pertinent matters."
    "しばらくのあいだ、健二がどういう進路を進めば奴の唯一のスキルを適切に生かせるだろうかと俺は考えをめぐらせる。その後で、もっと切実な事柄へと思考を移す。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5623
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_a7c5d3cb:

    # "Lilly seems pleased, if somewhat guarded, about the enthusiasm Hanako's suddenly excited from those around her. She might not see it, but Hanako's much less panicked about the affair than I'd anticipated."
    "華子が急に周りの女の子たちの興奮を呼び起こしたことに、リリーは多少用心しつつも、喜んでいるように見える。リリーには見えないだろうけど、華子はこんな状況でも俺が予想していたよりずっと落ち着いている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5625
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_08dd4691:

    # "Shuffling my way through the gaggle of classmates, I eventually manage to reach her."
    "周りの生徒の集団にもみくちゃにされながらも、俺はようやくリリーの元にたどり着く。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5627
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_37ff7772:

    # hi "Don't worry, Hanako's fine."
    hi "心配ないよ、華子は大丈夫だ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5632
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_f507d2d9:

    # li "Thank you. I thought she might be overwhelmed by them."
    li "ありがとうございます。華ちゃんが参ってしまうかもしれないと思ったので"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5634
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_747d3bc8:

    # "Classmate" "Don't worry, we'll be gentle!"
    "クラスメイト" "心配ないわよ、私たち優しいもん！"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5639
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_335c6b44:

    # "Both of us grimace in unison. Hanako's nervous grin stays plastered on her face as another couple of girls moves in to meet her."
    "俺とリリーは同時に顔をしかめる。他の生徒たちが近寄ってくるあいだも、華子は相変わらず張り付いたような引きつった笑顔を見せている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5641
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_4dcd76ba:

    # "It's kind of amazing that even just a month ago she'd never have been able to cope with a situation such as this. Even when I first met her, the two of us completely alone, she sprinted from the library."
    "華子もたった一ヶ月前まではこんな状況に決して馴染めなかったに違いない。俺はなんだか信じられない気分になる。俺が華子と２人っきりで最初に出会った時も、彼女は全力疾走で図書室から出て行ってしまったんだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5643
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_f7b31355:

    # hi "So, got everything you need?"
    hi "さて、必要なものは全部持った？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5648
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_f02ab6e3:

    # li "It's all packed. I just have to go by my room to pick it up on the way, and Hanako and I need to change."
    li "荷づくりはすべて終えました。出発の時にそれを部屋まで取りに行かないといけませんが。それから、華ちゃんと私は着替えないと"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5650
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_4b7efb9a:

    # hi "I guess we'd better get going, then. Hanako?"
    hi "じゃあ、そろそろ行ったほうがいいな。華子？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5655
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_5b89d922:

    # "Hanako's head flicks up towards us in a flash, her face rather unmistakably appreciating the chance to extricate herself from the small group gathered around her."
    "華子がハッと俺たちのほうを振り返る。周りに群がる連中から抜け出せるチャンスを得た彼女の顔には、ありがたいという表情がありありと浮かんている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5662
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_4e9c9b46:

    # ha "C-coming!"
    ha "い、今行きます！"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5673
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_9604c1d2:

    # "The long taxi ride to the airport is surprisingly pleasant, despite the three of us being rather squashed together to fit in the small back seat. On the other hand, maybe 'despite' isn't the right word."
    "タクシーでの長い旅は、俺たち３人が皆後部座席に押し込まれていたにもかかわらず驚くほど快適だ。逆の見方をすれば、『にもかかわらず』という言葉はたぶん適切じゃない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5675
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_b0d34183:

    # "Lilly pays the fare to the driver as we file out, Hanako's eyes flittering left and right. Thankfully there aren't too many people around, most of them being inside the main building rather than milling around outside."
    "リリーがタクシー代を払い、みんなで車を降りる。華子は左右をきょろきょろとうかがっている。幸い、周りにはそれほど人はいない。ほとんどの人は外でうろつくこともなく建物の中にいるみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5682
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_5e441323:

    # "It isn't hard to spot Akira and Hideaki leaning against a fence while talking to pass the time. A large black travel bag, complete with wheels and travel handle, leans against the fence alongside them."
    "すぐにフェンスにもたれかかって時間つぶしのおしゃべりをしている晃さんと秀明くんを見つける。そばの車輪とハンドルの付いた大きな黒い旅行かばんもフェンスに立てかけてある。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5687
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_82e188a5:

    # "Hideaki's the first to notice us, pointing us out to Akira who gives an overenthusiastic wave."
    "まず秀明くんが俺たちに気づき、晃さんに俺たちを指し示す。すると晃さんがやたら大げさにこちらに手を振る。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5692
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_0a43f240:

    # aki "Hey! He~y!"
    aki "おい！　お～い！"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5694
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_6f35085b:

    # "I grab Lilly's travel bag for her as we go to meet the two, earning a nod of appreciation."
    "２人のほうに向かうため、俺はリリーの旅行かばんを手に取る。リリーがうなずいて俺に感謝の意を表す。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5700
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_6101972f:

    # aki "I've got all my stuff here, you got yours? Plane ticket as well?"
    aki "あたしの荷物は全部ここにあるよ。リリーはちゃんと持ったかい？　飛行機のチケットも？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5705
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_38ecaa6a:

    # li "Don't worry, I have everything. You?"
    li "心配しないで、全て持っているわ。姉さんは？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5710
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_d1bb0666:

    # aki "Yep. All ready to go."
    aki "うん。準備オッケーだな"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5715
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_c9369609:

    # hh "Not without some problems along the way, I might add."
    hh "ちなみに、準備中にトラブルもなくはなかったけどね"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5723
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_35a5d6fa:

    # "The snide remark has his head roughly dragged around by a very firmly clamped-on hand."
    "当てつけがましいコメントをした秀明くんの頭が硬く締め付ける腕によって乱暴に引き回される。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5729
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_fbb3db1a:

    # aki "Haha yeah, I kinda sorta forgot it was in my trousers' pocket. Trousers that I'd put in the wash…"
    aki "ははっ、ああ。なんていうか、ズボンのポケットにチケット入れてるの忘れちゃっててさ。ズボンを洗濯……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5734
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_c07cc9dc:

    # li "Oh no…"
    li "いやだ、もう……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5739
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_b9652b3c:

    # aki "Don't worry, don't worry. Did you know you can print out tickets if you order online nowadays? It's really cool."
    aki "大丈夫、大丈夫。最近はオンラインで予約したチケットはプリントアウトできるって知ってたかい？　すげえよな"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5744
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_522f5621:

    # "Hideaki's pained expression says that this wasn't a solution found quickly. It could have been worse, I guess."
    "秀明くんの苦渋の表情が、この解決法を見つけるのも簡単じゃなかったことを物語っている。大事にならずに済んでよかった、のかな。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5749
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_e6607490:

    # li "We'd better start off then. Check-in should be ready by now."
    li "じゃあ、そろそろ行ったほうがいいわね。チェックインはもう始まっているはずだから"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5756
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_8ee007bd:

    # aki "Yeah, you're right."
    aki "ああ、そうだな"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5758
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_2364b61c:

    # "There's a certain amount of wistfulness in both their voices. To say nothing of the people left behind, meeting their family again after all these years would be big for them."
    "２人の口調にはある種の感慨深い気持ちがこもっている。後に残していく人々のことは言うまでもなく、何年も経った後の家族との再会はとても大きな出来事だろう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5765
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_eee002c4:

    # ha "Lilly…"
    ha "リリー……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5767
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_401313a2:

    # "Hanako wraps Lilly in a gentle hug to say goodbye, one which is warmly reciprocated. Lilly and I share a brief hug afterward, each of us saying our goodbyes."
    "華子は別れを告げるためにリリーにそっと抱きつき、リリーも心からの抱擁を返す。それからリリーと俺は軽く抱き合い、お互いに別れを告げる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5769
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_f3ad736d:

    # "Beside us, Akira and Hideaki break off from a small hug and a word or two between them. It would probably look quite nice if not for the almost comical height difference between the two."
    "そばでは晃さんと秀明くんが軽いハグを終えて体を離し、いくつか言葉を交わしている。もし２人の滑稽なほどの身長差がなければ、とても素晴らしい光景になっていただろう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5777
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_ade2cc52:

    # "Lilly takes ahold of her sister's arm once all that needs to be said in farewells is said, the two walking past the huge glass doors."
    "リリーは告げるべき別れの言葉を全て告げ終えると晃さんの腕につかまり、２人は大きなガラスのドアの向こう側へと歩いていく。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5782
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_37f08616:

    # li "Goodbye Hisao, Hanako!"
    li "さようなら、久夫さん、華ちゃん！"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5787
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_1352e1e2:

    # aki "Seeya! Don't do anything stupid, Shortie!"
    aki "またな！　バカな真似するなよ、チビ助！"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5793
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_37439474:

    # "We wave at them until they disappear from sight in the throng of people moving about inside."
    "２人の姿が中の人だかりに埋もれて完全に見えなくなるまで、俺たちは手を振り続ける。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5795
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_b3f8f497:

    # "And then… we're alone."
    "そうして……俺たちは取り残される。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5797
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_18c783e4:

    # hi "Well… that's that."
    hi "さてと……行っちゃったな"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5802
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_ad23fcbc:

    # "I turn to see Hideaki already beginning to walk off."
    "すでに立ち去ろうとしている秀明くんのほうを振り返る。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5804
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_b14c559a:

    # hi "Seeya."
    hi "またな"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5816
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_75e96d9f:

    # "He throws a hand into the air, in a manner I'd expect of Akira. In the end, it's just Hanako and me left standing outside."
    "秀明くんは晃さんっぽいやり方で無造作に手を振る。そうしてついに、外で立っているのは華子と俺だけになる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5821
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_4438b574:

    # "I rest my hand on her shoulder. She absentmindedly gazes towards the front doors of the building, as if she might catch a glimpse of either of the two before they disappear."
    "俺は華子の肩の上に手を乗せる。彼女は今もぼんやりとビルのフロントドアを見つめ続けている。まるで去りゆく２人のどちらかをもうひと目見られるかもしれないと期待しているかのように。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5823
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_ad31e358:

    # hi "Don't worry, the time'll pass fast."
    hi "心配ないって、時間なんてあっという間に過ぎるからさ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5828
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_d87b7c30:

    # "She hesitates for a moment, but eventually nods."
    "華子はしばらくためらっていたけど、やがてうなずく。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5830
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_dd8a633b:

    # "With the scorching heat of the summer sun beaming down on us, we make our way to the nearby bus stop."
    "焼けつくような夏の日差しを浴びながら、俺と華子は近くのバス停まで歩いていく。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5835
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_990dd570:

    # "It's strange, really. Just when I'd begun to see Lilly differently, she leaves on what almost feels like a pilgrimage to the past."
    "本当に奇妙だ。俺が今までと違う見方でリリーを見始めたちょうどその時、彼女は自身の過去への巡礼ともいえるべき旅へと去ってしまう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5837
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_98ddb856:

    # "In a way, though, that's just what I've been doing since coming to Yamaku."
    "だけどそれはある意味、俺が山久に来てからずっと続けてきたことなんだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5839
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_a5ba77c5:

    # "As much as I may reflect on everything that's happened to me, I really am hardly unique. Everyone has their own circumstances and separate paths to get where they are now."
    "俺の身に起こってきた全てのことを考える限り、俺は決して特別なんかじゃない。誰もがそれぞれ違った状況にいて、各々が違う道のりで今いる場所にたどり着いたんだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5841
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_85d5abc6:

    # "Yet I still can't really work out how I should proceed. My life may have practically been reset, and I still can't find anything that satisfactorily fills the hole I still feel in myself."
    "それでも、俺がこれからどう歩むべきなのかが未だによく分からない。俺の人生は一度リセットされたも同然だ。そうして心にぽっかりと空いてしまった穴をまだ満足に埋められずにいる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5843
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_530f8b92:

    # "Maybe Lilly's leaving will be a good thing for me. Without her to lean on, I'll need to do more for myself. I'll have to be there for Hanako as well."
    "リリーが旅立ってしまったことは、きっと俺にはいいことなのかもしれない。頼るべき人がいない今、今まで以上に自分の面倒は自分で見なきゃいけない。華子の側にもいてやらなきゃな。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5845
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_4a141977:

    # "It feels strange to have so much changing so quickly after my months in that hospital that seemed to exist so separately from reality, but that's all the more reason for me to keep focused."
    "あんなにも現実から引き離されたかに思えた長い病院生活の後で、これほどたくさんの転機を短期間に迎えるなんて、なんだか変な気分だ。だけど、それがますます俺の意識を集中させる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5847
translate jp a2_lilly_bon_voyage_89a537b1:

    # "I can't let any opportunity slip out of my fingers in my attempt to rebuild my life."
    "自分の人生を立て直すためのチャンスを一つたりとも逃すわけにはいかないんだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5858
translate jp a2lc1o1_2d803fea:

    # hi "I was just thinking about some of the stuff that's happened, don't worry."
    hi "最近起こったことを考えてただけだよ。心配すんなって"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5865
translate jp a2lc1o1_16b10efa:

    # li "Hmm?"
    li "はい？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5867
translate jp a2lc1o1_eb53b994:

    # "She leans in even closer, forcing me to move sideways."
    "リリーが体を近づけて俺を深く覗き込み、俺は思わず体をそらす。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5869
translate jp a2lc1o1_50fe9ad9:

    # hi "Come on, don't you ever do that as well?"
    hi "おいおい、リリーだってそういうことあるだろ？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5874
translate jp a2lc1o1_d9060065:

    # li "You make it sound as if you're hiding something…"
    li "だって、まるで私に何か隠しているように聞こえるから……"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5878
translate jp a2lc1o1_fe47734e:

    # "Erk. Why must this girl be so perceptive?"
    "うっ。なんでこの子はこんなに鋭いんだ？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5880
translate jp a2lc1o1_3ea72233:

    # "Glancing back at her face though, she wears a cute, playful smile."
    "だけど、リリーの顔にはふざけているようなかわいい笑顔が浮かんでいる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5882
translate jp a2lc1o1_89b1018e:

    # "She's… playing with me? Even so, I'd rather not pursue this with her."
    "リリーが……俺をからかってる？　もしそうであっても、これ以上は話したくない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5884
translate jp a2lc1o1_c3218ae7:

    # hi "I told you, it's nothing."
    hi "言っただろ、何でもないよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5889
translate jp a2lc1o1_2a03162e:

    # "Lilly furrows her brow in disapproval."
    "リリーが納得いかない様子で眉をひそめる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5891
translate jp a2lc1o1_f1b7b2c2:

    # li "Is that so?"
    li "そうなんですか？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5893
translate jp a2lc1o1_178d2b99:

    # hi "Yes, it is."
    hi "そうだよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5898
translate jp a2lc1o1_3052d214:

    # li "You're a very bad liar, Hisao."
    li "久夫さんって、嘘が下手ですね"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5900
translate jp a2lc1o1_ea51b25c:

    # hi "That's true, but that's why I'm not lying. I'm a very trustworthy person."
    hi "それは認めるけど、だから俺は嘘をついてないってことだよ。俺は信用に値する人間さ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5905
translate jp a2lc1o1_e0fd7105:

    # li "I'm sure you are. I think I can forgive you just this once, though."
    li "ええ、そうですね。だけどまあ、今回だけは許してあげます"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5907
translate jp a2lc1o1_6363f6c3:

    # hi "Forgive? What for, exactly?"
    hi "許す？　何を許すって？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5917
translate jp a2lc1o1_9256d547:

    # "She giggles a little before resuming her quiet walking. Just what is she thinking now?"
    "リリーがくすくすと笑い、また静かに歩き出す。彼女は今何を考えているんだろう？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5921
translate jp a2lc1o1_acb5390d:

    # "I look up to the dark sky as I slump my shoulders."
    "俺は肩を落としながら暗い空を見上げる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5923
translate jp a2lc1o1_2693eeb0:

    # "I think this is something I have to sort out for myself, rather than relying on her for everything."
    "これは自分の頭の中で整理しなければいけないことだろう。全てをリリーに頼るのはよくない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5928
translate jp a2lc1o2_c0849fe4:

    # hi "It was just kind of… I was thinking about how you seem to have everything so sorted out, even with Hanako relying on you. I can admit that even I kind of relied on you when I first transferred in."
    hi "何ていうかさ……リリーは本当にいつも自分自身をきちんとしてるみたいだなって思って。華子にもああやって頼られているのに。俺だって、転入してきたばっかりの時はリリーに頼ってたって認めるよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5930
translate jp a2lc1o2_94e37d34:

    # hi "I think it's a good quality to have."
    hi "そういう性質を持ってるのって、いいことだと思う"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5932
translate jp a2lc1o2_47a4a17b:

    # "I turn to Lilly, surveying her reaction."
    "俺はリリーのほうを向き、彼女の反応をうかがう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5939
translate jp a2lc1o2_924770ff:

    # "She's forcing herself to look forward and furrowing her brow quite a bit. Her face looks a bit awkward, as if she was trying to find just the right words."
    "リリーは眉をひそめながら無理やり前を向く。その顔には気まずい感じの表情が浮かんでいる。まるでふさわしい返答の言葉を懸命に選んでいるかのようだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5941
translate jp a2lc1o2_ae1c704a:

    # hi "…Lilly?"
    hi "……リリー？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5946
translate jp a2lc1o2_d195aac8:

    # li "I would thank you, but… assuming that I don't rely on the presence of others is too much. You'd be wrong to think that Hanako simply depends on me with nothing in return."
    li "お礼を言うべきなのでしょうが……私が他の人を必要としていないと思うのなら、買いかぶりすぎです。華ちゃんが私に頼ることに、私が何の見返りも求めていないと考えるのも間違いですよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5948
translate jp a2lc1o2_5b54c61c:

    # "She seems to have a bit of trouble saying it, even though it's largely what I'd thought already."
    "リリーが少しためらいがちに言う。その内容は、俺にとってはもうほとんど分かっていたことだけど。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5950
translate jp a2lc1o2_7d220cf8:

    # "If she's tried so hard to maintain her independence, as anyone would have had to in her position, sighted or not, maybe she finds it hard to talk about her own needs."
    "目が見えるかどうかに関係なく、同じ立場に置かれたら誰でもそうするだろうけど、リリーがあんなに努力して自立した生活を保とうとしているのなら、自分が必要としていることを他人に話すのは難しいのかもな。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5952
translate jp a2lc1o2_bc4a7e2b:

    # "It's only now that I realize an omission in what she says, though. I decide to follow it up, largely in jest, to avoid things getting too personal."
    "だけどこの時になって初めて、俺はリリーがあることに触れていないのに気づく。話が個人的な話題になり過ぎるのを避けるため、冗談半分でそれを聞いてみることにする。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5954
translate jp a2lc1o2_8eefb666:

    # hi "Oh? And what about me?"
    hi "そうなの？　じゃあ、俺は？"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5961
translate jp a2lc1o2_013b7ffa:

    # "She suddenly runs ahead of me and turns, blocking me off."
    "リリーが突然前方に駆け出し、俺の行く手を遮るようにして振り返る。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5966
translate jp a2lc1o2_d6180298:

    # "With a smile, she holds her hands behind her as she leans forwards."
    "微笑みながら両手を後ろに回し、前かがみになる。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5968
translate jp a2lc1o2_4bd09d8f:

    # li "You're different."
    li "久夫さんは、違いますよ"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5974
translate jp a2lc1o2_09006685:

    # "And with that, she turns back and continues to walk ahead of me, a newfound spring in her step."
    "そう言うと、リリーはくるりと向きを変え、俺の前をとても軽やかなステップで歩き出す。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5976
translate jp a2lc1o2_f93e1cd1:

    # "All I can do is raise an eyebrow and give a dazed grin. I don't think I've ever seen this playful and teasing side of her before."
    "俺は目を見開いて呆然とした笑いを浮かべることしかできない。こんなにも無邪気でいたずらっぽい姿のリリーを今まで見たことがない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5978
translate jp a2lc1o2_3198719b:

    # "So… I'm 'different'. It's hard to work out the exact context, but knowing her, this ambiguity was intended."
    "じゃあ……俺は『違う』のか。それがどういう意味なのか正確にはよく分からないけど、リリーの性格からして、彼女がわざとあいまいな言葉を使ったのは間違いない。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5980
translate jp a2lc1o2_984cc428:

    # "Our relationship has been changing, at the very least simply because I've begun to stand on my own feet more and started getting more curious about the situation of those around me."
    "俺とリリーの関係が変わってきている。少なくともそれは、俺がここで自立し始めて、以前よりももっと自分の身の回りのことに目を向け始めたからだ。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5982
translate jp a2lc1o2_de855c40:

    # "As to why… probably a mix of personal curiosity, and a want to try and work out how to deal with my situation."
    "それはつまり……たぶん個人的な好奇心でもあり、俺の今の状況にもっとうまく馴染もうとする自分自身の願望でもあるんだろう。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5984
translate jp a2lc1o2_254c0849:

    # "I'm less sure of Lilly, though. That's why her own statement, so similar to my own feelings towards her, throws me off so much."
    "だけど、リリーのことについてはまだよく分からない。だから、彼女が今言った言葉、俺の今の感情にとても近いそれが、俺をこんなにも煙に巻いている。"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5986
translate jp a2lc1o2_ca410592:

    # "Watching her make her way up the street, cane tapping from left to right, I decide to settle the matter later, and just smile. This is a nice side to her, and I don't want to forget it."
    "俺は杖を左右に打ち道を登っていくリリーを見ながら、このことについてはまた後で考えようと決め、今はただ笑うことにする。リリーの素敵な面を見ることができた。この出来事は忘れたくないな。"

